"use strict";(self.webpackChunksozler_kitabi=self.webpackChunksozler_kitabi||[]).push([[359],{359:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('[{"pageId":1,"rawText":"On Be\u015finci S\xf6z\\n\\n\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\\n\\n\u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u064f\u0646\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0656\u064a\u062d\u064e \u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064f\u062c\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650\\n\\nEy kozmo\u011frafyan\u0131n ruhsuz meseleleriyle zihni darla\u015fan ve akl\u0131 g\xf6z\xfcne inen ve \u015fu \xe2yetin azametli s\u0131rr\u0131n\u0131, o s\u0131k\u0131\u015fm\u0131\u015f zihninde yerle\u015ftiremeyen mektepli efendi! \u015eu \xe2yetin semas\u0131na yedi basamakl\u0131 bir merdivenle \xe7\u0131k\u0131labilir. Gel, beraber \xe7\u0131kaca\u011f\u0131z!\\n\\nBirinci Basamak: Hakikat ve hikmet ister ki zemin gibi semavat\u0131n da kendine m\xfcnasip sekeneleri bulunsun. Lisan-\u0131 \u015fer\u2019\xeede o ecnas-\u0131 muhtelifeye, melaike ve ruhaniyat tesmiye edilir.\\n\\nEvet, hakikat \xf6yle iktiza eder. Zira zemin k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve hakaretiyle beraber, z\xeehayat ve z\xee\u015fuur mahluklardan doldurulmas\u0131 ve ara s\u0131ra bo\u015falt\u0131l\u0131p yeniden z\xee\u015fuurlarla \u015fenlendirilmesi i\u015faret eder, belki tasrih eder ki \u015fu muhte\u015fem bur\xe7lar sahibi, m\xfczeyyen kas\u0131rlar h\xfckm\xfcnde olan semavat dahi z\xee\u015fuur ve zevi\u2019l-idrak mahluklarla doludur. Onlar dahi ins ve cin gibi \u015fu \xe2lem saray\u0131n\u0131n seyircileri ve \u015fu k\xe2inat kitab\u0131n\u0131n m\xfctalaac\u0131lar\u0131 ve \u015fu saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin dell\xe2llar\u0131d\u0131rlar. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc k\xe2inat\u0131, hadd \xfc hesaba gelmeyen tezyinat ve mehasin ve nuku\u015f ile s\xfcslendirip tezyin etmesi, bilbedahe m\xfctefekkir istihsan edici ve m\xfctehayyir takdir edicilerin enzar\u0131n\u0131 ister.\\n\\nEvet, h\xfcs\xfcn elbette bir \xe2\u015f\u0131k ister; taam ise a\xe7 olana verilir. Halbuki ins ve cin, \u015fu nihayetsiz vazifeye, \u015fu ha\u015fmetli nezarete ve \u015fu v\xfcs\u2019atli ubudiyete kar\u015f\u0131 milyondan birisini ancak yapabilir. Demek bu nihayetsiz ve m\xfctenevvi vezaife ve ibadata, nihayetsiz melaike enva\u0131 ve ruhaniyat ecnas\u0131 l\xe2z\u0131md\u0131r.\\n\\nBaz\u0131 rivayat\u0131n i\u015farat\u0131yla ve intizam-\u0131 \xe2lemin hikmetiyle denilebilir ki bir k\u0131s\u0131m ecsam-\u0131 seyyare, seyyarattan tut, t\xe2 katarata kadar bir k\u0131s\u0131m melaikenin merakibidirler. Onlar bunlara izn-i \u0130lah\xee ile binerler, \xe2lem-i \u015fehadeti seyredip gezerler. Hem denilebilir ki bir k\u0131s\u0131m ecsam-\u0131 hayvaniye, had\xeeste \u201cTuy\xfbrun Hudrun\u201d tesmiye edilen cennet ku\u015flar\u0131ndan tut, t\xe2 sineklere kadar bir cins ervah\u0131n tayyareleridirler. Onlar, bunlar\u0131n i\xe7ine emr-i Hak ile girerler, \xe2lem-i cismaniyat\u0131 seyran edip o cesetlerdeki h\xe2sselerin pencereleriyle cisman\xee mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 f\u0131trat\u0131 tema\u015fa ederler.\\n\\nElbette kesafetli topraktan ve k\xfcd\xfbretli sudan m\xfctemadiyen letafetli hayat\u0131 ve nuraniyetli zevi\u2019l-idraki halk eden H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131n, elbette ruha ve hayata m\xfcnasip \u015fu nur denizinden ve hatt\xe2 zulmet bahrinden bir k\u0131s\u0131m z\xee\u015fuur mahluklar\u0131 vard\u0131r. Hem \xe7ok kesretli olarak vard\u0131r. Melaike ve ruhaniyat\u0131n v\xfccudlar\u0131na dair \u201cNokta\u201d nam\u0131nda bir risalemde ve Yirmi Dokuzuncu S\xf6z\u2019de iki kere iki d\xf6rt eder derecesinde bir kat\u2019iyetle ispat edilmi\u015ftir. E\u011fer istersen ona m\xfcracaat et.\\n\\n\u0130kinci Basamak: Zemin ile g\xf6kler, bir h\xfck\xfbmetin iki memleketi gibi birbirine al\xe2kadard\u0131rlar. Ortalar\u0131nda ehemmiyetli irtibat ve m\xfchim muameleler vard\u0131r. Zemine l\xe2z\u0131m olan ziya, hararet ve bereket ve rahmet gibi \u015feyler semadan geliyor, yani g\xf6nderiliyor. Vahye istinad eden b\xfct\xfcn edyan-\u0131 semaviyenin icma\u0131 ile ve \u015fuhuda istinad eden b\xfct\xfcn ehl-i ke\u015ffin tevat\xfcr\xfcyle melaike ve ervah, semadan zemine geliyorlar.\\n\\nBundan, hisse karib bir hads-i kat\u2019\xee ile bilinir ki sekene-i arz i\xe7in semaya \xe7\u0131kmak i\xe7in bir yol vard\u0131r. Evet, nas\u0131l herkesin ak\u0131l ve hayal ve nazar\u0131 her vakit semaya gider. \xd6yle de a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 b\u0131rakan ervah-\u0131 enbiya ve evliya veya cesetlerini \xe7\u0131karan ervah-\u0131 emvat, izn-i \u0130lah\xee ile oraya giderler. Madem hiffet ve letafet bulanlar oraya giderler. Elbette cesed-i misal\xee giyen ve ervah gibi hafif ve lat\xeef bir k\u0131s\u0131m sekene-i arz ve hava, semaya gidebilirler.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc Basamak: Seman\u0131n s\xfck\xfbt ve s\xfck\xfbneti ve intizam ve \u0131tt\u0131rad\u0131 ve v\xfcs\u2019at ve nuraniyeti g\xf6sterir ki sekenesi, zeminin sekenesi gibi de\u011filler; belki b\xfct\xfcn ahalisi mut\xeedirler. Ne emrolunsa onu i\u015flerler. M\xfczahame ve m\xfcnaka\u015fay\u0131 icab edecek bir sebep yoktur. Zira memleket geni\u015f, f\u0131tratlar\u0131 safi, kendileri masum, makamlar\u0131 sabittir.","oldText":"On Be\u015finci S\xf6z\\n\\n[[\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|Rahm\xe2n ve Rah\xeem olan Allah\'\u0131n ad\u0131yla]]\\n\\n[[\u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0651\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064f\u0651\u0646\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0656\u064a\u062d\u064e \u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064f\u062c\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|Andolsun ki biz, en yak\u0131n g\xf6\u011f\xfc kandillerle s\xfcsledik ve onlar\u0131 \u015feytanlara at\u0131lacak ta\u015flar k\u0131ld\u0131k (M\xfclk, 67/5)]]\\n\\nEy [[kozmo\u011frafyan\u0131n|g\xf6k biliminin|astronomi ve co\u011frafyan\u0131n]] ruhsuz [[meseleleriyle|konular\u0131yla|sorunlar\u0131yla]] zihni darla\u015fan ve akl\u0131 g\xf6z\xfcne inen ve \u015fu \xe2yetin [[azametli|b\xfcy\xfck|y\xfcce, heybetli]] s\u0131rr\u0131n\u0131, o s\u0131k\u0131\u015fm\u0131\u015f zihninde yerle\u015ftiremeyen [[mektepli|okullu|modern e\u011fitim alm\u0131\u015f]] efendi! \u015eu \xe2yetin [[semas\u0131na|g\xf6\u011f\xfcne]] yedi basamakl\u0131 bir merdivenle \xe7\u0131k\u0131labilir. Gel, beraber \xe7\u0131kaca\u011f\u0131z!\\n\\nBirinci Basamak: [[Hakikat|Ger\xe7ek]] ve [[hikmet|bilgelik|felsefe, gaye ve fayda g\xf6zetilerek yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f]] [[ister ki|gerektirir ki]] zemin gibi [[semavat\u0131n|g\xf6klerin]] da kendine [[m\xfcnasip|uygun]] [[sekeneleri|sakinleri|orada oturanlar\u0131]] bulunsun. [[Lisan-\u0131 \u015fer\u2019\xeede|\u015eeriat dilinde|Dini terminolojide]] o [[ecnas-\u0131 muhtelifeye|\xe7e\u015fitli cinslere|farkl\u0131 t\xfcrlere]], [[melaike|melekler]] ve [[ruhaniyat|ruhaniler|ruhsal varl\u0131klar]] [[tesmiye edilir|isimlendirilir|ad verilir]].\\n\\nEvet, [[hakikat|ger\xe7ek]] \xf6yle [[iktiza eder|gerektirir]]. Zira zemin k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve [[hakaretiyle|de\u011fersizli\u011fiyle|k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve \xf6nemsizli\u011fiyle]] beraber, [[z\xeehayat|hayat sahibi|canl\u0131]] ve [[z\xee\u015fuur|bilin\xe7 sahibi]] mahluklardan doldurulmas\u0131 ve ara s\u0131ra bo\u015falt\u0131l\u0131p yeniden [[z\xee\u015fuurlarla|bilin\xe7 sahipleriyle]] \u015fenlendirilmesi i\u015faret eder, belki [[tasrih eder|a\xe7\u0131k\xe7a belirtir|vurgular]] ki \u015fu muhte\u015fem bur\xe7lar sahibi, [[m\xfczeyyen|s\xfcslenmi\u015f]] [[kas\u0131rlar|k\xf6\u015fkler|saraylar]] h\xfckm\xfcnde olan [[semavat|g\xf6kler]] dahi [[z\xee\u015fuur|bilin\xe7 sahibi]] ve [[zevi\u2019l-idrak|idrak sahipleri|anlay\u0131\u015f sahibi varl\u0131klar]] mahluklarla doludur. Onlar dahi [[ins|insan]] ve cin gibi \u015fu \xe2lem saray\u0131n\u0131n seyircileri ve \u015fu k\xe2inat kitab\u0131n\u0131n [[m\xfctalaac\u0131lar\u0131|okuyucular\u0131|dikkatle inceleyenleri]] ve \u015fu [[saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin|Rabl\u0131k saltanat\u0131n\u0131n|Allah\'\u0131n terbiye ve idare edicilik egemenli\u011finin]] [[dell\xe2llar\u0131d\u0131rlar|duyurucular\u0131d\u0131r|ilanc\u0131lar\u0131d\u0131r]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc k\xe2inat\u0131, [[hadd \xfc hesaba gelmeyen|say\u0131s\u0131z|s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z]] [[tezyinat|s\xfcslemeler]] ve [[mehasin|g\xfczellikler]] ve [[nuku\u015f|nak\u0131\u015flar|i\u015flemeler]] ile s\xfcslendirip [[tezyin etmesi|s\xfcslemesi]], [[bilbedahe|apa\xe7\u0131k|besbelli]] [[m\xfctefekkir|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen]] [[istihsan edici|be\u011fenen|g\xfczel bulan]] ve [[m\xfctehayyir|hayran kalan]] takdir edicilerin [[enzar\u0131n\u0131|bak\u0131\u015flar\u0131n\u0131]] ister.\\n\\nEvet, [[h\xfcs\xfcn|g\xfczellik]] elbette bir \xe2\u015f\u0131k ister; [[taam|yemek]] ise a\xe7 olana verilir. Halbuki [[ins|insan]] ve cin, \u015fu nihayetsiz vazifeye, \u015fu [[ha\u015fmetli|g\xf6rkemli|heybetli]] [[nezarete|g\xf6zetimine|seyircili\u011fine]] ve \u015fu [[v\xfcs\u2019atli|geni\u015f]] [[ubudiyete|kullu\u011fa]] kar\u015f\u0131 milyondan birisini ancak yapabilir. Demek bu nihayetsiz ve [[m\xfctenevvi|\xe7e\u015fitli]] [[vezaife|vazifelere]] ve [[ibadata|ibadetlere]], nihayetsiz [[melaike|melek]] [[enva\u0131|t\xfcrleri|nevileri]] ve [[ruhaniyat|ruhaniler]] [[ecnas\u0131|cinsleri]] l\xe2z\u0131md\u0131r.\\n\\nBaz\u0131 [[rivayat\u0131n|rivayetlerin|Peygamberden nakledilen s\xf6zlerin]] [[i\u015farat\u0131yla|i\u015faretleriyle]] ve [[intizam-\u0131 \xe2lemin|\xe2lemin d\xfczeninin]] [[hikmetiyle|gayesiyle|anlaml\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla]] denilebilir ki bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[ecsam-\u0131 seyyare|gezici cisimler]], [[seyyarattan|gezegenlerden]] tut, t\xe2 [[katarata|damlalara]] kadar bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[melaikenin|meleklerin]] [[merakibidirler|binekleridir]]. Onlar bunlara [[izn-i \u0130lah\xee|Allah\'\u0131n izni]] ile binerler, [[\xe2lem-i \u015fehadeti|g\xf6r\xfcnen \xe2lemi|maddi d\xfcnyay\u0131]] seyredip gezerler. Hem denilebilir ki bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[ecsam-\u0131 hayvaniye|hayvansal cisimler]], had\xeeste \u201c[[Tuy\xfbrun Hudrun|Ye\u015fil Ku\u015flar]]\u201d [[tesmiye edilen|isimlendirilen]] cennet ku\u015flar\u0131ndan tut, t\xe2 sineklere kadar bir cins [[ervah\u0131n|ruhlar\u0131n]] [[tayyareleridirler|u\xe7aklar\u0131d\u0131r]]. Onlar, bunlar\u0131n i\xe7ine [[emr-i Hak|Hakk\'\u0131n emri|Allah\'\u0131n emri]] ile girerler, [[\xe2lem-i cismaniyat\u0131|cisimler \xe2lemini|maddi alemi]] [[seyran edip|gezip]] o cesetlerdeki [[h\xe2sselerin|duyular\u0131n]] pencereleriyle [[cisman\xee|bedensel|maddi]] [[mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 f\u0131trat\u0131|yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f mucizelerini]] [[tema\u015fa ederler|izlerler|seyrederler]].\\n\\nElbette [[kesafetli|yo\u011fun|kat\u0131, maddeci]] topraktan ve [[k\xfcd\xfbretli|bulan\u0131k]] sudan [[m\xfctemadiyen|s\xfcrekli]] [[letafetli|ho\u015f|ince, latif]] hayat\u0131 ve [[nuraniyetli|nurlu|ayd\u0131nl\u0131k]] [[zevi\u2019l-idraki|idrak sahiplerini|anlay\u0131\u015f sahiplerini]] [[halk eden|yaratan]] [[H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131n|Yarat\u0131c\u0131\'n\u0131n]], elbette ruha ve hayata [[m\xfcnasip|uygun]] \u015fu nur denizinden ve hatt\xe2 [[zulmet|karanl\u0131k]] [[bahrinden|denizinden]] bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[z\xee\u015fuur|bilin\xe7 sahibi]] mahluklar\u0131 vard\u0131r. Hem \xe7ok [[kesretli|\xe7oklukla|bol miktarda]] olarak vard\u0131r. [[Melaike|Melekler]] ve [[ruhaniyat\u0131n|ruhanilerin]] [[v\xfccudlar\u0131na|varl\u0131klar\u0131na]] dair \u201cNokta\u201d nam\u0131nda bir [[risalemde|k\xfc\xe7\xfck kitab\u0131mda]] ve Yirmi Dokuzuncu S\xf6z\u2019de iki kere iki d\xf6rt eder derecesinde bir [[kat\u2019iyetle|kesinlikle]] [[ispat edilmi\u015ftir|kan\u0131tlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r]]. E\u011fer istersen ona [[m\xfcracaat et|ba\u015fvur]].\\n\\n\u0130kinci Basamak: Zemin ile g\xf6kler, bir h\xfck\xfbmetin iki memleketi gibi birbirine [[al\xe2kadard\u0131rlar|ilgilidirler|ba\u011flant\u0131l\u0131d\u0131rlar]]. Ortalar\u0131nda [[ehemmiyetli|\xf6nemli]] [[irtibat|ba\u011flant\u0131]] ve [[m\xfchim|\xf6nemli]] [[muameleler|ili\u015fkiler|i\u015flemler]] vard\u0131r. Zemine l\xe2z\u0131m olan [[ziya|\u0131\u015f\u0131k]], [[hararet|s\u0131cakl\u0131k]] ve bereket ve rahmet gibi \u015feyler semadan geliyor, yani g\xf6nderiliyor. [[Vahye|Allah\'\u0131n bildirmesine]] [[istinad eden|dayanan]] b\xfct\xfcn [[edyan-\u0131 semaviyenin|semavi dinlerin|ilahi dinlerin]] [[icma\u0131|fikir birli\u011fi]] ile ve [[\u015fuhuda|g\xf6rmeye|manevi m\xfc\u015fahedeye]] [[istinad eden|dayanan]] b\xfct\xfcn [[ehl-i ke\u015ffin|ke\u015fif ehlinin|manevi gizlilikleri g\xf6ren velilerin]] [[tevat\xfcr\xfcyle|g\xfc\xe7l\xfc haberleriyle|yalan \xfczere birle\u015fmesi imkans\u0131z topluluk haberiyle]] [[melaike|melekler]] ve [[ervah|ruhlar]], semadan zemine geliyorlar.\\n\\nBundan, [[hisse|duyuya]] [[karib|yak\u0131n]] bir [[hads-i kat\u2019\xee|kesin sezgi]] ile bilinir ki [[sekene-i arz|yery\xfcz\xfc sakinleri]] i\xe7in semaya \xe7\u0131kmak i\xe7in bir yol vard\u0131r. Evet, nas\u0131l herkesin ak\u0131l ve hayal ve [[nazar\u0131|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131]] her vakit semaya gider. \xd6yle de a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 b\u0131rakan [[ervah-\u0131 enbiya|peygamberlerin ruhlar\u0131]] ve [[evliya|veliler|ermi\u015fler]] veya cesetlerini \xe7\u0131karan [[ervah-\u0131 emvat|\xf6l\xfclerin ruhlar\u0131]], [[izn-i \u0130lah\xee|Allah\'\u0131n izni]] ile oraya giderler. Madem [[hiffet|hafiflik]] ve [[letafet|incelik|ho\u015fluk]] bulanlar oraya giderler. Elbette [[cesed-i misal\xee|misal\xee ceset|ruhsal, latif beden]] giyen ve [[ervah|ruhlar]] gibi hafif ve [[lat\xeef|ince|cismani olmayan]] bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[sekene-i arz|yer sakinleri]] ve hava, semaya gidebilirler.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc Basamak: Seman\u0131n [[s\xfck\xfbt|suskunlu\u011fu|sessizli\u011fi]] ve [[s\xfck\xfbneti|durgunlu\u011fu|huzuru]] ve [[intizam|d\xfczen]] ve [[\u0131tt\u0131rad\u0131|s\xfcregenli\u011fi|d\xfczenli ak\u0131\u015f\u0131]] ve [[v\xfcs\u2019at|geni\u015flik]] ve [[nuraniyeti|parlakl\u0131\u011f\u0131|ayd\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131]] g\xf6sterir ki [[sekenesi|sakinleri]], zeminin [[sekenesi|sakinleri]] gibi de\u011filler; belki b\xfct\xfcn ahalisi [[mut\xeedirler|itaatkard\u0131rlar]]. Ne [[emrolunsa|emredilse]] onu i\u015flerler. [[M\xfczahame|s\u0131k\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131k|birbirine zahmet verme, iti\u015f kak\u0131\u015f]] ve [[m\xfcnaka\u015fay\u0131|tart\u0131\u015fmay\u0131|\xe7eki\u015fmeyi]] [[icab edecek|gerektirecek]] bir sebep yoktur. Zira memleket geni\u015f, [[f\u0131tratlar\u0131|yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015flar\u0131]] [[safi|temiz|saf]], kendileri masum, makamlar\u0131 sabittir.","modernText":"On Be\u015finci S\xf6z\\n\\n[[Rahm\xe2n ve Rah\xeem olan Allah\'\u0131n ad\u0131yla|\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|]]\\n\\n[[Andolsun ki biz, en yak\u0131n g\xf6\u011f\xfc kandillerle s\xfcsledik ve onlar\u0131 \u015feytanlara at\u0131lacak ta\u015flar k\u0131ld\u0131k (M\xfclk, 67/5)|\u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0651\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064f\u0651\u0646\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0656\u064a\u062d\u064e \u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064f\u062c\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|]]\\n\\nEy [[g\xf6k biliminin|kozmo\u011frafyan\u0131n|astronomi ve co\u011frafyan\u0131n]] ruhsuz [[konular\u0131yla|meseleleriyle|sorunlar\u0131yla]] zihni darla\u015fan ve akl\u0131 g\xf6z\xfcne inen ve \u015fu \xe2yetin [[b\xfcy\xfck|azametli|y\xfcce, heybetli]] s\u0131rr\u0131n\u0131, o s\u0131k\u0131\u015fm\u0131\u015f zihninde yerle\u015ftiremeyen [[okullu|mektepli|modern e\u011fitim alm\u0131\u015f]] efendi! \u015eu \xe2yetin [[g\xf6\u011f\xfcne|semas\u0131na|]] yedi basamakl\u0131 bir merdivenle \xe7\u0131k\u0131labilir. Gel, beraber \xe7\u0131kaca\u011f\u0131z!\\n\\nBirinci Basamak: [[Ger\xe7ek|Hakikat|]] ve [[bilgelik|hikmet|felsefe, gaye ve fayda g\xf6zetilerek yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f]] [[gerektirir ki|ister ki|]] zemin gibi [[g\xf6klerin|semavat\u0131n|]] da kendine [[uygun|m\xfcnasip|]] [[sakinleri|sekeneleri|orada oturanlar\u0131]] bulunsun. [[\u015eeriat dilinde|Lisan-\u0131 \u015fer\u2019\xeede|Dini terminolojide]] o [[\xe7e\u015fitli cinslere|ecnas-\u0131 muhtelifeye|farkl\u0131 t\xfcrlere]], [[melekler|melaike|]] ve [[ruhaniler|ruhaniyat|ruhsal varl\u0131klar]] [[isimlendirilir|tesmiye edilir|ad verilir]].\\n\\nEvet, [[ger\xe7ek|hakikat|]] \xf6yle [[gerektirir|iktiza eder|]]. Zira zemin k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve [[de\u011fersizli\u011fiyle|hakaretiyle|k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve \xf6nemsizli\u011fiyle]] beraber, [[hayat sahibi|z\xeehayat|canl\u0131]] ve [[bilin\xe7 sahibi|z\xee\u015fuur|]] mahluklardan doldurulmas\u0131 ve ara s\u0131ra bo\u015falt\u0131l\u0131p yeniden [[bilin\xe7 sahipleriyle|z\xee\u015fuurlarla|]] \u015fenlendirilmesi i\u015faret eder, belki [[a\xe7\u0131k\xe7a belirtir|tasrih eder|vurgular]] ki \u015fu muhte\u015fem bur\xe7lar sahibi, [[s\xfcslenmi\u015f|m\xfczeyyen|]] [[k\xf6\u015fkler|kas\u0131rlar|saraylar]] h\xfckm\xfcnde olan [[g\xf6kler|semavat|]] dahi [[bilin\xe7 sahibi|z\xee\u015fuur|]] ve [[idrak sahipleri|zevi\u2019l-idrak|anlay\u0131\u015f sahibi varl\u0131klar]] mahluklarla doludur. Onlar dahi [[insan|ins|]] ve cin gibi \u015fu \xe2lem saray\u0131n\u0131n seyircileri ve \u015fu k\xe2inat kitab\u0131n\u0131n [[okuyucular\u0131|m\xfctalaac\u0131lar\u0131|dikkatle inceleyenleri]] ve \u015fu [[Rabl\u0131k saltanat\u0131n\u0131n|saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin|Allah\'\u0131n terbiye ve idare edicilik egemenli\u011finin]] [[duyurucular\u0131d\u0131r|dell\xe2llar\u0131d\u0131rlar|ilanc\u0131lar\u0131d\u0131r]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc k\xe2inat\u0131, [[say\u0131s\u0131z|hadd \xfc hesaba gelmeyen|s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z]] [[s\xfcslemeler|tezyinat|]] ve [[g\xfczellikler|mehasin|]] ve [[nak\u0131\u015flar|nuku\u015f|i\u015flemeler]] ile s\xfcslendirip [[s\xfcslemesi|tezyin etmesi|]], [[apa\xe7\u0131k|bilbedahe|besbelli]] [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen|m\xfctefekkir|]] [[be\u011fenen|istihsan edici|g\xfczel bulan]] ve [[hayran kalan|m\xfctehayyir|]] takdir edicilerin [[bak\u0131\u015flar\u0131n\u0131|enzar\u0131n\u0131|]] ister.\\n\\nEvet, [[g\xfczellik|h\xfcs\xfcn|]] elbette bir \xe2\u015f\u0131k ister; [[yemek|taam|]] ise a\xe7 olana verilir. Halbuki [[insan|ins|]] ve cin, \u015fu nihayetsiz vazifeye, \u015fu [[g\xf6rkemli|ha\u015fmetli|heybetli]] [[g\xf6zetimine|nezarete|seyircili\u011fine]] ve \u015fu [[geni\u015f|v\xfcs\u2019atli|]] [[kullu\u011fa|ubudiyete|]] kar\u015f\u0131 milyondan birisini ancak yapabilir. Demek bu nihayetsiz ve [[\xe7e\u015fitli|m\xfctenevvi|]] [[vazifelere|vezaife|]] ve [[ibadetlere|ibadata|]], nihayetsiz [[melek|melaike|]] [[t\xfcrleri|enva\u0131|nevileri]] ve [[ruhaniler|ruhaniyat|]] [[cinsleri|ecnas\u0131|]] l\xe2z\u0131md\u0131r.\\n\\nBaz\u0131 [[rivayetlerin|rivayat\u0131n|Peygamberden nakledilen s\xf6zlerin]] [[i\u015faretleriyle|i\u015farat\u0131yla|]] ve [[\xe2lemin d\xfczeninin|intizam-\u0131 \xe2lemin|]] [[gayesiyle|hikmetiyle|anlaml\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla]] denilebilir ki bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[gezici cisimler|ecsam-\u0131 seyyare|]], [[gezegenlerden|seyyarattan|]] tut, t\xe2 [[damlalara|katarata|]] kadar bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[meleklerin|melaikenin|]] [[binekleridir|merakibidirler|]]. Onlar bunlara [[Allah\'\u0131n izni|izn-i \u0130lah\xee|]] ile binerler, [[g\xf6r\xfcnen \xe2lemi|\xe2lem-i \u015fehadeti|maddi d\xfcnyay\u0131]] seyredip gezerler. Hem denilebilir ki bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[hayvansal cisimler|ecsam-\u0131 hayvaniye|]], had\xeeste \u201c[[Ye\u015fil Ku\u015flar|Tuy\xfbrun Hudrun|]]\u201d [[isimlendirilen|tesmiye edilen|]] cennet ku\u015flar\u0131ndan tut, t\xe2 sineklere kadar bir cins [[ruhlar\u0131n|ervah\u0131n|]] [[u\xe7aklar\u0131d\u0131r|tayyareleridirler|]]. Onlar, bunlar\u0131n i\xe7ine [[Hakk\'\u0131n emri|emr-i Hak|Allah\'\u0131n emri]] ile girerler, [[cisimler \xe2lemini|\xe2lem-i cismaniyat\u0131|maddi alemi]] [[gezip|seyran edip|]] o cesetlerdeki [[duyular\u0131n|h\xe2sselerin|]] pencereleriyle [[bedensel|cisman\xee|maddi]] [[yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f mucizelerini|mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 f\u0131trat\u0131|]] [[izlerler|tema\u015fa ederler|seyrederler]].\\n\\nElbette [[yo\u011fun|kesafetli|kat\u0131, maddeci]] topraktan ve [[bulan\u0131k|k\xfcd\xfbretli|]] sudan [[s\xfcrekli|m\xfctemadiyen|]] [[ho\u015f|letafetli|ince, latif]] hayat\u0131 ve [[nurlu|nuraniyetli|ayd\u0131nl\u0131k]] [[idrak sahiplerini|zevi\u2019l-idraki|anlay\u0131\u015f sahiplerini]] [[yaratan|halk eden|]] [[Yarat\u0131c\u0131\'n\u0131n|H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131n|]], elbette ruha ve hayata [[uygun|m\xfcnasip|]] \u015fu nur denizinden ve hatt\xe2 [[karanl\u0131k|zulmet|]] [[denizinden|bahrinden|]] bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[bilin\xe7 sahibi|z\xee\u015fuur|]] mahluklar\u0131 vard\u0131r. Hem \xe7ok [[\xe7oklukla|kesretli|bol miktarda]] olarak vard\u0131r. [[Melekler|Melaike|]] ve [[ruhanilerin|ruhaniyat\u0131n|]] [[varl\u0131klar\u0131na|v\xfccudlar\u0131na|]] dair \u201cNokta\u201d nam\u0131nda bir [[k\xfc\xe7\xfck kitab\u0131mda|risalemde|]] ve Yirmi Dokuzuncu S\xf6z\u2019de iki kere iki d\xf6rt eder derecesinde bir [[kesinlikle|kat\u2019iyetle|]] [[kan\u0131tlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r|ispat edilmi\u015ftir|]]. E\u011fer istersen ona [[ba\u015fvur|m\xfcracaat et|]].\\n\\n\u0130kinci Basamak: Zemin ile g\xf6kler, bir h\xfck\xfbmetin iki memleketi gibi birbirine [[ilgilidirler|al\xe2kadard\u0131rlar|ba\u011flant\u0131l\u0131d\u0131rlar]]. Ortalar\u0131nda [[\xf6nemli|ehemmiyetli|]] [[ba\u011flant\u0131|irtibat|]] ve [[\xf6nemli|m\xfchim|]] [[ili\u015fkiler|muameleler|i\u015flemler]] vard\u0131r. Zemine l\xe2z\u0131m olan [[\u0131\u015f\u0131k|ziya|]], [[s\u0131cakl\u0131k|hararet|]] ve bereket ve rahmet gibi \u015feyler semadan geliyor, yani g\xf6nderiliyor. [[Allah\'\u0131n bildirmesine|Vahye|]] [[dayanan|istinad eden|]] b\xfct\xfcn [[semavi dinlerin|edyan-\u0131 semaviyenin|ilahi dinlerin]] [[fikir birli\u011fi|icma\u0131|]] ile ve [[g\xf6rmeye|\u015fuhuda|manevi m\xfc\u015fahedeye]] [[dayanan|istinad eden|]] b\xfct\xfcn [[ke\u015fif ehlinin|ehl-i ke\u015ffin|manevi gizlilikleri g\xf6ren velilerin]] [[g\xfc\xe7l\xfc haberleriyle|tevat\xfcr\xfcyle|yalan \xfczere birle\u015fmesi imkans\u0131z topluluk haberiyle]] [[melekler|melaike|]] ve [[ruhlar|ervah|]], semadan zemine geliyorlar.\\n\\nBundan, [[duyuya|hisse|]] [[yak\u0131n|karib|]] bir [[kesin sezgi|hads-i kat\u2019\xee|]] ile bilinir ki [[yery\xfcz\xfc sakinleri|sekene-i arz|]] i\xe7in semaya \xe7\u0131kmak i\xe7in bir yol vard\u0131r. Evet, nas\u0131l herkesin ak\u0131l ve hayal ve [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131|nazar\u0131|]] her vakit semaya gider. \xd6yle de a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 b\u0131rakan [[peygamberlerin ruhlar\u0131|ervah-\u0131 enbiya|]] ve [[veliler|evliya|ermi\u015fler]] veya cesetlerini \xe7\u0131karan [[\xf6l\xfclerin ruhlar\u0131|ervah-\u0131 emvat|]], [[Allah\'\u0131n izni|izn-i \u0130lah\xee|]] ile oraya giderler. Madem [[hafiflik|hiffet|]] ve [[incelik|letafet|ho\u015fluk]] bulanlar oraya giderler. Elbette [[misal\xee ceset|cesed-i misal\xee|ruhsal, latif beden]] giyen ve [[ruhlar|ervah|]] gibi hafif ve [[ince|lat\xeef|cismani olmayan]] bir k\u0131s\u0131m [[yer sakinleri|sekene-i arz|]] ve hava, semaya gidebilirler.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc Basamak: Seman\u0131n [[suskunlu\u011fu|s\xfck\xfbt|sessizli\u011fi]] ve [[durgunlu\u011fu|s\xfck\xfbneti|huzuru]] ve [[d\xfczen|intizam|]] ve [[s\xfcregenli\u011fi|\u0131tt\u0131rad\u0131|d\xfczenli ak\u0131\u015f\u0131]] ve [[geni\u015flik|v\xfcs\u2019at|]] ve [[parlakl\u0131\u011f\u0131|nuraniyeti|ayd\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131]] g\xf6sterir ki [[sakinleri|sekenesi|]], zeminin [[sakinleri|sekenesi|]] gibi de\u011filler; belki b\xfct\xfcn ahalisi [[itaatkard\u0131rlar|mut\xeedirler|]]. Ne [[emredilse|emrolunsa|]] onu i\u015flerler. [[s\u0131k\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131k|M\xfczahame|birbirine zahmet verme, iti\u015f kak\u0131\u015f]] ve [[tart\u0131\u015fmay\u0131|m\xfcnaka\u015fay\u0131|\xe7eki\u015fmeyi]] [[gerektirecek|icab edecek|]] bir sebep yoktur. Zira memleket geni\u015f, [[yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015flar\u0131|f\u0131tratlar\u0131|]] [[temiz|safi|saf]], kendileri masum, makamlar\u0131 sabittir.","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.21-19:13","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"},{"pageId":2,"rawText":"Evet, zeminde ezdad i\xe7tima etmi\u015f, e\u015frar ahyara kar\u0131\u015fm\u0131\u015f, i\xe7lerinde m\xfcnaka\u015fat ba\u015flam\u0131\u015f; o sebepten ihtilafat ve \u0131zd\u0131rabat d\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f ve ondan imtihanat ve m\xfcsabakat teklif edilmi\u015f ve ondan terakkiyat ve tedenniyat \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015f. \u015eu hakikatin hikmeti \u015fudur ki:\\n\\nBe\u015fer, \u015fecere-i hilkatin en son c\xfcz\xfc olan meyvesidir. Mal\xfbmdur ki bir \u015feyin semeresi en uzak en cem\u2019iyetli en nazik en ehemmiyetli c\xfcz\xfcd\xfcr. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7in semere-i \xe2lem olan insan en c\xe2mi\u2019 en bed\xee\u2019 en \xe2ciz en zay\u0131f ve en lat\xeef bir mu\u2019cize-i kudret oldu\u011fundan, be\u015fi\u011fi ve meskeni olan zemin, \xe2sumana nisbeten maddeten k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle ve hakaretiyle beraber manen ve sanaten b\xfct\xfcn k\xe2inat\u0131n kalbi, merkezi, b\xfct\xfcn mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 sanat\u0131n me\u015fheri, sergisi ve b\xfct\xfcn tecelliyat-\u0131 esmas\u0131n\u0131n mazhar\u0131, nokta-i mihrak\u0131yesi ve nihayetsiz faaliyet-i Rabbaniyenin mah\u015feri ve ma\u2019kesi ve hadsiz hallak\u0131yet-i \u0130lahiyenin, hususan nebatat ve hayvanat\u0131n kesretli enva-\u0131 sa\u011firesinde cevvadane icad\u0131n medar ve \xe7ar\u015f\u0131s\u0131 ve pek geni\u015f \xe2hiret \xe2lemlerindeki masnuat\u0131n k\xfc\xe7\xfck mikyasta numuneg\xe2h\u0131 ve mensucat-\u0131 ebediyenin s\xfcratle i\u015fleyen tezg\xe2h\u0131 ve menaz\u0131r-\u0131 sermediyenin s\xfcratle de\u011fi\u015fen taklitg\xe2h\u0131 ve besatin-i daimenin tohumcuklar\u0131na s\xfcratle s\xfcmb\xfcllenen dar ve muvakkat mezraas\u0131 ve terbiyeg\xe2h\u0131 olmu\u015ftur.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte arz\u0131n (H\xe2\u015fiye[1]) bu azamet-i maneviyesinden ve ehemmiyet-i san\u2019aviyesindendir ki Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem, semavata nisbeten, b\xfcy\xfck bir a\u011fac\u0131n k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir meyvesi h\xfckm\xfcnde olan arz\u0131, b\xfct\xfcn semavata denk tutuyor. Onu bir kefede, b\xfct\xfcn semavat\u0131 bir kefede koyuyor. M\xfckerreren \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650 der.\\n\\nHem arz\u0131n \u015fu mezk\xfbr hikmetlerden ne\u015f\u2019et eden s\xfcratli tahavv\xfcl\xfc ve devaml\u0131 tagayy\xfcr\xfc iktiza eder ki sekenesi de ona g\xf6re mazhar-\u0131 tahavv\xfclat olsun. Hem \u015fu mahdud arz, hadsiz mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 kudrete mazhar oldu\u011fundand\u0131r ki en m\xfchim sekeneleri olan ins ve cinnin kuvalar\u0131na, sair z\xeehayatlar gibi f\u0131tr\xee bir had ve hulk\xee bir kay\u0131t konulmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in nihayetsiz terakki ve nihayetsiz tedenniye mazhar olmu\u015ftur. Enbiyadan, evliyadan tut, t\xe2 nemrutlara t\xe2 \u015feytanlara kadar uzun bir meydan-\u0131 imtihanlar\u0131 peyda olmu\u015ftur. Madem \xf6yledir, elbette firavunla\u015fm\u0131\u015f \u015feytanlar, hadsiz \u015feraretiyle semaya ve ehline ta\u015f atacaklar.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc Basamak: B\xfct\xfcn \xe2lemlerin Rabb\u2019i ve M\xfcdebbir\u2019i ve H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131 olan Zat-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal\u2019in, ahk\xe2mlar\u0131 ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131 pek \xe7ok namlar\u0131 ve unvanlar\u0131 ve esma-i h\xfcsnas\u0131 vard\u0131r. Mesela, Ashab-\u0131 Nebi saf\u0131nda k\xfcffara kar\u015f\u0131 muharebe etmek i\xe7in melaikeleri g\xf6ndermesini iktiza eden hangi isim ve unvan ise o isim ve unvan iktiza eder ki melaike ile \u015feyat\xeen ortas\u0131nda muharebe bulunsun ve ahyar-\u0131 semaviyy\xeen ve e\u015frar-\u0131 arz\xeen mabeynlerinde m\xfcbareze olsun. Evet, k\xfcffar\u0131n n\xfcfus ve enfaslar\u0131 kabza-i kudretinde olan Kad\xeer-i Z\xfclcelal, bir emir ile bir sayha ile onlar\u0131 mahvetmiyor. Rububiyet-i \xe2mme unvan\u0131yla, Hak\xeem ve M\xfcdebbir ismiyle bir meydan-\u0131 imtihan ve m\xfcbareze a\xe7\u0131yor.","oldText":"Evet, [[zeminde|yery\xfcz\xfcnde]] [[ezdad|z\u0131tlar|birbirine z\u0131t olan \u015feyler]] [[i\xe7tima etmi\u015f|toplanm\u0131\u015f/bir araya gelmi\u015f]], [[e\u015frar|k\xf6t\xfcler/\u015ferliler]] [[ahyara|hay\u0131rl\u0131lara/iyilere]] kar\u0131\u015fm\u0131\u015f, i\xe7lerinde [[m\xfcnaka\u015fat|tart\u0131\u015fmalar/\xe7eki\u015fmeler]] ba\u015flam\u0131\u015f; o sebepten [[ihtilafat|anla\u015fmazl\u0131klar/ayr\u0131l\u0131klar]] ve [[\u0131zd\u0131rabat|ac\u0131lar/s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131lar]] d\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f ve ondan [[imtihanat|imtihanlar/s\u0131navlar]] ve [[m\xfcsabakat|yar\u0131\u015fmalar]] [[teklif edilmi\u015f|\xf6nerilmi\u015f/sorumlu tutulmu\u015f]] ve ondan [[terakkiyat|ilerlemeler/y\xfckseli\u015fler]] ve [[tedenniyat|gerilemeler/al\xe7al\u0131\u015flar]] \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015f. \u015eu [[hakikatin|ger\xe7e\u011fin]] [[hikmeti|sebebi/gayesi]] \u015fudur ki:\\n\\n[[Be\u015fer|\u0130nsan/\u0130nsano\u011flu]], [[\u015fecere-i hilkatin|yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f a\u011fac\u0131n\u0131n]] en son [[c\xfcz\xfc|par\xe7as\u0131/k\u0131sm\u0131]] olan meyvesidir. [[Mal\xfbmdur|Bilinen bir ger\xe7ektir]] ki bir \u015feyin [[semeresi|meyvesi/sonucu]] en uzak en [[cem\u2019iyetli|kapsaml\u0131/bir\xe7ok \xf6zelli\u011fi toplayan]] en nazik en [[ehemmiyetli|\xf6nemli]] [[c\xfcz\xfcd\xfcr|par\xe7as\u0131d\u0131r]]. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7in [[semere-i \xe2lem|\xe2lemin meyvesi/evrenin sonucu]] olan insan en [[c\xe2mi\u2019|kapsaml\u0131/i\xe7ine alan]] en [[bed\xee\u2019|e\u015fsiz g\xfczel/\xf6rneksiz yarat\u0131lan]] en \xe2ciz en zay\u0131f ve en [[lat\xeef|ince/nazik/ho\u015f]] bir [[mu\u2019cize-i kudret|kudret mucizesi|Allah\'\u0131n g\xfc\xe7 ve iktidar\u0131n\u0131n ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc eseri]] oldu\u011fundan, be\u015fi\u011fi ve [[meskeni|evi/yerle\u015fim yeri]] olan [[zemin|yery\xfcz\xfc]], [[\xe2sumana|g\xf6ky\xfcz\xfcne]] [[nisbeten|k\u0131yasla/g\xf6re]] maddeten k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle ve [[hakaretiyle|k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle/de\u011fersizli\u011fiyle]] beraber manen ve sanaten b\xfct\xfcn k\xe2inat\u0131n kalbi, merkezi, b\xfct\xfcn [[mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 sanat\u0131n|sanat mucizelerinin]] [[me\u015fheri|te\u015fhir yeri/sergisi]], sergisi ve b\xfct\xfcn [[tecelliyat-\u0131 esmas\u0131n\u0131n|isimlerinin tecellilerinin/isimlerinin yans\u0131malar\u0131n\u0131n]] [[mazhar\u0131|g\xf6r\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc yer/sahne oldu\u011fu yer]], [[nokta-i mihrak\u0131yesi|odak noktas\u0131]] ve [[nihayetsiz|sonsuz]] [[faaliyet-i Rabbaniyenin|Rabbani faaliyetin/Allah\'\u0131n icraat\u0131n\u0131n]] [[mah\u015feri|toplanma yeri]] ve [[ma\u2019kesi|yans\u0131ma yeri/aynas\u0131]] ve [[hadsiz|s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z]] [[hallak\u0131yet-i \u0130lahiyenin|\u0130lahi yarat\u0131c\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131n/Allah\'\u0131n s\xfcrekli yaratmas\u0131n\u0131n]], hususan [[nebatat|bitkiler]] ve [[hayvanat\u0131n|hayvanlar\u0131n]] [[kesretli|\xe7oklu/bol]] [[enva-\u0131 sa\u011firesinde|k\xfc\xe7\xfck t\xfcrlerinde/\xe7e\u015fitlerinde]] [[cevvadane|c\xf6mert\xe7e]] [[icad\u0131n|yaratman\u0131n/var etmenin]] [[medar|dayanak/kaynak]] ve \xe7ar\u015f\u0131s\u0131 ve pek geni\u015f \xe2hiret \xe2lemlerindeki [[masnuat\u0131n|sanatl\u0131 eserlerin]] k\xfc\xe7\xfck [[mikyasta|\xf6l\xe7ekte]] [[numuneg\xe2h\u0131|numune yeri/\xf6rneklerin sergilendi\u011fi yer]] ve [[mensucat-\u0131 ebediyenin|sonsuzluk dokumalar\u0131n\u0131n]] s\xfcratle i\u015fleyen tezg\xe2h\u0131 ve [[menaz\u0131r-\u0131 sermediyenin|sonsuz manzaralar\u0131n]] s\xfcratle de\u011fi\u015fen [[taklitg\xe2h\u0131|taklit yeri/\xf6rne\u011finin yap\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 yer]] ve [[besatin-i daimenin|daimi bostanlar\u0131n/sonsuz bah\xe7elerin]] tohumcuklar\u0131na s\xfcratle [[s\xfcmb\xfcllenen|filizlenen/geli\u015fen]] dar ve [[muvakkat|ge\xe7ici]] [[mezraas\u0131|tarlas\u0131/ekim yeri]] ve [[terbiyeg\xe2h\u0131|terbiye yeri/e\u011fitim yeri]] olmu\u015ftur.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte [[arz\u0131n|yerin/d\xfcnyan\u0131n]] ([[H\xe2\u015fiye|Dipnot]][1]) bu [[azamet-i maneviyesinden|manevi b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcnden]] ve [[ehemmiyet-i san\u2019aviyesindendir|sanat y\xf6n\xfcnden \xf6nemindendir]] ki [[Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem|hikmetli Kur\'an]], [[semavata|g\xf6klere]] [[nisbeten|k\u0131yasla]], b\xfcy\xfck bir a\u011fac\u0131n k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir meyvesi h\xfckm\xfcnde olan [[arz\u0131|yeri]], b\xfct\xfcn [[semavata|g\xf6klere]] denk tutuyor. Onu bir kefede, b\xfct\xfcn [[semavat\u0131|g\xf6kleri]] bir kefede koyuyor. [[M\xfckerreren|Tekrar tekrar]] [[\u0631\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650|G\xf6klerin ve yerin Rabbi|Ra\'d 16, \u0130sr\xe2 102 vb.]] der.\\n\\nHem [[arz\u0131n|yerin]] \u015fu [[mezk\xfbr|zikredilen/an\u0131lan]] hikmetlerden [[ne\u015f\u2019et eden|do\u011fan/kaynaklanan]] s\xfcratli [[tahavv\xfcl\xfc|d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcm\xfc/ba\u015fkala\u015fmas\u0131]] ve devaml\u0131 [[tagayy\xfcr\xfc|de\u011fi\u015fimi]] [[iktiza eder|gerektirir]] ki [[sekenesi|sakinleri/oturanlar\u0131]] de ona g\xf6re [[mazhar-\u0131 tahavv\xfclat|d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcmlere sahne/de\u011fi\u015fimlere ayna]] olsun. Hem \u015fu [[mahdud|s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131/k\xfc\xe7\xfck]] [[arz|yer/d\xfcnya]], [[hadsiz|s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z/say\u0131s\u0131z]] [[mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 kudrete|kudret mucizelerine]] [[mazhar|sahne/ayna]] oldu\u011fundand\u0131r ki en m\xfchim [[sekeneleri|sakinleri]] olan [[ins ve cinnin|insanlar\u0131n ve cinlerin]] [[kuvalar\u0131na|kuvvetlerine/duygular\u0131na/yeteneklerine]], [[sair|di\u011fer]] [[z\xeehayatlar|canl\u0131lar/hayat sahipleri]] gibi [[f\u0131tr\xee|yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015ftan gelen/do\u011fal]] bir had ve [[hulk\xee|yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015fla ilgili]] bir kay\u0131t konulmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in [[nihayetsiz|sonsuz]] [[terakki|ilerleme/y\xfckselme]] ve [[nihayetsiz|sonsuz]] [[tedenniye|al\xe7almaya/gerilemeye]] [[mazhar|sahne/konu]] olmu\u015ftur. [[Enbiyadan|Peygamberlerden]], [[evliyadan|velilerden/Allah dostlar\u0131ndan]] tut, t\xe2 nemrutlara t\xe2 \u015feytanlara kadar uzun bir [[meydan-\u0131 imtihanlar\u0131|s\u0131nav meydanlar\u0131]] [[peyda olmu\u015ftur|ortaya \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015ft\u0131r/olu\u015fmu\u015ftur]]. Madem \xf6yledir, elbette firavunla\u015fm\u0131\u015f \u015feytanlar, [[hadsiz|s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z]] [[\u015feraretiyle|k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle/\u015ferlili\u011fiyle]] semaya ve ehline ta\u015f atacaklar.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc Basamak: B\xfct\xfcn \xe2lemlerin Rabb\u2019i ve [[M\xfcdebbir\u2019i|idare edeni/tedbir alan\u0131]] ve [[H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131|Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131]] olan [[Zat-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal\u2019in|b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck ve ha\u015fmet sahibi Zat\'\u0131n (Allah\'\u0131n)]], [[ahk\xe2mlar\u0131|h\xfck\xfcmleri]] ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131 pek \xe7ok namlar\u0131 ve unvanlar\u0131 ve [[esma-i h\xfcsnas\u0131|en g\xfczel isimleri]] vard\u0131r. Mesela, [[Ashab-\u0131 Nebi|Peygamberin arkada\u015flar\u0131/sahabeler]] saf\u0131nda [[k\xfcffara|k\xe2firlere/ink\xe2rc\u0131lara]] kar\u015f\u0131 [[muharebe etmek|sava\u015fmak]] i\xe7in melaikeleri g\xf6ndermesini [[iktiza eden|gerektiren]] hangi isim ve unvan ise o isim ve unvan [[iktiza eder|gerektirir]] ki melaike ile [[\u015feyat\xeen|\u015feytanlar]] ortas\u0131nda muharebe bulunsun ve [[ahyar-\u0131 semaviyy\xeen|g\xf6klerin hay\u0131rl\u0131lar\u0131/melekler]] ve [[e\u015frar-\u0131 arz\xeen|yerin \u015ferlileri/k\xf6t\xfcleri (\u015feytanlar ve k\xf6t\xfc cinler)]] [[mabeynlerinde|aralar\u0131nda]] [[m\xfcbareze|\xe7arp\u0131\u015fma/d\xfcello/m\xfccadele]] olsun. Evet, [[k\xfcffar\u0131n|k\xe2firlerin]] [[n\xfcfus|nefisleri/canlar\u0131]] ve [[enfaslar\u0131|nefesleri]] [[kabza-i kudretinde|kudret elinde/egemenli\u011finde]] olan [[Kad\xeer-i Z\xfclcelal|b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck sahibi ve her \u015feye g\xfcc\xfc yeten Allah]], bir emir ile bir [[sayha|ses/\xe7\u0131\u011fl\u0131k (ilahi ceza sesi)]] ile onlar\u0131 mahvetmiyor. [[Rububiyet-i \xe2mme|Genel rabl\u0131k/genel terbiye ve idare edicilik]] unvan\u0131yla, [[Hak\xeem|her i\u015fi hikmetli olan (Allah)]] ve [[M\xfcdebbir|her \u015feyi \xe7ekip \xe7eviren/idare eden (Allah)]] ismiyle bir [[meydan-\u0131 imtihan|s\u0131nav meydan\u0131]] ve [[m\xfcbareze|\xe7arp\u0131\u015fma/m\xfccadele]] a\xe7\u0131yor.","modernText":"Evet, [[yery\xfcz\xfcnde|zeminde|]] [[z\u0131tlar|ezdad|birbirine z\u0131t olan \u015feyler]] [[toplanm\u0131\u015f/bir araya gelmi\u015f|i\xe7tima etmi\u015f|]], [[k\xf6t\xfcler/\u015ferliler|e\u015frar|]] [[hay\u0131rl\u0131lara/iyilere|ahyara|]] kar\u0131\u015fm\u0131\u015f, i\xe7lerinde [[tart\u0131\u015fmalar/\xe7eki\u015fmeler|m\xfcnaka\u015fat|]] ba\u015flam\u0131\u015f; o sebepten [[anla\u015fmazl\u0131klar/ayr\u0131l\u0131klar|ihtilafat|]] ve [[ac\u0131lar/s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131lar|\u0131zd\u0131rabat|]] d\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f ve ondan [[imtihanlar/s\u0131navlar|imtihanat|]] ve [[yar\u0131\u015fmalar|m\xfcsabakat|]] [[\xf6nerilmi\u015f/sorumlu tutulmu\u015f|teklif edilmi\u015f|]] ve ondan [[ilerlemeler/y\xfckseli\u015fler|terakkiyat|]] ve [[gerilemeler/al\xe7al\u0131\u015flar|tedenniyat|]] \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015f. \u015eu [[ger\xe7e\u011fin|hakikatin|]] [[sebebi/gayesi|hikmeti|]] \u015fudur ki:\\n\\n[[\u0130nsan/\u0130nsano\u011flu|Be\u015fer|]], [[yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f a\u011fac\u0131n\u0131n|\u015fecere-i hilkatin|]] en son [[par\xe7as\u0131/k\u0131sm\u0131|c\xfcz\xfc|]] olan meyvesidir. [[Bilinen bir ger\xe7ektir|Mal\xfbmdur|]] ki bir \u015feyin [[meyvesi/sonucu|semeresi|]] en uzak en [[kapsaml\u0131/bir\xe7ok \xf6zelli\u011fi toplayan|cem\u2019iyetli|]] en nazik en [[\xf6nemli|ehemmiyetli|]] [[par\xe7as\u0131d\u0131r|c\xfcz\xfcd\xfcr|]]. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7in [[\xe2lemin meyvesi/evrenin sonucu|semere-i \xe2lem|]] olan insan en [[kapsaml\u0131/i\xe7ine alan|c\xe2mi\u2019|]] en [[e\u015fsiz g\xfczel/\xf6rneksiz yarat\u0131lan|bed\xee\u2019|]] en \xe2ciz en zay\u0131f ve en [[ince/nazik/ho\u015f|lat\xeef|]] bir [[kudret mucizesi|mu\u2019cize-i kudret|Allah\'\u0131n g\xfc\xe7 ve iktidar\u0131n\u0131n ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc eseri]] oldu\u011fundan, be\u015fi\u011fi ve [[evi/yerle\u015fim yeri|meskeni|]] olan [[yery\xfcz\xfc|zemin|]], [[g\xf6ky\xfcz\xfcne|\xe2sumana|]] [[k\u0131yasla/g\xf6re|nisbeten|]] maddeten k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle ve [[k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle/de\u011fersizli\u011fiyle|hakaretiyle|]] beraber manen ve sanaten b\xfct\xfcn k\xe2inat\u0131n kalbi, merkezi, b\xfct\xfcn [[sanat mucizelerinin|mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 sanat\u0131n|]] [[te\u015fhir yeri/sergisi|me\u015fheri|]], sergisi ve b\xfct\xfcn [[isimlerinin tecellilerinin/isimlerinin yans\u0131malar\u0131n\u0131n|tecelliyat-\u0131 esmas\u0131n\u0131n|]] [[g\xf6r\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc yer/sahne oldu\u011fu yer|mazhar\u0131|]], [[odak noktas\u0131|nokta-i mihrak\u0131yesi|]] ve [[sonsuz|nihayetsiz|]] [[Rabbani faaliyetin/Allah\'\u0131n icraat\u0131n\u0131n|faaliyet-i Rabbaniyenin|]] [[toplanma yeri|mah\u015feri|]] ve [[yans\u0131ma yeri/aynas\u0131|ma\u2019kesi|]] ve [[s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z|hadsiz|]] [[\u0130lahi yarat\u0131c\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131n/Allah\'\u0131n s\xfcrekli yaratmas\u0131n\u0131n|hallak\u0131yet-i \u0130lahiyenin|]], hususan [[bitkiler|nebatat|]] ve [[hayvanlar\u0131n|hayvanat\u0131n|]] [[\xe7oklu/bol|kesretli|]] [[k\xfc\xe7\xfck t\xfcrlerinde/\xe7e\u015fitlerinde|enva-\u0131 sa\u011firesinde|]] [[c\xf6mert\xe7e|cevvadane|]] [[yaratman\u0131n/var etmenin|icad\u0131n|]] [[dayanak/kaynak|medar|]] ve \xe7ar\u015f\u0131s\u0131 ve pek geni\u015f \xe2hiret \xe2lemlerindeki [[sanatl\u0131 eserlerin|masnuat\u0131n|]] k\xfc\xe7\xfck [[\xf6l\xe7ekte|mikyasta|]] [[numune yeri/\xf6rneklerin sergilendi\u011fi yer|numuneg\xe2h\u0131|]] ve [[sonsuzluk dokumalar\u0131n\u0131n|mensucat-\u0131 ebediyenin|]] s\xfcratle i\u015fleyen tezg\xe2h\u0131 ve [[sonsuz manzaralar\u0131n|menaz\u0131r-\u0131 sermediyenin|]] s\xfcratle de\u011fi\u015fen [[taklit yeri/\xf6rne\u011finin yap\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 yer|taklitg\xe2h\u0131|]] ve [[daimi bostanlar\u0131n/sonsuz bah\xe7elerin|besatin-i daimenin|]] tohumcuklar\u0131na s\xfcratle [[filizlenen/geli\u015fen|s\xfcmb\xfcllenen|]] dar ve [[ge\xe7ici|muvakkat|]] [[tarlas\u0131/ekim yeri|mezraas\u0131|]] ve [[terbiye yeri/e\u011fitim yeri|terbiyeg\xe2h\u0131|]] olmu\u015ftur.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte [[yerin/d\xfcnyan\u0131n|arz\u0131n|]] ([[Dipnot|H\xe2\u015fiye|]][1]) bu [[manevi b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcnden|azamet-i maneviyesinden|]] ve [[sanat y\xf6n\xfcnden \xf6nemindendir|ehemmiyet-i san\u2019aviyesindendir|]] ki [[hikmetli Kur\'an|Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem|]], [[g\xf6klere|semavata|]] [[k\u0131yasla|nisbeten|]], b\xfcy\xfck bir a\u011fac\u0131n k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir meyvesi h\xfckm\xfcnde olan [[yeri|arz\u0131|]], b\xfct\xfcn [[g\xf6klere|semavata|]] denk tutuyor. Onu bir kefede, b\xfct\xfcn [[g\xf6kleri|semavat\u0131|]] bir kefede koyuyor. [[Tekrar tekrar|M\xfckerreren|]] [[G\xf6klerin ve yerin Rabbi|\u0631\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650|Ra\'d 16, \u0130sr\xe2 102 vb.]] der.\\n\\nHem [[yerin|arz\u0131n|]] \u015fu [[zikredilen/an\u0131lan|mezk\xfbr|]] hikmetlerden [[do\u011fan/kaynaklanan|ne\u015f\u2019et eden|]] s\xfcratli [[d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcm\xfc/ba\u015fkala\u015fmas\u0131|tahavv\xfcl\xfc|]] ve devaml\u0131 [[de\u011fi\u015fimi|tagayy\xfcr\xfc|]] [[gerektirir|iktiza eder|]] ki [[sakinleri/oturanlar\u0131|sekenesi|]] de ona g\xf6re [[d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcmlere sahne/de\u011fi\u015fimlere ayna|mazhar-\u0131 tahavv\xfclat|]] olsun. Hem \u015fu [[s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131/k\xfc\xe7\xfck|mahdud|]] [[yer/d\xfcnya|arz|]], [[s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z/say\u0131s\u0131z|hadsiz|]] [[kudret mucizelerine|mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 kudrete|]] [[sahne/ayna|mazhar|]] oldu\u011fundand\u0131r ki en m\xfchim [[sakinleri|sekeneleri|]] olan [[insanlar\u0131n ve cinlerin|ins ve cinnin|]] [[kuvvetlerine/duygular\u0131na/yeteneklerine|kuvalar\u0131na|]], [[di\u011fer|sair|]] [[canl\u0131lar/hayat sahipleri|z\xeehayatlar|]] gibi [[yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015ftan gelen/do\u011fal|f\u0131tr\xee|]] bir had ve [[yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015fla ilgili|hulk\xee|]] bir kay\u0131t konulmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in [[sonsuz|nihayetsiz|]] [[ilerleme/y\xfckselme|terakki|]] ve [[sonsuz|nihayetsiz|]] [[al\xe7almaya/gerilemeye|tedenniye|]] [[sahne/konu|mazhar|]] olmu\u015ftur. [[Peygamberlerden|Enbiyadan|]], [[velilerden/Allah dostlar\u0131ndan|evliyadan|]] tut, t\xe2 nemrutlara t\xe2 \u015feytanlara kadar uzun bir [[s\u0131nav meydanlar\u0131|meydan-\u0131 imtihanlar\u0131|]] [[ortaya \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015ft\u0131r/olu\u015fmu\u015ftur|peyda olmu\u015ftur|]]. Madem \xf6yledir, elbette firavunla\u015fm\u0131\u015f \u015feytanlar, [[s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z|hadsiz|]] [[k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle/\u015ferlili\u011fiyle|\u015feraretiyle|]] semaya ve ehline ta\u015f atacaklar.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc Basamak: B\xfct\xfcn \xe2lemlerin Rabb\u2019i ve [[idare edeni/tedbir alan\u0131|M\xfcdebbir\u2019i|]] ve [[Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131|H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131|]] olan [[b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck ve ha\u015fmet sahibi Zat\'\u0131n (Allah\'\u0131n)|Zat-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal\u2019in|]], [[h\xfck\xfcmleri|ahk\xe2mlar\u0131|]] ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131 pek \xe7ok namlar\u0131 ve unvanlar\u0131 ve [[en g\xfczel isimleri|esma-i h\xfcsnas\u0131|]] vard\u0131r. Mesela, [[Peygamberin arkada\u015flar\u0131/sahabeler|Ashab-\u0131 Nebi|]] saf\u0131nda [[k\xe2firlere/ink\xe2rc\u0131lara|k\xfcffara|]] kar\u015f\u0131 [[sava\u015fmak|muharebe etmek|]] i\xe7in melaikeleri g\xf6ndermesini [[gerektiren|iktiza eden|]] hangi isim ve unvan ise o isim ve unvan [[gerektirir|iktiza eder|]] ki melaike ile [[\u015feytanlar|\u015feyat\xeen|]] ortas\u0131nda muharebe bulunsun ve [[g\xf6klerin hay\u0131rl\u0131lar\u0131/melekler|ahyar-\u0131 semaviyy\xeen|]] ve [[yerin \u015ferlileri/k\xf6t\xfcleri (\u015feytanlar ve k\xf6t\xfc cinler)|e\u015frar-\u0131 arz\xeen|]] [[aralar\u0131nda|mabeynlerinde|]] [[\xe7arp\u0131\u015fma/d\xfcello/m\xfccadele|m\xfcbareze|]] olsun. Evet, [[k\xe2firlerin|k\xfcffar\u0131n|]] [[nefisleri/canlar\u0131|n\xfcfus|]] ve [[nefesleri|enfaslar\u0131|]] [[kudret elinde/egemenli\u011finde|kabza-i kudretinde|]] olan [[b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck sahibi ve her \u015feye g\xfcc\xfc yeten Allah|Kad\xeer-i Z\xfclcelal|]], bir emir ile bir [[ses/\xe7\u0131\u011fl\u0131k (ilahi ceza sesi)|sayha|]] ile onlar\u0131 mahvetmiyor. [[Genel rabl\u0131k/genel terbiye ve idare edicilik|Rububiyet-i \xe2mme|]] unvan\u0131yla, [[her i\u015fi hikmetli olan (Allah)|Hak\xeem|]] ve [[her \u015feyi \xe7ekip \xe7eviren/idare eden (Allah)|M\xfcdebbir|]] ismiyle bir [[s\u0131nav meydan\u0131|meydan-\u0131 imtihan|]] ve [[\xe7arp\u0131\u015fma/m\xfccadele|m\xfcbareze|]] a\xe7\u0131yor.","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.21-19:13","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"},{"pageId":3,"rawText":"Temsilde hata olmas\u0131n, g\xf6r\xfcyoruz ki nas\u0131l ki bir padi\u015fah\u0131n daire-i h\xfck\xfbmeti itibar\u0131yla ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131 pek \xe7ok unvanlar\u0131, isimleri bulunur. Mesela, daire-i adliye onu \u201ch\xe2kim-i \xe2dil\u201d nam\u0131yla y\xe2d eder. Daire-i askeriye onu \u201ckumandan-\u0131 a\u2019zam\u201d nam\u0131yla bilir. Daire-i me\u015fihat onu \u201chalife\u201d ismiyle zikreder. Daire-i m\xfclkiye onu \u201csultan\u201d nam\u0131yla tan\u0131r. Mut\xee ahali ona \u201cmerhametk\xe2r padi\u015fah\u201d derler. \xc2si insanlar ona \u201ckahhar h\xe2kim\u201d derler. Daha bunlara k\u0131yas et. \u0130\u015fte baz\u0131 vakit oluyor ki b\xfct\xfcn ahali onun elinde olan o padi\u015fah-\u0131 \xe2l\xee; \xe2ciz, zelil bir \xe2siyi bir emir ile idam etmiyor. Belki \u201ch\xe2kim-i \xe2dil\u201d ismiyle onu mahkemeye g\xf6nderir. Hem muktedir hem sad\u0131k bir memurunu taltife liyakatini biliyor. Fakat hususi ilmiyle, hususi telefonuyla onu taltif etmiyor. Belki ha\u015fmet-i saltanat ve tedbir-i h\xfck\xfbmet unvan\u0131yla m\xfck\xe2fata istihkak\u0131n\u0131 te\u015fhir etmek i\xe7in bir meydan-\u0131 m\xfcsabaka a\xe7ar. Vezirine emreder, ahaliyi tema\u015faya davet eder. Bir istikbal-i siyas\xee yapt\u0131r\u0131r. Muhte\u015fem bir imtihan-\u0131 ulvi neticesinde, bir mecma-\u0131 \xe2l\xeede onu taltif eder, liyakatini ilan eder. Daha ba\u015fka cihetleri bunlara k\u0131yas et.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte \u0648\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062b\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0644\u0670\u0649 ezel ve ebed Sultan\u0131\u2019n\u0131n pek \xe7ok esma-i h\xfcsnas\u0131 vard\u0131r. Tecelliyat-\u0131 celaliye ve tezah\xfcrat-\u0131 cemaliye ile pek \xe7ok \u015fuunat\u0131 ve unvanlar\u0131 vard\u0131r. Nur ve zulmet, yaz ve k\u0131\u015f, cennet ve cehennemin v\xfccudunu iktiza eden isim ve unvan ve \u015fe\u2019n ise kanun-u tenas\xfcl, kanun-u m\xfcsabaka, kanun-u teav\xfcn gibi pek \xe7ok umum\xee kanunlar misill\xfc kanun-u m\xfcbarezenin dahi bir derece tamimini isterler. Kalp etraf\u0131ndaki ilhamat ve vesveselerin m\xfcbarezelerinden tut, t\xe2 sema \xe2fak\u0131nda melaike ve \u015feytanlar\u0131n m\xfcbarezesine kadar o kanunun \u015f\xfcmul\xfcn\xfc iktiza eder.\\n\\nBe\u015finci Basamak: Madem arzdan semaya gidip gelmek var. Semadan arza inip \xe7\u0131kmak oluyor. Ehemmiyetli levaz\u0131mat-\u0131 arziye, oradan g\xf6nderiliyor. Ve madem ervah-\u0131 tayyibeler semaya gidiyorlar. Elbette ervah-\u0131 hab\xeese dahi ahyar\u0131 takliden semavat memleketine gitmeye te\u015febb\xfcs edecekler. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc v\xfccudca letafet ve hiffetleri var. Hem \u015f\xfcphesiz tard ve reddedilecekler. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc mahiyet\xe7e \u015feraret ve n\xfchusetleri vard\u0131r.\\n\\nHem bil\xe2-\u015fek vel\xe2 \u015f\xfcphe, \u015fu muamele-i m\xfchimmenin ve \u015fu m\xfcbareze-i maneviyenin \xe2lem-i \u015fehadette bir al\xe2meti, bir i\u015fareti bulunacakt\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin hikmeti iktiza eder ki z\xee\u015fuur i\xe7in b\xe2husus en m\xfchim vazifesi m\xfc\u015fahede ve \u015fehadet ve dell\xe2ll\u0131k ve nezaret olan insan i\xe7in tasarrufat-\u0131 gaybiyenin m\xfchimlerine bir i\u015faret koysun, birer al\xe2met b\u0131raks\u0131n. Nas\u0131l ki nihayetsiz bahar mu\u2019cizat\u0131na ya\u011fmuru i\u015faret koymu\u015f ve hav\xe2r\u0131k-\u0131 sanat\u0131na esbab-\u0131 zahiriyeyi al\xe2met etmi\u015f. T\xe2 \xe2lem-i \u015fehadet ehlini i\u015fhad etsin. Belki o acib tema\u015faya, umum ehl-i semavat ve sekene-i arz\u0131n enzar-\u0131 dikkatlerini celbetsin. Yani o koca semavat\u0131, etraf\u0131nda n\xf6bettarlar dizilmi\u015f, bur\xe7lar\u0131 tezyin edilmi\u015f bir kale h\xfckm\xfcnde, bir \u015fehir suretinde g\xf6sterip ha\u015fmet-i rububiyetini tefekk\xfcr ettirsin.\\n\\nMadem \u015fu m\xfcbareze-i ulviyenin ilan\u0131, hikmeten l\xe2z\u0131md\u0131r. Elbette ona bir i\u015faret vard\u0131r. Halbuki h\xe2disat-\u0131 cevviye ve semaviye i\xe7inde \u015fu ilana m\xfcnasip hi\xe7bir h\xe2dise g\xf6r\xfcnm\xfcyor. Bundan daha ensebi yoktur. Zira y\xfcksek kalelerin muhkem bur\xe7lar\u0131ndan at\u0131lan manc\u0131n\u0131klar ve i\u015faret fi\u015feklerine benzeyen \u015fu h\xe2disat-\u0131 necmiye, bu recm-i \u015feytana ne kadar enseb d\xfc\u015ft\xfc\u011f\xfc bedaheten anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131r. Halbuki \u015fu h\xe2disenin, bu hikmetten ve \u015fu gayeden ba\u015fka ona m\xfcnasip bir hikmeti bilinmiyor. Sair h\xe2disat \xf6yle de\u011fil. Hem \u015fu hikmet, zaman-\u0131 \xc2dem\u2019den beri me\u015fhurdur ve ehl-i hakikat i\xe7in me\u015fhuddur.\\n\\nAlt\u0131nc\u0131 Basamak: Be\u015fer ve cin, nihayetsiz \u015ferre ve c\xfchuda m\xfcstaid olduklar\u0131ndan nihayetsiz bir temerr\xfcd ve bir tu\u011fyan yaparlar. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7in Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Ker\xeem, \xf6yle i\u2019cazk\xe2r bir bel\xe2gatla ve \xf6yle \xe2l\xee ve b\xe2hir \xfcsluplarla ve \xf6yle g\xe2l\xee ve zahir temsiller ve mesellerle ins ve cinni isyandan ve tu\u011fyandan zecreder ki k\xe2inat\u0131 titretir. Mesela:","oldText":"[[Temsilde|Benzetmede]] hata olmas\u0131n, g\xf6r\xfcyoruz ki nas\u0131l ki bir padi\u015fah\u0131n [[daire-i h\xfck\xfbmeti|h\xfck\xfcmet dairesi|devlet idaresi alan\u0131]] [[itibar\u0131yla|bak\u0131m\u0131ndan]] ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131 pek \xe7ok unvanlar\u0131, isimleri bulunur. Mesela, [[daire-i adliye|adalet dairesi]] onu \u201c[[h\xe2kim-i \xe2dil|adaletli hakim]]\u201d [[nam\u0131yla|ad\u0131yla|\xfcnvan\u0131yla]] [[y\xe2d eder|anar]]. [[Daire-i askeriye|Askeriye dairesi]] onu \u201c[[kumandan-\u0131 a\u2019zam|ba\u015fkomutan|en b\xfcy\xfck komutan]]\u201d [[nam\u0131yla|\xfcnvan\u0131yla]] bilir. [[Daire-i me\u015fihat|\u015eeyh\xfclislaml\u0131k makam\u0131|Dini i\u015fler dairesi]] onu \u201chalife\u201d ismiyle [[zikreder|anar|s\xf6yler]]. [[Daire-i m\xfclkiye|M\xfclki idare dairesi|Sivil y\xf6netim]] onu \u201csultan\u201d [[nam\u0131yla|\xfcnvan\u0131yla]] tan\u0131r. [[Mut\xee|\u0130taat eden]] ahali ona \u201c[[merhametk\xe2r|merhametli]] padi\u015fah\u201d derler. \xc2si insanlar ona \u201c[[kahhar|kahredici|ceza verici]] h\xe2kim\u201d derler. Daha bunlara k\u0131yas et. \u0130\u015fte baz\u0131 vakit oluyor ki b\xfct\xfcn ahali onun elinde olan o [[padi\u015fah-\u0131 \xe2l\xee|y\xfcce padi\u015fah]]; \xe2ciz, [[zelil|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131k|al\xe7ak]] bir [[\xe2siyi|isyanc\u0131y\u0131]] bir emir ile idam etmiyor. Belki \u201c[[h\xe2kim-i \xe2dil|adaletli hakim]]\u201d ismiyle onu mahkemeye g\xf6nderir. Hem [[muktedir|g\xfcc\xfc yeten|iktidarl\u0131]] hem [[sad\u0131k|ba\u011fl\u0131|do\u011fru]] bir memurunu [[taltife|\xf6d\xfcllendirmeye|iltifat etmeye]] [[liyakatini|lay\u0131k olu\u015funu]] biliyor. Fakat [[hususi|\xf6zel]] ilmiyle, [[hususi|\xf6zel]] telefonuyla onu [[taltif etmiyor|\xf6d\xfcllendirmiyor]]; Belki [[ha\u015fmet-i saltanat|saltanat\u0131n g\xf6rkemi]] ve [[tedbir-i h\xfck\xfbmet|h\xfck\xfcmet idaresi|y\xf6netim tedbiri]] unvan\u0131yla [[m\xfck\xe2fata|\xf6d\xfcle]] [[istihkak\u0131n\u0131|hak edi\u015fini]] [[te\u015fhir etmek i\xe7in|sergilemek i\xe7in|herkese g\xf6stermek i\xe7in]] bir [[meydan-\u0131 m\xfcsabaka|yar\u0131\u015fma meydan\u0131]] a\xe7ar. Vezirine emreder, ahaliyi [[tema\u015faya|izlemeye|seyre]] davet eder. Bir [[istikbal-i siyas\xee|siyasi kar\u015f\u0131lama t\xf6reni]] yapt\u0131r\u0131r. Muhte\u015fem bir [[imtihan-\u0131 ulvi|y\xfcce imtihan]] neticesinde, bir [[mecma-\u0131 \xe2l\xeede|y\xfcce toplulukta]] onu [[taltif eder|\xf6d\xfcllendirir]], [[liyakatini|lay\u0131k oldu\u011funu]] [[ilan eder|duyurur]]. Daha ba\u015fka [[cihetleri|y\xf6nleri]] bunlara k\u0131yas et.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte [[\u0648\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062b\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0644\u0670\u0649|En y\xfcce misal Allah\'\u0131nd\u0131r (Nahl, 16/60)]] [[ezel|ba\u015flang\u0131c\u0131 olmayan ge\xe7mi\u015f]] ve [[ebed|sonu olmayan gelecek]] Sultan\u0131\u2019n\u0131n pek \xe7ok [[esma-i h\xfcsnas\u0131|g\xfczel isimleri]] vard\u0131r. [[Tecelliyat-\u0131 celaliye|Celal isminin yans\u0131malar\u0131|B\xfcy\xfckl\xfck ve ha\u015fmetinin g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcmleri]] ve [[tezah\xfcrat-\u0131 cemaliye|Cemal isminin belirmeleri|G\xfczellik ve l\xfctfunun ortaya \xe7\u0131kmalar\u0131]] ile pek \xe7ok [[\u015fuunat\u0131|i\u015fleri|halleri, icraatlar\u0131]] ve unvanlar\u0131 vard\u0131r. Nur ve [[zulmet|karanl\u0131k]], yaz ve k\u0131\u015f, cennet ve cehennemin [[v\xfccudunu|varl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131]] [[iktiza eden|gerektiren]] isim ve unvan ve [[\u015fe\u2019n|i\u015f|hal, \xf6zellik]] ise [[kanun-u tenas\xfcl|\xfcreme kanunu]], [[kanun-u m\xfcsabaka|yar\u0131\u015fma kanunu]], [[kanun-u teav\xfcn|yard\u0131mla\u015fma kanunu]] gibi pek \xe7ok [[umum\xee|genel]] kanunlar [[misill\xfc|gibi|benzeri]] [[kanun-u m\xfcbarezenin|m\xfccadele kanununun|\xe7arp\u0131\u015fma yasas\u0131n\u0131n]] dahi bir derece [[tamimini|genelle\u015ftirilmesini|yayg\u0131nla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131]] isterler. Kalp etraf\u0131ndaki [[ilhamat|ilhamlar]] ve vesveselerin [[m\xfcbarezelerinden|\xe7arp\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131ndan|m\xfccadelelerinden]] tut, t\xe2 sema [[\xe2fak\u0131nda|ufuklar\u0131nda]] [[melaike|melekler]] ve \u015feytanlar\u0131n [[m\xfcbarezesine|\xe7arp\u0131\u015fmas\u0131na|m\xfccadelesine]] kadar o kanunun [[\u015f\xfcmul\xfcn\xfc|kapsam\u0131n\u0131|i\xe7ine almas\u0131n\u0131]] [[iktiza eder|gerektirir]].\\n\\nBe\u015finci Basamak: Madem [[arzdan|yerden|d\xfcnyadan]] semaya gidip gelmek var. Semadan [[arza|yere]] inip \xe7\u0131kmak oluyor. [[Ehemmiyetli|\xd6nemli]] [[levaz\u0131mat-\u0131 arziye|yery\xfcz\xfc ihtiya\xe7lar\u0131|d\xfcnya malzemeleri]], oradan g\xf6nderiliyor. Ve madem [[ervah-\u0131 tayyibeler|temiz ruhlar]] semaya gidiyorlar. Elbette [[ervah-\u0131 hab\xeese|k\xf6t\xfc ruhlar|pis ruhlar]] dahi [[ahyar\u0131|hay\u0131rl\u0131lar\u0131|iyileri]] [[takliden|taklit ederek]] [[semavat|g\xf6kler]] memleketine gitmeye [[te\u015febb\xfcs edecekler|giri\u015fecekler]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[v\xfccudca|bedence|yap\u0131ca]] [[letafet|incelik|ho\u015fluk]] ve [[hiffetleri|hafiflikleri]] var. Hem \u015f\xfcphesiz [[tard|kovulma]] ve reddedilecekler. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[mahiyet\xe7e|nitelik\xe7e|i\xe7y\xfcz\xfc itibar\u0131yla]] [[\u015feraret|k\xf6t\xfcl\xfck|haylazl\u0131k]] ve [[n\xfchusetleri|u\u011fursuzluklar\u0131|pislikleri]] vard\u0131r.\\n\\nHem [[bil\xe2-\u015fek vel\xe2 \u015f\xfcphe|\u015feksiz ve \u015f\xfcphesiz]] , \u015fu [[muamele-i m\xfchimmenin|\xf6nemli i\u015flemin|\xf6nemli ili\u015fkinin]] ve \u015fu [[m\xfcbareze-i maneviyenin|manevi \xe7arp\u0131\u015fman\u0131n|manevi m\xfccadelenin]] [[\xe2lem-i \u015fehadette|g\xf6r\xfcnen d\xfcnyada|maddi \xe2lemde]] bir [[al\xe2meti|belirtisi]], bir i\u015fareti bulunacakt\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin|Rabl\u0131k saltanat\u0131n\u0131n|Allah\'\u0131n terbiye ve idare edicilik egemenli\u011finin]] [[hikmeti|bilgeli\u011fi|gayesi]] [[iktiza eder|gerektirir]] ki [[z\xee\u015fuur|bilin\xe7 sahibi]] i\xe7in [[b\xe2husus|\xf6zellikle]] en m\xfchim vazifesi [[m\xfc\u015fahede|g\xf6zlem]] ve [[\u015fehadet|\u015fahitlik]] ve [[dell\xe2ll\u0131k|ilanc\u0131l\u0131k|duyuruculuk]] ve [[nezaret|g\xf6zetleme|seyircilik]] olan insan i\xe7in [[tasarrufat-\u0131 gaybiyenin|gizli icraatlar\u0131n|g\xf6r\xfcnmeyen tasarruflar\u0131n]] [[m\xfchimlerine|\xf6nemlilerine]] bir i\u015faret koysun, birer [[al\xe2met|belirti]] b\u0131raks\u0131n. Nas\u0131l ki nihayetsiz bahar [[mu\u2019cizat\u0131na|mucizelerine]] ya\u011fmuru i\u015faret koymu\u015f ve [[hav\xe2r\u0131k-\u0131 sanat\u0131na|sanat harikalar\u0131na]] [[esbab-\u0131 zahiriyeyi|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr sebepleri]] [[al\xe2met etmi\u015f|i\u015faret etmi\u015f]]. T\xe2 [[\xe2lem-i \u015fehadet|g\xf6r\xfcnen \xe2lem]] ehlini [[i\u015fhad etsin|\u015fahit tutsun]]. Belki o acib [[tema\u015faya|seyre|izlemeye]], [[umum|b\xfct\xfcn]] [[ehl-i semavat|g\xf6k ehli]] ve [[sekene-i arz\u0131n|yer sakinlerinin]] [[enzar-\u0131 dikkatlerini|dikkatli bak\u0131\u015flar\u0131n\u0131]] [[celbetsin|\xe7eksin]]. Yani o koca [[semavat\u0131|g\xf6kleri]], etraf\u0131nda n\xf6bettarlar dizilmi\u015f, bur\xe7lar\u0131 [[tezyin edilmi\u015f|s\xfcslenmi\u015f]] bir kale h\xfckm\xfcnde, bir \u015fehir suretinde g\xf6sterip [[ha\u015fmet-i rububiyetini|Rabl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131n g\xf6rkemini]] [[tefekk\xfcr ettirsin|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnd\xfcrs\xfcn]].\\n\\nMadem \u015fu [[m\xfcbareze-i ulviyenin|y\xfcce \xe7arp\u0131\u015fman\u0131n]] ilan\u0131, [[hikmeten|bilgelik gere\u011fi|ama\xe7 bak\u0131m\u0131ndan]] l\xe2z\u0131md\u0131r. Elbette ona bir i\u015faret vard\u0131r. Halbuki [[h\xe2disat-\u0131 cevviye|hava olaylar\u0131|atmosferik olaylar]] ve [[semaviye|g\xf6ksel]] i\xe7inde \u015fu ilana [[m\xfcnasip|uygun]] hi\xe7bir h\xe2dise g\xf6r\xfcnm\xfcyor. Bundan daha [[ensebi|uygunu]] yoktur. Zira y\xfcksek kalelerin [[muhkem|sa\u011flam]] bur\xe7lar\u0131ndan at\u0131lan manc\u0131n\u0131klar ve i\u015faret fi\u015feklerine benzeyen \u015fu [[h\xe2disat-\u0131 necmiye|y\u0131ld\u0131z olaylar\u0131|kayan y\u0131ld\u0131zlar]], bu [[recm-i \u015feytana|\u015feytan\u0131n ta\u015flanmas\u0131na]] ne kadar [[enseb|uygun]] d\xfc\u015ft\xfc\u011f\xfc [[bedaheten|apa\xe7\u0131k|hemen]] anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131r. Halbuki \u015fu h\xe2disenin, bu [[hikmetten|gayeden]] ve \u015fu gayeden ba\u015fka ona [[m\xfcnasip|uygun]] bir [[hikmeti|sebebi|anlam\u0131]] bilinmiyor. [[Sair|Di\u011fer]] [[h\xe2disat|olaylar]] \xf6yle de\u011fil. Hem \u015fu [[hikmet|gaye]], [[zaman-\u0131 \xc2dem\u2019den|Hz. Adem zaman\u0131ndan]] beri me\u015fhurdur ve [[ehl-i hakikat|hakikat ehli|ger\xe7e\u011fi bilenler]] i\xe7in [[me\u015fhuddur|g\xf6r\xfclmektedir|izlenmektedir]].\\n\\nAlt\u0131nc\u0131 Basamak: [[Be\u015fer|\u0130nsan]] ve cin, nihayetsiz \u015ferre ve [[c\xfchuda|inkara|inatla redde]] [[m\xfcstaid|yatk\u0131n|yetenekli]] olduklar\u0131ndan nihayetsiz bir [[temerr\xfcd|inat|dik kafal\u0131l\u0131k]] ve bir [[tu\u011fyan|azg\u0131nl\u0131k|ta\u015fk\u0131nl\u0131k]] yaparlar. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7in Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Ker\xeem, \xf6yle [[i\u2019cazk\xe2r|mucizeli|aciz b\u0131rakan]] bir [[bel\xe2gatla|s\xf6z ustal\u0131\u011f\u0131yla|etkili anlat\u0131mla]] ve \xf6yle [[\xe2l\xee|y\xfcce]] ve [[b\xe2hir|a\xe7\u0131k|parlak]] \xfcsluplarla ve \xf6yle [[g\xe2l\xee|y\xfcksek|k\u0131ymetli]] ve [[zahir|g\xf6r\xfcnen|a\xe7\u0131k]] temsiller ve mesellerle [[ins|insan]] ve cinni isyandan ve [[tu\u011fyandan|azg\u0131nl\u0131ktan]] [[zecreder|men eder|zorla vazge\xe7irir, sak\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131r]] ki k\xe2inat\u0131 titretir. Mesela:","modernText":"[[Benzetmede|Temsilde|]] hata olmas\u0131n, g\xf6r\xfcyoruz ki nas\u0131l ki bir padi\u015fah\u0131n [[h\xfck\xfcmet dairesi|daire-i h\xfck\xfbmeti|devlet idaresi alan\u0131]] [[bak\u0131m\u0131ndan|itibar\u0131yla|]] ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131 pek \xe7ok unvanlar\u0131, isimleri bulunur. Mesela, [[adalet dairesi|daire-i adliye|]] onu \u201c[[adaletli hakim|h\xe2kim-i \xe2dil|]]\u201d [[ad\u0131yla|nam\u0131yla|\xfcnvan\u0131yla]] [[anar|y\xe2d eder|]]. [[Askeriye dairesi|Daire-i askeriye|]] onu \u201c[[ba\u015fkomutan|kumandan-\u0131 a\u2019zam|en b\xfcy\xfck komutan]]\u201d [[\xfcnvan\u0131yla|nam\u0131yla|]] bilir. [[\u015eeyh\xfclislaml\u0131k makam\u0131|Daire-i me\u015fihat|Dini i\u015fler dairesi]] onu \u201chalife\u201d ismiyle [[anar|zikreder|s\xf6yler]]. [[M\xfclki idare dairesi|Daire-i m\xfclkiye|Sivil y\xf6netim]] onu \u201csultan\u201d [[\xfcnvan\u0131yla|nam\u0131yla|]] tan\u0131r. [[\u0130taat eden|Mut\xee|]] ahali ona \u201c[[merhametli|merhametk\xe2r|]] padi\u015fah\u201d derler. \xc2si insanlar ona \u201c[[kahredici|kahhar|ceza verici]] h\xe2kim\u201d derler. Daha bunlara k\u0131yas et. \u0130\u015fte baz\u0131 vakit oluyor ki b\xfct\xfcn ahali onun elinde olan o [[y\xfcce padi\u015fah|padi\u015fah-\u0131 \xe2l\xee|]]; \xe2ciz, [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131k|zelil|al\xe7ak]] bir [[isyanc\u0131y\u0131|\xe2siyi|]] bir emir ile idam etmiyor. Belki \u201c[[adaletli hakim|h\xe2kim-i \xe2dil|]]\u201d ismiyle onu mahkemeye g\xf6nderir. Hem [[g\xfcc\xfc yeten|muktedir|iktidarl\u0131]] hem [[ba\u011fl\u0131|sad\u0131k|do\u011fru]] bir memurunu [[\xf6d\xfcllendirmeye|taltife|iltifat etmeye]] [[lay\u0131k olu\u015funu|liyakatini|]] biliyor. Fakat [[\xf6zel|hususi|]] ilmiyle, [[\xf6zel|hususi|]] telefonuyla onu [[\xf6d\xfcllendirmiyor|taltif etmiyor|]]; Belki [[saltanat\u0131n g\xf6rkemi|ha\u015fmet-i saltanat|]] ve [[h\xfck\xfcmet idaresi|tedbir-i h\xfck\xfbmet|y\xf6netim tedbiri]] unvan\u0131yla [[\xf6d\xfcle|m\xfck\xe2fata|]] [[hak edi\u015fini|istihkak\u0131n\u0131|]] [[sergilemek i\xe7in|te\u015fhir etmek i\xe7in|herkese g\xf6stermek i\xe7in]] bir [[yar\u0131\u015fma meydan\u0131|meydan-\u0131 m\xfcsabaka|]] a\xe7ar. Vezirine emreder, ahaliyi [[izlemeye|tema\u015faya|seyre]] davet eder. Bir [[siyasi kar\u015f\u0131lama t\xf6reni|istikbal-i siyas\xee|]] yapt\u0131r\u0131r. Muhte\u015fem bir [[y\xfcce imtihan|imtihan-\u0131 ulvi|]] neticesinde, bir [[y\xfcce toplulukta|mecma-\u0131 \xe2l\xeede|]] onu [[\xf6d\xfcllendirir|taltif eder|]], [[lay\u0131k oldu\u011funu|liyakatini|]] [[duyurur|ilan eder|]]. Daha ba\u015fka [[y\xf6nleri|cihetleri|]] bunlara k\u0131yas et.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte [[En y\xfcce misal Allah\'\u0131nd\u0131r (Nahl, 16/60)|\u0648\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062b\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0644\u0670\u0649|]] [[ba\u015flang\u0131c\u0131 olmayan ge\xe7mi\u015f|ezel|]] ve [[sonu olmayan gelecek|ebed|]] Sultan\u0131\u2019n\u0131n pek \xe7ok [[g\xfczel isimleri|esma-i h\xfcsnas\u0131|]] vard\u0131r. [[Celal isminin yans\u0131malar\u0131|Tecelliyat-\u0131 celaliye|B\xfcy\xfckl\xfck ve ha\u015fmetinin g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcmleri]] ve [[Cemal isminin belirmeleri|tezah\xfcrat-\u0131 cemaliye|G\xfczellik ve l\xfctfunun ortaya \xe7\u0131kmalar\u0131]] ile pek \xe7ok [[i\u015fleri|\u015fuunat\u0131|halleri, icraatlar\u0131]] ve unvanlar\u0131 vard\u0131r. Nur ve [[karanl\u0131k|zulmet|]], yaz ve k\u0131\u015f, cennet ve cehennemin [[varl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131|v\xfccudunu|]] [[gerektiren|iktiza eden|]] isim ve unvan ve [[i\u015f|\u015fe\u2019n|hal, \xf6zellik]] ise [[\xfcreme kanunu|kanun-u tenas\xfcl|]], [[yar\u0131\u015fma kanunu|kanun-u m\xfcsabaka|]], [[yard\u0131mla\u015fma kanunu|kanun-u teav\xfcn|]] gibi pek \xe7ok [[genel|umum\xee|]] kanunlar [[gibi|misill\xfc|benzeri]] [[m\xfccadele kanununun|kanun-u m\xfcbarezenin|\xe7arp\u0131\u015fma yasas\u0131n\u0131n]] dahi bir derece [[genelle\u015ftirilmesini|tamimini|yayg\u0131nla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131]] isterler. Kalp etraf\u0131ndaki [[ilhamlar|ilhamat|]] ve vesveselerin [[\xe7arp\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131ndan|m\xfcbarezelerinden|m\xfccadelelerinden]] tut, t\xe2 sema [[ufuklar\u0131nda|\xe2fak\u0131nda|]] [[melekler|melaike|]] ve \u015feytanlar\u0131n [[\xe7arp\u0131\u015fmas\u0131na|m\xfcbarezesine|m\xfccadelesine]] kadar o kanunun [[kapsam\u0131n\u0131|\u015f\xfcmul\xfcn\xfc|i\xe7ine almas\u0131n\u0131]] [[gerektirir|iktiza eder|]].\\n\\nBe\u015finci Basamak: Madem [[yerden|arzdan|d\xfcnyadan]] semaya gidip gelmek var. Semadan [[yere|arza|]] inip \xe7\u0131kmak oluyor. [[\xd6nemli|Ehemmiyetli|]] [[yery\xfcz\xfc ihtiya\xe7lar\u0131|levaz\u0131mat-\u0131 arziye|d\xfcnya malzemeleri]], oradan g\xf6nderiliyor. Ve madem [[temiz ruhlar|ervah-\u0131 tayyibeler|]] semaya gidiyorlar. Elbette [[k\xf6t\xfc ruhlar|ervah-\u0131 hab\xeese|pis ruhlar]] dahi [[hay\u0131rl\u0131lar\u0131|ahyar\u0131|iyileri]] [[taklit ederek|takliden|]] [[g\xf6kler|semavat|]] memleketine gitmeye [[giri\u015fecekler|te\u015febb\xfcs edecekler|]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[bedence|v\xfccudca|yap\u0131ca]] [[incelik|letafet|ho\u015fluk]] ve [[hafiflikleri|hiffetleri|]] var. Hem \u015f\xfcphesiz [[kovulma|tard|]] ve reddedilecekler. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[nitelik\xe7e|mahiyet\xe7e|i\xe7y\xfcz\xfc itibar\u0131yla]] [[k\xf6t\xfcl\xfck|\u015feraret|haylazl\u0131k]] ve [[u\u011fursuzluklar\u0131|n\xfchusetleri|pislikleri]] vard\u0131r.\\n\\nHem [[\u015feksiz ve \u015f\xfcphesiz|bil\xe2-\u015fek vel\xe2 \u015f\xfcphe|]] , \u015fu [[\xf6nemli i\u015flemin|muamele-i m\xfchimmenin|\xf6nemli ili\u015fkinin]] ve \u015fu [[manevi \xe7arp\u0131\u015fman\u0131n|m\xfcbareze-i maneviyenin|manevi m\xfccadelenin]] [[g\xf6r\xfcnen d\xfcnyada|\xe2lem-i \u015fehadette|maddi \xe2lemde]] bir [[belirtisi|al\xe2meti|]], bir i\u015fareti bulunacakt\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[Rabl\u0131k saltanat\u0131n\u0131n|saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin|Allah\'\u0131n terbiye ve idare edicilik egemenli\u011finin]] [[bilgeli\u011fi|hikmeti|gayesi]] [[gerektirir|iktiza eder|]] ki [[bilin\xe7 sahibi|z\xee\u015fuur|]] i\xe7in [[\xf6zellikle|b\xe2husus|]] en m\xfchim vazifesi [[g\xf6zlem|m\xfc\u015fahede|]] ve [[\u015fahitlik|\u015fehadet|]] ve [[ilanc\u0131l\u0131k|dell\xe2ll\u0131k|duyuruculuk]] ve [[g\xf6zetleme|nezaret|seyircilik]] olan insan i\xe7in [[gizli icraatlar\u0131n|tasarrufat-\u0131 gaybiyenin|g\xf6r\xfcnmeyen tasarruflar\u0131n]] [[\xf6nemlilerine|m\xfchimlerine|]] bir i\u015faret koysun, birer [[belirti|al\xe2met|]] b\u0131raks\u0131n. Nas\u0131l ki nihayetsiz bahar [[mucizelerine|mu\u2019cizat\u0131na|]] ya\u011fmuru i\u015faret koymu\u015f ve [[sanat harikalar\u0131na|hav\xe2r\u0131k-\u0131 sanat\u0131na|]] [[g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr sebepleri|esbab-\u0131 zahiriyeyi|]] [[i\u015faret etmi\u015f|al\xe2met etmi\u015f|]]. T\xe2 [[g\xf6r\xfcnen \xe2lem|\xe2lem-i \u015fehadet|]] ehlini [[\u015fahit tutsun|i\u015fhad etsin|]]. Belki o acib [[seyre|tema\u015faya|izlemeye]], [[b\xfct\xfcn|umum|]] [[g\xf6k ehli|ehl-i semavat|]] ve [[yer sakinlerinin|sekene-i arz\u0131n|]] [[dikkatli bak\u0131\u015flar\u0131n\u0131|enzar-\u0131 dikkatlerini|]] [[\xe7eksin|celbetsin|]]. Yani o koca [[g\xf6kleri|semavat\u0131|]], etraf\u0131nda n\xf6bettarlar dizilmi\u015f, bur\xe7lar\u0131 [[s\xfcslenmi\u015f|tezyin edilmi\u015f|]] bir kale h\xfckm\xfcnde, bir \u015fehir suretinde g\xf6sterip [[Rabl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131n g\xf6rkemini|ha\u015fmet-i rububiyetini|]] [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnd\xfcrs\xfcn|tefekk\xfcr ettirsin|]].\\n\\nMadem \u015fu [[y\xfcce \xe7arp\u0131\u015fman\u0131n|m\xfcbareze-i ulviyenin|]] ilan\u0131, [[bilgelik gere\u011fi|hikmeten|ama\xe7 bak\u0131m\u0131ndan]] l\xe2z\u0131md\u0131r. Elbette ona bir i\u015faret vard\u0131r. Halbuki [[hava olaylar\u0131|h\xe2disat-\u0131 cevviye|atmosferik olaylar]] ve [[g\xf6ksel|semaviye|]] i\xe7inde \u015fu ilana [[uygun|m\xfcnasip|]] hi\xe7bir h\xe2dise g\xf6r\xfcnm\xfcyor. Bundan daha [[uygunu|ensebi|]] yoktur. Zira y\xfcksek kalelerin [[sa\u011flam|muhkem|]] bur\xe7lar\u0131ndan at\u0131lan manc\u0131n\u0131klar ve i\u015faret fi\u015feklerine benzeyen \u015fu [[y\u0131ld\u0131z olaylar\u0131|h\xe2disat-\u0131 necmiye|kayan y\u0131ld\u0131zlar]], bu [[\u015feytan\u0131n ta\u015flanmas\u0131na|recm-i \u015feytana|]] ne kadar [[uygun|enseb|]] d\xfc\u015ft\xfc\u011f\xfc [[apa\xe7\u0131k|bedaheten|hemen]] anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131r. Halbuki \u015fu h\xe2disenin, bu [[gayeden|hikmetten|]] ve \u015fu gayeden ba\u015fka ona [[uygun|m\xfcnasip|]] bir [[sebebi|hikmeti|anlam\u0131]] bilinmiyor. [[Di\u011fer|Sair|]] [[olaylar|h\xe2disat|]] \xf6yle de\u011fil. Hem \u015fu [[gaye|hikmet|]], [[Hz. Adem zaman\u0131ndan|zaman-\u0131 \xc2dem\u2019den|]] beri me\u015fhurdur ve [[hakikat ehli|ehl-i hakikat|ger\xe7e\u011fi bilenler]] i\xe7in [[g\xf6r\xfclmektedir|me\u015fhuddur|izlenmektedir]].\\n\\nAlt\u0131nc\u0131 Basamak: [[\u0130nsan|Be\u015fer|]] ve cin, nihayetsiz \u015ferre ve [[inkara|c\xfchuda|inatla redde]] [[yatk\u0131n|m\xfcstaid|yetenekli]] olduklar\u0131ndan nihayetsiz bir [[inat|temerr\xfcd|dik kafal\u0131l\u0131k]] ve bir [[azg\u0131nl\u0131k|tu\u011fyan|ta\u015fk\u0131nl\u0131k]] yaparlar. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7in Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Ker\xeem, \xf6yle [[mucizeli|i\u2019cazk\xe2r|aciz b\u0131rakan]] bir [[s\xf6z ustal\u0131\u011f\u0131yla|bel\xe2gatla|etkili anlat\u0131mla]] ve \xf6yle [[y\xfcce|\xe2l\xee|]] ve [[a\xe7\u0131k|b\xe2hir|parlak]] \xfcsluplarla ve \xf6yle [[y\xfcksek|g\xe2l\xee|k\u0131ymetli]] ve [[g\xf6r\xfcnen|zahir|a\xe7\u0131k]] temsiller ve mesellerle [[insan|ins|]] ve cinni isyandan ve [[azg\u0131nl\u0131ktan|tu\u011fyandan|]] [[men eder|zecreder|zorla vazge\xe7irir, sak\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131r]] ki k\xe2inat\u0131 titretir. Mesela:","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.21-19:15","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"},{"pageId":4,"rawText":"Ey ins ve cin! Emirlerime itaat etmezseniz haydi hudud-u m\xfclk\xfcmden elinizden gelirse \xe7\u0131k\u0131n\u0131z, meseline i\u015faret eden\\n\\n\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0634\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u0650\u0646\u0651\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0633\u064f\u0644\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064d \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0649\u0651\u0650 \u0627\u0670\u0644\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u0650\u0643\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064f\u0643\u064e\u0630\u0651\u0650\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u06de \u064a\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0634\u064f\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0638\u064c \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0648\u064e \u0646\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0635\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u06de\\n\\n\xe2yetindeki azametli inzara ve deh\u015fetli tehdide ve \u015fiddetli zecre dikkat et. Nas\u0131l, ins ve cinnin gayet ma\u011frurane temerr\xfcdlerini, gayet mu\u2019cizane bir bel\xe2gatla k\u0131rar. Aczlerini ilan eder. Saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin geni\u015fli\u011fi ve azameti nisbetinde ne kadar \xe2ciz ve b\xee\xe7are olduklar\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterir. G\xfcya \u015fu \xe2yetle hem \u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064f\u062c\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 \xe2yetiyle b\xf6yle diyor ki:\\n\\n\u201cEy hakareti i\xe7inde ma\u011frur ve m\xfctemerrid ve ey zaaf ve fakr\u0131 i\xe7inde serke\u015f ve muannid olan cin ve ins! Nas\u0131l cesaret edersiniz ki isyan\u0131n\u0131zla \xf6yle bir Sultan-\u0131 Z\xee\u015fan\u2019\u0131n evamirine kar\u015f\u0131 geliyorsunuz ki y\u0131ld\u0131zlar, aylar, g\xfcne\u015fler emirber neferleri gibi emirlerine itaat ederler. Hem tu\u011fyan\u0131n\u0131zla \xf6yle bir H\xe2kim-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019e kar\u015f\u0131 m\xfcbareze ediyorsunuz ki \xf6yle azametli mut\xee askerleri var, faraza \u015feytanlar\u0131n\u0131z dayanabilseler onlar\u0131 da\u011f gibi g\xfcllelerle recmedebilirler. Hem k\xfcfran\u0131n\u0131zla \xf6yle bir M\xe2lik-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019in memleketinde isyan ediyorsunuz ki ibad\u0131ndan ve c\xfcnudundan \xf6yleleri var ki de\u011fil sizin gibi k\xfc\xe7\xfcc\xfck \xe2ciz mahluklar\u0131, belki farz-\u0131 muhal olarak da\u011f ve arz b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcnde birer ad\xfcvv-\xfc k\xe2fir olsayd\u0131n\u0131z, arz ve da\u011f b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcnde y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131, ate\u015fli demirleri, \u015f\xfcvazl\u0131 n\xfchaslar\u0131 size atabilirler, sizi da\u011f\u0131t\u0131rlar. Hem \xf6yle bir kanunu k\u0131r\u0131yorsunuz ki o kanun ile \xf6yleler ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131r, e\u011fer l\xfczum olsa arz\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 y\xfcz\xfcn\xfcze \xe7arpar. G\xfclleler gibi k\xfcreniz misill\xfc y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131 \xfcst\xfcn\xfcze ya\u011fd\u0131rabilirler.\u201d\\n\\nEvet, Kur\u2019an\u2019da baz\u0131 m\xfchim tah\u015fidat vard\u0131r ki d\xfc\u015fmanlar\u0131n kuvvetli oldu\u011fundan ileri gelmiyor. Belki ha\u015fmetin izhar\u0131 ve d\xfc\u015fman \u015fenaatinin te\u015fhiri gibi sebeplerden ileri geliyor.\\n\\nHem bazen kemal-i intizam\u0131 ve nihayet-i adli ve gayet-i hilmi ve kuvvet-i hikmeti g\xf6stermek i\xe7in en b\xfcy\xfck ve kuvvetli esbab\u0131, en k\xfc\xe7\xfck ve zay\u0131f bir \u015feye kar\u015f\u0131 tah\u015fid eder ve \xfcst\xfcnde tutar; d\xfc\u015f\xfcrtmez, tecav\xfcz ettirmez. Mesela, \u015fu \xe2yete bak:\\n\\n\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064e\u0638\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e\u062c\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u062d\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0653\u0626\u0650\u0643\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0628\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0638\u064e\u0647\u0656\u064a\u0631\u064c\\n\\nNe kadar Nebi hakk\u0131na h\xfcrmet ve ne kadar ezvac\u0131n hukukuna merhamet var. \u015eu m\xfchim tah\u015fidat, yaln\u0131z h\xfcrmet-i Nebinin azametini ve iki za\xeefenin \u015fekvalar\u0131n\u0131n ehemmiyetini ve haklar\u0131n\u0131n riayetini rah\xeemane ifade etmek i\xe7indir.\\n\\nYedinci Basamak: Melekler ve semekler gibi y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131n dahi gayet muhtelif efradlar\u0131 vard\u0131r. Bir k\u0131sm\u0131 nihayet k\xfc\xe7\xfck, bir k\u0131sm\u0131 gayet b\xfcy\xfckt\xfcr. Hatt\xe2 g\xf6ky\xfcz\xfcnde her parlayana \u201cy\u0131ld\u0131z\u201d denilir. \u0130\u015fte bu y\u0131ld\u0131z cinsinden bir nev\u2019i de n\xe2zenin sema y\xfcz\xfcn\xfcn murassa ziynetleri ve o a\u011fac\u0131n m\xfcnevver meyveleri ve o denizin m\xfcsebbih bal\u0131klar\u0131 h\xfckm\xfcnde; F\xe2t\u0131r-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal, S\xe2ni\u2019-i Z\xfclcemal onlar\u0131 yaratm\u0131\u015f ve meleklerine mesireler, binekler, menziller yapm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Ve y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131n k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir nevini de \u015feyat\xeenin recmine \xe2let etmi\u015f. \u0130\u015fte bu recm-i \u015feyat\xeen i\xe7in at\u0131lan \u015fahaplar\u0131n \xfc\xe7 manas\u0131 olabilir:\\n\\nBirincisi: Kanun-u m\xfcbareze, en geni\u015f dairede dahi cereyan etti\u011fine remiz ve al\xe2mettir.\\n\\n\u0130kincisi: Semavatta h\xfc\u015fyar n\xf6bettarlar, mut\xee sekeneler var. Arzl\u0131 \u015ferirlerin ihtilat\u0131ndan ve istima\u2019lar\u0131ndan ho\u015flanmayan c\xfcnudullah bulundu\u011funa ilan ve i\u015farettir.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfcs\xfc: Muzahrefat-\u0131 arziyenin m\xfcmessil\xe2t-\u0131 hab\xeeseleri olan casus \u015feytanlar\u0131, temiz ve temizlerin meskeni olan semay\u0131 telvis etmemek ve n\xfcfus-u hab\xeese hesab\u0131na tecess\xfcs ettirmemek i\xe7in edepsiz casuslar\u0131 korkutmak i\xe7in at\u0131lan manc\u0131n\u0131klar ve i\u015faret fi\u015fekleri misill\xfc, o \u015feytanlar\u0131 ebvab-\u0131 semadan o \u015fahaplarla red ve tardd\u0131r.","oldText":"Ey [[ins|insanlar]] ve cin! Emirlerime [[itaat etmezseniz|boyun e\u011fmezseniz]] haydi [[hudud-u m\xfclk\xfcmden|m\xfclk\xfcm\xfcn s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131ndan|h\xfck\xfcmranl\u0131\u011f\u0131m alt\u0131ndaki yerlerden]] elinizden gelirse \xe7\u0131k\u0131n\u0131z, [[meseline|temsiline/\xf6rne\u011fine]] i\u015faret eden\\n\\n[[\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0634\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u0650\u0646\u0650\u0651 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0633\u064f\u0644\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064d \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0649\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u0670\u0644\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651\u0643\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064f\u0643\u064e\u0630\u0650\u0651\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u06de \u064a\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0634\u064f\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0638\u064c \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0648\u064e \u0646\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0635\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u06de|Ey cin ve insan toplulu\u011fu! G\xf6klerin ve yerin s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131ndan ge\xe7ip gitmeye g\xfcc\xfcn\xfcz yetiyorsa ge\xe7in! Ancak (Allah\'\u0131n verece\u011fi) bir g\xfc\xe7 olmad\u0131k\xe7a ge\xe7emezsiniz. O halde Rabbinizin hangi nimetlerini yalanl\u0131yorsunuz? \xdczerinize ate\u015ften bir alev ve erimi\u015f bak\u0131r (veya duman) g\xf6nderilir de yard\u0131mla\u015famazs\u0131n\u0131z.|Rahman Suresi, 33-35. Ayetler]]\\n\\n\xe2yetindeki [[azametli|b\xfcy\xfck/ha\u015fmetli]] [[inzara|uyar\u0131ya/korkutmaya]] ve deh\u015fetli tehdide ve \u015fiddetli [[zecre|yasaklamaya/menetmeye]] dikkat et. Nas\u0131l, [[ins|insan]] ve cinnin gayet [[ma\u011frurane|gururlu bir \u015fekilde]] [[temerr\xfcdlerini|inat\xe7\u0131l\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131/ba\u015fkald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131]], gayet [[mu\u2019cizane|mucizevi bir \u015fekilde]] bir [[bel\xe2gatla|etkili ve g\xfczel s\xf6zle]] k\u0131rar. [[Aczlerini|acizliklerini/g\xfc\xe7s\xfczl\xfcklerini]] ilan eder. [[Saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin|Rabl\u0131k saltanat\u0131n\u0131n/Allah\'\u0131n terbiye ve idare edicilik egemenli\u011finin]] geni\u015fli\u011fi ve [[azameti|b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc]] [[nisbetinde|oran\u0131nda/\xf6l\xe7\xfcs\xfcnde]] ne kadar \xe2ciz ve [[b\xee\xe7are|\xe7aresiz]] olduklar\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterir. G\xfcya \u015fu \xe2yetle hem [[\u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064f\u062c\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|Biz onlar\u0131 (y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131) \u015feytanlar i\xe7in ta\u015flama taneleri k\u0131ld\u0131k.|M\xfclk Suresi, 5. Ayet]] \xe2yetiyle b\xf6yle diyor ki:\\n\\n\u201cEy [[hakareti|k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc/de\u011fersizli\u011fi]] i\xe7inde [[ma\u011frur|gururlu]] ve [[m\xfctemerrid|inat\xe7\u0131/ba\u015fkald\u0131ran]] ve ey [[zaaf|zay\u0131fl\u0131k]] ve [[fakr\u0131|fakirli\u011fi/ihtiya\xe7 sahibi olu\u015fu]] i\xe7inde [[serke\u015f|asi/dikba\u015fl\u0131]] ve [[muannid|inat\xe7\u0131]] olan cin ve [[ins|insan]]! Nas\u0131l cesaret edersiniz ki isyan\u0131n\u0131zla \xf6yle bir [[Sultan-\u0131 Z\xee\u015fan\u2019\u0131n|\u015fanl\u0131 Sultan\'\u0131n (Allah\'\u0131n)]] [[evamirine|emirlerine]] kar\u015f\u0131 geliyorsunuz ki y\u0131ld\u0131zlar, aylar, g\xfcne\u015fler [[emirber neferleri|emir kulu askerleri/emir alan erleri]] gibi emirlerine itaat ederler. Hem [[tu\u011fyan\u0131n\u0131zla|azg\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131zla/isyan\u0131n\u0131zla]] \xf6yle bir [[H\xe2kim-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019e|ha\u015fmet ve b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck sahibi H\xe2kim\'e (Allah\'a)]] kar\u015f\u0131 [[m\xfcbareze ediyorsunuz|sava\u015f\u0131yorsunuz/d\xfcelloya kalk\u0131\u015f\u0131yorsunuz]] ki \xf6yle [[azametli|b\xfcy\xfck/ha\u015fmetli]] [[mut\xee|itaat eden]] askerleri var, [[faraza|varsayal\u0131m ki]] \u015feytanlar\u0131n\u0131z dayanabilseler onlar\u0131 da\u011f gibi g\xfcllelerle [[recmedebilirler|ta\u015flayabilirler/ta\u015fa tutabilirler]]. Hem [[k\xfcfran\u0131n\u0131zla|nank\xf6rl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfczle/ink\xe2r\u0131n\u0131zla]] \xf6yle bir [[M\xe2lik-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019in|b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck sahibi M\xfclk Sahibi\'nin (Allah\'\u0131n)]] memleketinde isyan ediyorsunuz ki [[ibad\u0131ndan|kullar\u0131ndan]] ve [[c\xfcnudundan|askerlerinden/ordular\u0131ndan]] \xf6yleleri var ki de\u011fil sizin gibi k\xfc\xe7\xfcc\xfck \xe2ciz [[mahluklar\u0131|yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flar\u0131]], belki [[farz-\u0131 muhal|imkans\u0131z oldu\u011fu halde varsay\u0131larak]] da\u011f ve [[arz|yerk\xfcre]] b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcnde birer [[ad\xfcvv-\xfc k\xe2fir|ink\xe2rc\u0131 d\xfc\u015fman]] olsayd\u0131n\u0131z, [[arz|yerk\xfcre]] ve da\u011f b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcnde y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131, ate\u015fli demirleri, [[\u015f\xfcvazl\u0131|alevli/ate\u015fli]] [[n\xfchaslar\u0131|bak\u0131rlar\u0131/erimi\u015f madenleri]] size atabilirler, sizi da\u011f\u0131t\u0131rlar. Hem \xf6yle bir kanunu k\u0131r\u0131yorsunuz ki o kanun ile \xf6yleler ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131r, e\u011fer [[l\xfczum olsa|gerekse]] [[arz\u0131n\u0131z\u0131|yerinizi/d\xfcnyan\u0131z\u0131]] y\xfcz\xfcn\xfcze \xe7arpar. G\xfclleler gibi k\xfcreniz [[misill\xfc|benzeri]] y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131 \xfcst\xfcn\xfcze ya\u011fd\u0131rabilirler.\u201d\\n\\nEvet, Kur\u2019an\u2019da baz\u0131 [[m\xfchim|\xf6nemli]] [[tah\u015fidat|y\u0131\u011f\u0131nak yapma/kuvvet toplama (burada; kelimelerle vurgu yapma)]] vard\u0131r ki d\xfc\u015fmanlar\u0131n kuvvetli oldu\u011fundan ileri gelmiyor. Belki [[ha\u015fmetin|b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn/heybetin]] [[izhar\u0131|g\xf6sterilmesi/a\xe7\u0131\u011fa \xe7\u0131kar\u0131lmas\u0131]] ve d\xfc\u015fman [[\u015fenaatinin|\xe7irkinli\u011finin/k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfcn]] [[te\u015fhiri|sergilenmesi/herkese duyurulmas\u0131]] gibi sebeplerden ileri geliyor.\\n\\nHem bazen [[kemal-i intizam\u0131|d\xfczenin m\xfckemmelli\u011fini]] ve [[nihayet-i adli|adaletin son noktas\u0131n\u0131/sonsuz adaleti]] ve [[gayet-i hilmi|yumu\u015fak huylulu\u011fun zirvesini]] ve [[kuvvet-i hikmeti|hikmetin g\xfcc\xfcn\xfc]] g\xf6stermek i\xe7in en b\xfcy\xfck ve kuvvetli [[esbab\u0131|sebepleri]], en k\xfc\xe7\xfck ve zay\u0131f bir \u015feye kar\u015f\u0131 [[tah\u015fid eder|y\u0131\u011far/toplar]] ve \xfcst\xfcnde tutar; d\xfc\u015f\xfcrtmez, [[tecav\xfcz ettirmez|sald\u0131rtmaz/haddi a\u015ft\u0131rmaz]]. Mesela, \u015fu \xe2yete bak:\\n\\n[[\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064e\u0638\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e\u062c\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u062d\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0653\u0626\u0650\u0643\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0628\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0638\u064e\u0647\u0656\u064a\u0631\u064c|E\u011fer Peygamber\u2019e kar\u015f\u0131 birbirinize arka \xe7\u0131karsan\u0131z (bilin ki) Allah onun sahibidir. Cebrail ve m\xfcminlerin iyileri de (onun yard\u0131mc\u0131lar\u0131d\u0131r). Bunlar\u0131n ard\u0131ndan melekler de (ona) destek\xe7idir.|Tahrim Suresi, 4. Ayet]]\\n\\nNe kadar [[Nebi|Peygamber]] hakk\u0131na h\xfcrmet ve ne kadar [[ezvac\u0131n|e\u015flerin (Peygamber e\u015flerinin)]] hukukuna merhamet var. \u015eu [[m\xfchim|\xf6nemli]] [[tah\u015fidat|y\u0131\u011f\u0131nak/vurgu]], yaln\u0131z [[h\xfcrmet-i Nebinin|Peygambere sayg\u0131n\u0131n]] [[azametini|b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc]] ve iki [[za\xeefenin|zay\u0131f kad\u0131n\u0131n (Hz. Ai\u015fe ve Hz. Hafsa)]] [[\u015fekvalar\u0131n\u0131n|\u015fikayetlerinin]] [[ehemmiyetini|\xf6nemini]] ve haklar\u0131n\u0131n [[riayetini|g\xf6zetilmesini/uyulmas\u0131n\u0131]] [[rah\xeemane|merhametlice]] ifade etmek i\xe7indir.\\n\\nYedinci Basamak: Melekler ve [[semekler|bal\u0131klar]] gibi y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131n dahi gayet [[muhtelif|\xe7e\u015fitli]] [[efradlar\u0131|fertleri/bireyleri]] vard\u0131r. Bir k\u0131sm\u0131 [[nihayet|son derece]] k\xfc\xe7\xfck, bir k\u0131sm\u0131 gayet b\xfcy\xfckt\xfcr. Hatt\xe2 g\xf6ky\xfcz\xfcnde her parlayana \u201cy\u0131ld\u0131z\u201d denilir. \u0130\u015fte bu y\u0131ld\u0131z cinsinden bir [[nev\u2019i|\xe7e\u015fidi/t\xfcr\xfc]] de [[n\xe2zenin|nazl\u0131/ince]] sema y\xfcz\xfcn\xfcn [[murassa|m\xfccevherlerle s\xfcslenmi\u015f]] [[ziynetleri|s\xfcsleri]] ve o a\u011fac\u0131n [[m\xfcnevver|nurlu/ayd\u0131nl\u0131k]] meyveleri ve o denizin [[m\xfcsebbih|tesbih eden/Allah\'\u0131 zikreden]] bal\u0131klar\u0131 h\xfckm\xfcnde; [[F\xe2t\u0131r-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal|b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck sahibi, her \u015feyi harika yaratan Allah]], [[S\xe2ni\u2019-i Z\xfclcemal|sonsuz g\xfczellik sahibi Sanatkar (Allah)]] onlar\u0131 yaratm\u0131\u015f ve meleklerine [[mesireler|gezinti yerleri]], binekler, [[menziller|konak yerleri/duraklar]] yapm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Ve y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131n k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir [[nevini|t\xfcr\xfcn\xfc]] de [[\u015feyat\xeenin|\u015feytanlar\u0131n]] [[recmine|ta\u015flanmas\u0131na]] \xe2let etmi\u015f. \u0130\u015fte bu [[recm-i \u015feyat\xeen|\u015feytanlar\u0131n ta\u015flanmas\u0131]] i\xe7in at\u0131lan [[\u015fahaplar\u0131n|akan y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131n/g\xf6kta\u015flar\u0131n\u0131n]] \xfc\xe7 manas\u0131 olabilir:\\n\\n\\n\\nBirincisi: [[Kanun-u m\xfcbareze|m\xfccadele/sava\u015f kanunu]], en geni\u015f dairede dahi [[cereyan etti\u011fine|i\u015fledi\u011fine/ge\xe7erli oldu\u011funa]] [[remiz|i\u015faret/sembol]] ve [[al\xe2mettir|belirtidir]].\\n\\n\u0130kincisi: [[Semavatta|g\xf6klerde]] [[h\xfc\u015fyar|uyan\u0131k/dikkatli]] n\xf6bettarlar, [[mut\xee|itaat eden]] [[sekeneler|sakinler/oturanlar]] var. [[Arzl\u0131|yerli/d\xfcnyal\u0131]] [[\u015ferirlerin|k\xf6t\xfclerin]] [[ihtilat\u0131ndan|kar\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131ndan/i\xe7li d\u0131\u015fl\u0131 olmalar\u0131ndan]] ve [[istima\u2019lar\u0131ndan|kulak h\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131 yapmalar\u0131ndan/gizlice dinlemelerinden]] ho\u015flanmayan [[c\xfcnudullah|Allah\'\u0131n askerleri]] bulundu\u011funa ilan ve i\u015farettir.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfcs\xfc: [[Muzahrefat-\u0131 arziyenin|yery\xfcz\xfc pisliklerinin/k\xf6t\xfcl\xfcklerinin]] [[m\xfcmessil\xe2t-\u0131 hab\xeeseleri|pis temsilcileri]] olan casus \u015feytanlar\u0131, temiz ve temizlerin [[meskeni|evi/yurdu]] olan semay\u0131 [[telvis etmemek|kirletmemek]] ve [[n\xfcfus-u hab\xeese|k\xf6t\xfc ruhlar/k\xf6t\xfc nefisler]] hesab\u0131na [[tecess\xfcs ettirmemek|gizlice ara\u015ft\u0131rma yapt\u0131rmamak/casusluk yapt\u0131rmamak]] i\xe7in edepsiz casuslar\u0131 korkutmak i\xe7in at\u0131lan manc\u0131n\u0131klar ve i\u015faret fi\u015fekleri [[misill\xfc|benzeri/gibi]], o \u015feytanlar\u0131 [[ebvab-\u0131 semadan|g\xf6k kap\u0131lar\u0131ndan]] o [[\u015fahaplarla|akan y\u0131ld\u0131zlarla]] [[red ve tardd\u0131r|geri \xe7evirme ve kovmad\u0131r]].","modernText":"Ey [[insanlar|ins|]] ve cin! Emirlerime [[boyun e\u011fmezseniz|itaat etmezseniz|]] haydi [[m\xfclk\xfcm\xfcn s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131ndan|hudud-u m\xfclk\xfcmden|h\xfck\xfcmranl\u0131\u011f\u0131m alt\u0131ndaki yerlerden]] elinizden gelirse \xe7\u0131k\u0131n\u0131z, [[temsiline/\xf6rne\u011fine|meseline|]] i\u015faret eden\\n\\n[[Ey cin ve insan toplulu\u011fu! G\xf6klerin ve yerin s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131ndan ge\xe7ip gitmeye g\xfcc\xfcn\xfcz yetiyorsa ge\xe7in! Ancak (Allah\'\u0131n verece\u011fi) bir g\xfc\xe7 olmad\u0131k\xe7a ge\xe7emezsiniz. O halde Rabbinizin hangi nimetlerini yalanl\u0131yorsunuz? \xdczerinize ate\u015ften bir alev ve erimi\u015f bak\u0131r (veya duman) g\xf6nderilir de yard\u0131mla\u015famazs\u0131n\u0131z.|\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0634\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u0650\u0646\u0650\u0651 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0630\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0633\u064f\u0644\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064d \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0649\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u0670\u0644\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651\u0643\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064f\u0643\u064e\u0630\u0650\u0651\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u06de \u064a\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0634\u064f\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0638\u064c \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0648\u064e \u0646\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0635\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u06de|Rahman Suresi, 33-35. Ayetler]]\\n\\n\xe2yetindeki [[b\xfcy\xfck/ha\u015fmetli|azametli|]] [[uyar\u0131ya/korkutmaya|inzara|]] ve deh\u015fetli tehdide ve \u015fiddetli [[yasaklamaya/menetmeye|zecre|]] dikkat et. Nas\u0131l, [[insan|ins|]] ve cinnin gayet [[gururlu bir \u015fekilde|ma\u011frurane|]] [[inat\xe7\u0131l\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131/ba\u015fkald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131|temerr\xfcdlerini|]], gayet [[mucizevi bir \u015fekilde|mu\u2019cizane|]] bir [[etkili ve g\xfczel s\xf6zle|bel\xe2gatla|]] k\u0131rar. [[acizliklerini/g\xfc\xe7s\xfczl\xfcklerini|Aczlerini|]] ilan eder. [[Rabl\u0131k saltanat\u0131n\u0131n/Allah\'\u0131n terbiye ve idare edicilik egemenli\u011finin|Saltanat-\u0131 rububiyetin|]] geni\u015fli\u011fi ve [[b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc|azameti|]] [[oran\u0131nda/\xf6l\xe7\xfcs\xfcnde|nisbetinde|]] ne kadar \xe2ciz ve [[\xe7aresiz|b\xee\xe7are|]] olduklar\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterir. G\xfcya \u015fu \xe2yetle hem [[Biz onlar\u0131 (y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131) \u015feytanlar i\xe7in ta\u015flama taneleri k\u0131ld\u0131k.|\u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064f\u062c\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|M\xfclk Suresi, 5. Ayet]] \xe2yetiyle b\xf6yle diyor ki:\\n\\n\u201cEy [[k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfc/de\u011fersizli\u011fi|hakareti|]] i\xe7inde [[gururlu|ma\u011frur|]] ve [[inat\xe7\u0131/ba\u015fkald\u0131ran|m\xfctemerrid|]] ve ey [[zay\u0131fl\u0131k|zaaf|]] ve [[fakirli\u011fi/ihtiya\xe7 sahibi olu\u015fu|fakr\u0131|]] i\xe7inde [[asi/dikba\u015fl\u0131|serke\u015f|]] ve [[inat\xe7\u0131|muannid|]] olan cin ve [[insan|ins|]]! Nas\u0131l cesaret edersiniz ki isyan\u0131n\u0131zla \xf6yle bir [[\u015fanl\u0131 Sultan\'\u0131n (Allah\'\u0131n)|Sultan-\u0131 Z\xee\u015fan\u2019\u0131n|]] [[emirlerine|evamirine|]] kar\u015f\u0131 geliyorsunuz ki y\u0131ld\u0131zlar, aylar, g\xfcne\u015fler [[emir kulu askerleri/emir alan erleri|emirber neferleri|]] gibi emirlerine itaat ederler. Hem [[azg\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131zla/isyan\u0131n\u0131zla|tu\u011fyan\u0131n\u0131zla|]] \xf6yle bir [[ha\u015fmet ve b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck sahibi H\xe2kim\'e (Allah\'a)|H\xe2kim-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019e|]] kar\u015f\u0131 [[sava\u015f\u0131yorsunuz/d\xfcelloya kalk\u0131\u015f\u0131yorsunuz|m\xfcbareze ediyorsunuz|]] ki \xf6yle [[b\xfcy\xfck/ha\u015fmetli|azametli|]] [[itaat eden|mut\xee|]] askerleri var, [[varsayal\u0131m ki|faraza|]] \u015feytanlar\u0131n\u0131z dayanabilseler onlar\u0131 da\u011f gibi g\xfcllelerle [[ta\u015flayabilirler/ta\u015fa tutabilirler|recmedebilirler|]]. Hem [[nank\xf6rl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfczle/ink\xe2r\u0131n\u0131zla|k\xfcfran\u0131n\u0131zla|]] \xf6yle bir [[b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck sahibi M\xfclk Sahibi\'nin (Allah\'\u0131n)|M\xe2lik-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019in|]] memleketinde isyan ediyorsunuz ki [[kullar\u0131ndan|ibad\u0131ndan|]] ve [[askerlerinden/ordular\u0131ndan|c\xfcnudundan|]] \xf6yleleri var ki de\u011fil sizin gibi k\xfc\xe7\xfcc\xfck \xe2ciz [[yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flar\u0131|mahluklar\u0131|]], belki [[imkans\u0131z oldu\u011fu halde varsay\u0131larak|farz-\u0131 muhal|]] da\u011f ve [[yerk\xfcre|arz|]] b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcnde birer [[ink\xe2rc\u0131 d\xfc\u015fman|ad\xfcvv-\xfc k\xe2fir|]] olsayd\u0131n\u0131z, [[yerk\xfcre|arz|]] ve da\u011f b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcnde y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131, ate\u015fli demirleri, [[alevli/ate\u015fli|\u015f\xfcvazl\u0131|]] [[bak\u0131rlar\u0131/erimi\u015f madenleri|n\xfchaslar\u0131|]] size atabilirler, sizi da\u011f\u0131t\u0131rlar. Hem \xf6yle bir kanunu k\u0131r\u0131yorsunuz ki o kanun ile \xf6yleler ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131r, e\u011fer [[gerekse|l\xfczum olsa|]] [[yerinizi/d\xfcnyan\u0131z\u0131|arz\u0131n\u0131z\u0131|]] y\xfcz\xfcn\xfcze \xe7arpar. G\xfclleler gibi k\xfcreniz [[benzeri|misill\xfc|]] y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131 \xfcst\xfcn\xfcze ya\u011fd\u0131rabilirler.\u201d\\n\\nEvet, Kur\u2019an\u2019da baz\u0131 [[\xf6nemli|m\xfchim|]] [[y\u0131\u011f\u0131nak yapma/kuvvet toplama (burada; kelimelerle vurgu yapma)|tah\u015fidat|]] vard\u0131r ki d\xfc\u015fmanlar\u0131n kuvvetli oldu\u011fundan ileri gelmiyor. Belki [[b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn/heybetin|ha\u015fmetin|]] [[g\xf6sterilmesi/a\xe7\u0131\u011fa \xe7\u0131kar\u0131lmas\u0131|izhar\u0131|]] ve d\xfc\u015fman [[\xe7irkinli\u011finin/k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfcn|\u015fenaatinin|]] [[sergilenmesi/herkese duyurulmas\u0131|te\u015fhiri|]] gibi sebeplerden ileri geliyor.\\n\\nHem bazen [[d\xfczenin m\xfckemmelli\u011fini|kemal-i intizam\u0131|]] ve [[adaletin son noktas\u0131n\u0131/sonsuz adaleti|nihayet-i adli|]] ve [[yumu\u015fak huylulu\u011fun zirvesini|gayet-i hilmi|]] ve [[hikmetin g\xfcc\xfcn\xfc|kuvvet-i hikmeti|]] g\xf6stermek i\xe7in en b\xfcy\xfck ve kuvvetli [[sebepleri|esbab\u0131|]], en k\xfc\xe7\xfck ve zay\u0131f bir \u015feye kar\u015f\u0131 [[y\u0131\u011far/toplar|tah\u015fid eder|]] ve \xfcst\xfcnde tutar; d\xfc\u015f\xfcrtmez, [[sald\u0131rtmaz/haddi a\u015ft\u0131rmaz|tecav\xfcz ettirmez|]]. Mesela, \u015fu \xe2yete bak:\\n\\n[[E\u011fer Peygamber\u2019e kar\u015f\u0131 birbirinize arka \xe7\u0131karsan\u0131z (bilin ki) Allah onun sahibidir. Cebrail ve m\xfcminlerin iyileri de (onun yard\u0131mc\u0131lar\u0131d\u0131r). Bunlar\u0131n ard\u0131ndan melekler de (ona) destek\xe7idir.|\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064e\u0638\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e\u062c\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u062d\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0653\u0626\u0650\u0643\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0628\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0638\u064e\u0647\u0656\u064a\u0631\u064c|Tahrim Suresi, 4. Ayet]]\\n\\nNe kadar [[Peygamber|Nebi|]] hakk\u0131na h\xfcrmet ve ne kadar [[e\u015flerin (Peygamber e\u015flerinin)|ezvac\u0131n|]] hukukuna merhamet var. \u015eu [[\xf6nemli|m\xfchim|]] [[y\u0131\u011f\u0131nak/vurgu|tah\u015fidat|]], yaln\u0131z [[Peygambere sayg\u0131n\u0131n|h\xfcrmet-i Nebinin|]] [[b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc|azametini|]] ve iki [[zay\u0131f kad\u0131n\u0131n (Hz. Ai\u015fe ve Hz. Hafsa)|za\xeefenin|]] [[\u015fikayetlerinin|\u015fekvalar\u0131n\u0131n|]] [[\xf6nemini|ehemmiyetini|]] ve haklar\u0131n\u0131n [[g\xf6zetilmesini/uyulmas\u0131n\u0131|riayetini|]] [[merhametlice|rah\xeemane|]] ifade etmek i\xe7indir.\\n\\nYedinci Basamak: Melekler ve [[bal\u0131klar|semekler|]] gibi y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131n dahi gayet [[\xe7e\u015fitli|muhtelif|]] [[fertleri/bireyleri|efradlar\u0131|]] vard\u0131r. Bir k\u0131sm\u0131 [[son derece|nihayet|]] k\xfc\xe7\xfck, bir k\u0131sm\u0131 gayet b\xfcy\xfckt\xfcr. Hatt\xe2 g\xf6ky\xfcz\xfcnde her parlayana \u201cy\u0131ld\u0131z\u201d denilir. \u0130\u015fte bu y\u0131ld\u0131z cinsinden bir [[\xe7e\u015fidi/t\xfcr\xfc|nev\u2019i|]] de [[nazl\u0131/ince|n\xe2zenin|]] sema y\xfcz\xfcn\xfcn [[m\xfccevherlerle s\xfcslenmi\u015f|murassa|]] [[s\xfcsleri|ziynetleri|]] ve o a\u011fac\u0131n [[nurlu/ayd\u0131nl\u0131k|m\xfcnevver|]] meyveleri ve o denizin [[tesbih eden/Allah\'\u0131 zikreden|m\xfcsebbih|]] bal\u0131klar\u0131 h\xfckm\xfcnde; [[b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck sahibi, her \u015feyi harika yaratan Allah|F\xe2t\u0131r-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal|]], [[sonsuz g\xfczellik sahibi Sanatkar (Allah)|S\xe2ni\u2019-i Z\xfclcemal|]] onlar\u0131 yaratm\u0131\u015f ve meleklerine [[gezinti yerleri|mesireler|]], binekler, [[konak yerleri/duraklar|menziller|]] yapm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Ve y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131n k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir [[t\xfcr\xfcn\xfc|nevini|]] de [[\u015feytanlar\u0131n|\u015feyat\xeenin|]] [[ta\u015flanmas\u0131na|recmine|]] \xe2let etmi\u015f. \u0130\u015fte bu [[\u015feytanlar\u0131n ta\u015flanmas\u0131|recm-i \u015feyat\xeen|]] i\xe7in at\u0131lan [[akan y\u0131ld\u0131zlar\u0131n/g\xf6kta\u015flar\u0131n\u0131n|\u015fahaplar\u0131n|]] \xfc\xe7 manas\u0131 olabilir:\\n\\n\\n\\nBirincisi: [[m\xfccadele/sava\u015f kanunu|Kanun-u m\xfcbareze|]], en geni\u015f dairede dahi [[i\u015fledi\u011fine/ge\xe7erli oldu\u011funa|cereyan etti\u011fine|]] [[i\u015faret/sembol|remiz|]] ve [[belirtidir|al\xe2mettir|]].\\n\\n\u0130kincisi: [[g\xf6klerde|Semavatta|]] [[uyan\u0131k/dikkatli|h\xfc\u015fyar|]] n\xf6bettarlar, [[itaat eden|mut\xee|]] [[sakinler/oturanlar|sekeneler|]] var. [[yerli/d\xfcnyal\u0131|Arzl\u0131|]] [[k\xf6t\xfclerin|\u015ferirlerin|]] [[kar\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131ndan/i\xe7li d\u0131\u015fl\u0131 olmalar\u0131ndan|ihtilat\u0131ndan|]] ve [[kulak h\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131 yapmalar\u0131ndan/gizlice dinlemelerinden|istima\u2019lar\u0131ndan|]] ho\u015flanmayan [[Allah\'\u0131n askerleri|c\xfcnudullah|]] bulundu\u011funa ilan ve i\u015farettir.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfcs\xfc: [[yery\xfcz\xfc pisliklerinin/k\xf6t\xfcl\xfcklerinin|Muzahrefat-\u0131 arziyenin|]] [[pis temsilcileri|m\xfcmessil\xe2t-\u0131 hab\xeeseleri|]] olan casus \u015feytanlar\u0131, temiz ve temizlerin [[evi/yurdu|meskeni|]] olan semay\u0131 [[kirletmemek|telvis etmemek|]] ve [[k\xf6t\xfc ruhlar/k\xf6t\xfc nefisler|n\xfcfus-u hab\xeese|]] hesab\u0131na [[gizlice ara\u015ft\u0131rma yapt\u0131rmamak/casusluk yapt\u0131rmamak|tecess\xfcs ettirmemek|]] i\xe7in edepsiz casuslar\u0131 korkutmak i\xe7in at\u0131lan manc\u0131n\u0131klar ve i\u015faret fi\u015fekleri [[benzeri/gibi|misill\xfc|]], o \u015feytanlar\u0131 [[g\xf6k kap\u0131lar\u0131ndan|ebvab-\u0131 semadan|]] o [[akan y\u0131ld\u0131zlarla|\u015fahaplarla|]] [[geri \xe7evirme ve kovmad\u0131r|red ve tardd\u0131r|]].","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.21-19:15","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"},{"pageId":5,"rawText":"\u0130\u015fte y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi h\xfckm\xfcnde olan kafa fenerine itimat eden ve Kur\u2019an g\xfcne\u015finden g\xf6z\xfcn\xfc yuman kozmo\u011frafyac\u0131 efendi! \u015eu yedi basamaklarda i\u015faret edilen hakikatlere birden bak. G\xf6z\xfcn\xfc a\xe7, kafa fenerini b\u0131rak, g\xfcnd\xfcz gibi i\u2019caz \u0131\u015f\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7inde \u015fu \xe2yetin manas\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6r! O \xe2yetin semas\u0131ndan bir hakikat y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131 al, senin ba\u015f\u0131ndaki \u015feytana at, kendi \u015feytan\u0131n\u0131 recmet! Biz dahi etmeliyiz ve \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u0650 \u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 beraber demeliyiz. \u0641\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u062c\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u063a\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u0650\u0643\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0650\u0639\u064e\u0629\u064f\\n\\n\u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0643\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f\\n\\n***\\n\\nOn Be\u015finci S\xf6z\u2019\xfcn Zeyli\\n\\nYirmi Alt\u0131nc\u0131 Mektup\u2019un Birinci Mebhas\u0131\\n\\n\u0628\u0650\u0627\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u0649\u0652\u0621\u064d \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0628\u0651\u0650\u062d\u064f \u0628\u0650\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0647\u0656\\n\\n\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\\n\\n\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0645\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0632\u064e\u063a\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0646\u064e\u0632\u0652\u063a\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0639\u0650\u0630\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0639\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f\\n\\nH\xfcccet\xfc\u2019l-Kur\u2019an Ale\u2019\u015f-\u015feytan ve Hizbihi\\n\\n\u0130blisi ilzam, \u015feytan\u0131 ifham (\u0625\u0641\u062d\u0627\u0645), ehl-i tu\u011fyan\u0131 isk\xe2t eden Birinci Mebhas; b\xeetarafane muhakeme i\xe7inde \u015feytan\u0131n m\xfcthi\u015f bir desisesini kat\u2019\xee bir surette reddeden bir vak\u0131ad\u0131r. O vak\u0131an\u0131n m\xfccmel bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 on sene evvel Lemaat\u2019ta yazm\u0131\u015ft\u0131m. \u015e\xf6yle ki:\\n\\nBu risalenin telifinden on bir sene evvel ramazan-\u0131 \u015ferifte \u0130stanbul\u2019da Bayezid Cami-i \u015eerifi\u2019nde h\xe2f\u0131zlar\u0131 dinliyordum. Birden \u015fahs\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6rmedim fakat manev\xee bir ses i\u015fittim gibi bana geldi. Zihnimi kendine \xe7evirdi. Hayalen dinledim.\\n\\nBakt\u0131m ki bana der:\\n\\nSen Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 pek \xe2l\xee, \xe7ok parlak g\xf6r\xfcyorsun. B\xeetarafane muhakeme et, \xf6yle bak. Yani bir be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131 farz et, bak. Acaba o meziyetleri, o ziynetleri g\xf6recek misin?\\n\\nHakikaten ben de ona aldand\u0131m. Be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131 farz edip \xf6yle bakt\u0131m. G\xf6rd\xfcm ki nas\u0131l Bayezid\u2019in elektrik d\xfc\u011fmesi \xe7evrilip s\xf6nd\xfcr\xfcl\xfcnce ortal\u0131k karanl\u0131\u011fa d\xfc\u015fer. \xd6yle de o farz ile Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n parlak \u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131 gizlenmeye ba\u015flad\u0131. O vakit anlad\u0131m ki benim ile konu\u015fan \u015feytand\u0131r. Beni vartaya yuvarland\u0131r\u0131yor. Kur\u2019an\u2019dan istimdad ettim. Birden bir nur kalbime geldi. M\xfcdafaaya kat\u2019\xee bir kuvvet verdi. O vakit \u015f\xf6ylece \u015feytana kar\u015f\u0131 m\xfcnazara ba\u015flad\u0131.\\n\\nDedim:\\n\\nEy \u015feytan! B\xeetarafane muhakeme, iki taraf ortas\u0131nda bir vaziyettir. Halbuki hem senin hem insandaki senin \u015fakirdlerin, dedi\u011finiz b\xeetarafane muhakeme ise taraf-\u0131 muhalifi iltizamd\u0131r, b\xeetarafl\u0131k de\u011fildir. Muvakkaten bir dinsizliktir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc Kur\u2019an\u2019a kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer diye bakmak ve \xf6yle muhakeme etmek, \u015f\u0131kk-\u0131 muhalifi esas tutmakt\u0131r. B\xe2t\u0131l\u0131 iltizamd\u0131r, b\xeetarafane de\u011fildir, belki b\xe2t\u0131la tarafgirliktir.\\n\\n\u015eeytan dedi ki:\\n\\n\xd6yle ise ne Allah\u2019\u0131n kel\xe2m\u0131 ne de be\u015ferin kel\xe2m\u0131 deme. Ortada farz et, bak.\\n\\nBen dedim:\\n\\nO da olamaz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc m\xfcn\xe2zaun f\xeeh bir mal bulunsa e\u011fer iki m\xfcdde\xee birbirine yak\u0131n ise ve kurbiyet-i mek\xe2n varsa; o vakit o mal, ikisinden ba\u015fka birinin elinde veya ikisinin elleri yeti\u015fecek bir surette bir yere b\u0131rak\u0131lacak. Hangisi ispat etse o al\u0131r. E\u011fer o iki m\xfcdde\xee birbirinden gayet uzak, biri ma\u015fr\u0131kta, biri ma\u011fribde ise o vakit kaideten sahib\xfc\u2019l-yed kim ise onun elinde b\u0131rak\u0131lacakt\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ortada b\u0131rakmak kabil de\u011fildir.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte Kur\u2019an k\u0131ymettar bir mald\u0131r. Be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131 Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019\u0131n kel\xe2m\u0131ndan ne kadar uzaksa o iki taraf o kadar, belki hadsiz birbirinden uzakt\u0131r. \u0130\u015fte, ser\xe2dan s\xfcreyyaya kadar birbirinden uzak o iki taraf ortas\u0131nda b\u0131rakmak m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fildir. Hem ortas\u0131 yoktur. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc v\xfccud ve adem gibi ve nak\xeezeyn gibi iki z\u0131tt\u0131rlar. Ortas\u0131 olamaz.\\n\\n\xd6yle ise Kur\u2019an i\xe7in sahib\xfc\u2019l-yed, taraf-\u0131 \u0130lah\xeedir. \xd6yle ise onun elinde kabul edilip \xf6ylece delail-i ispata bak\u0131lacak. E\u011fer \xf6teki taraf onun kel\xe2mullah oldu\u011funa dair b\xfct\xfcn b\xfcrhanlar\u0131 birer birer \xe7\xfcr\xfctse elini ona uzatabilir. Yoksa uzatamaz. Heyhat! Binler berahin-i kat\u2019iyenin m\u0131hlar\u0131yla ar\u015f-\u0131 a\u2019zama \xe7ak\u0131lan bu muazzam p\u0131rlantay\u0131 hangi el b\xfct\xfcn o m\u0131hlar\u0131 s\xf6k\xfcp o direkleri kesip onu d\xfc\u015f\xfcrebilir?","oldText":"\u0130\u015fte y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi h\xfckm\xfcnde olan kafa fenerine [[itimat eden|g\xfcvenen]] ve Kur\u2019an g\xfcne\u015finden g\xf6z\xfcn\xfc yuman kozmo\u011frafyac\u0131 efendi! \u015eu yedi basamaklarda i\u015faret edilen [[hakikatlere|ger\xe7eklere]] birden bak. G\xf6z\xfcn\xfc a\xe7, kafa fenerini b\u0131rak, g\xfcnd\xfcz gibi [[i\u2019caz|mucizelik|benzersizlik, insan\u0131 aciz b\u0131rakan s\xf6z sanat\u0131]] \u0131\u015f\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7inde \u015fu \xe2yetin manas\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6r! O \xe2yetin [[semas\u0131ndan|g\xf6\u011f\xfcnden]] bir [[hakikat|ger\xe7ek]] y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131 al, senin ba\u015f\u0131ndaki \u015feytana at, kendi \u015feytan\u0131n\u0131 [[recmet|ta\u015fla|kov, uzakla\u015ft\u0131r]]! Biz dahi etmeliyiz ve [[\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|Rabbim! \u015eeytanlar\u0131n k\u0131\u015fk\u0131rtmalar\u0131ndan Sana s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131r\u0131m (M\xfc\'min\xfbn, 23/97)]] beraber demeliyiz. [[\u0641\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u062c\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u063a\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u0650\u0643\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0650\u0639\u064e\u0629\u064f|\xdcst\xfcn delil ve kesin hikmet Allah\'\u0131nd\u0131r (En\'\xe2m, 6/149)]]\\n\\n[[\u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0643\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0643\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f|Seni her t\xfcrl\xfc eksiklikten tenzih ederiz. Senin bize \xf6\u011fretti\u011finden ba\u015fka bizim hi\xe7bir bilgimiz yoktur. \u015e\xfcphesiz her \u015feyi hakk\u0131yla bilen ve her i\u015fi hikmetle yapan Sensin (Bakara, 2/32)]]\\n\\n***\\n\\nOn Be\u015finci S\xf6z\u2019\xfcn [[Zeyli|Eki|\u0130lavesi]]\\n\\nYirmi Alt\u0131nc\u0131 Mektup\u2019un Birinci [[Mebhas\u0131|B\xf6l\xfcm\xfc|Bahsi, konusu]]\\n\\n[[\u0628\u0650\u0627\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u0649\u0652\u0621\u064d \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u064a\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651\u062d\u064f \u0628\u0650\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0647\u0656|O\'nu eksikliklerden tenzih ederiz ki, O\'nun ismiyle ba\u015flar\u0131m; hi\xe7bir \u015fey yoktur ki O\'nu hamd ile tesbih etmesin (\u0130sr\xe2, 17/44)]]\\n\\n[[\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|Rahm\xe2n ve Rah\xeem olan Allah\'\u0131n ad\u0131yla]]\\n\\n[[\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0646\u0652z\u064e\u063a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0646\u064e\u0632\u0652\u063a\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0639\u0650\u0630\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0639\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f|E\u011fer \u015feytandan bir k\u0131\u015fk\u0131rtma seni d\xfcrtecek olursa, hemen Allah\'a s\u0131\u011f\u0131n. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc O, her \u015feyi i\u015fitendir, her \u015feyi bilendir (Fussilet, 41/36)]]\\n\\n[[H\xfcccet\xfc\u2019l-Kur\u2019an|Kur\'an\'\u0131n delili]] [[Ale\u2019\u015f-\u015feytan|\u015eeytana kar\u015f\u0131]] ve [[Hizbihi|Onun taraftarlar\u0131na]]\\n\\n\u0130blisi [[ilzam|susturan|susturmak, cevap veremez hale getirmek]], \u015feytan\u0131 [[ifham|susturan|delil ile a\u011fz\u0131n\u0131 kapamak]], [[ehl-i tu\u011fyan\u0131|azg\u0131nlar\u0131|haktan sapanlar\u0131]] [[isk\xe2t eden|susturan]] Birinci [[Mebhas|B\xf6l\xfcm]]; [[b\xeetarafane|tarafs\u0131zca]] [[muhakeme|yarg\u0131lama|zihinsel de\u011ferlendirme]] i\xe7inde \u015feytan\u0131n m\xfcthi\u015f bir [[desisesini|tuza\u011f\u0131n\u0131|hile ve aldatmacas\u0131n\u0131]] [[kat\u2019\xee|kesin]] bir surette reddeden bir [[vak\u0131ad\u0131r|olayd\u0131r]]. O [[vak\u0131an\u0131n|olay\u0131n]] [[m\xfccmel|k\u0131sa ve \xf6z]] bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 on sene evvel Lemaat\u2019ta yazm\u0131\u015ft\u0131m. \u015e\xf6yle ki:\\n\\nBu risalenin [[telifinden|yaz\u0131lmas\u0131ndan]] on bir sene evvel [[ramazan-\u0131 \u015ferifte|m\xfcbarek ramazan ay\u0131nda]] \u0130stanbul\u2019da Bayezid [[Cami-i \u015eerifi\u2019nde|M\xfcbarek Camisi\'nde]] [[h\xe2f\u0131zlar\u0131|Kur\'an\'\u0131 ezbere okuyanlar\u0131]] dinliyordum. Birden \u015fahs\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6rmedim fakat [[manev\xee|ruhsal]] bir ses i\u015fittim gibi bana geldi. Zihnimi kendine \xe7evirdi. Hayalen dinledim.\\n\\nBakt\u0131m ki bana der:\\n\\nSen Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 pek [[\xe2l\xee|y\xfcce]], \xe7ok parlak g\xf6r\xfcyorsun. [[B\xeetarafane|Tarafs\u0131zca]] [[muhakeme et|de\u011ferlendir]], \xf6yle bak. Yani bir [[be\u015fer|insan]] [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] [[farz et|say]], bak. Acaba o [[meziyetleri|\xfcst\xfcn \xf6zellikleri]], o [[ziynetleri|s\xfcsleri|g\xfczellikleri]] g\xf6recek misin?\\n\\nHakikaten ben de ona aldand\u0131m. [[Be\u015fer|\u0130nsan]] [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] [[farz edip|say\u0131p]] \xf6yle bakt\u0131m. G\xf6rd\xfcm ki nas\u0131l Bayezid\u2019in elektrik d\xfc\u011fmesi \xe7evrilip s\xf6nd\xfcr\xfcl\xfcnce ortal\u0131k karanl\u0131\u011fa d\xfc\u015fer. \xd6yle de o [[farz|varsay\u0131m]] ile Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n parlak \u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131 gizlenmeye ba\u015flad\u0131. O vakit anlad\u0131m ki benim ile konu\u015fan \u015feytand\u0131r. Beni [[vartaya|tehlikeli u\xe7uruma|hataya, tuza\u011fa]] yuvarland\u0131r\u0131yor. Kur\u2019an\u2019dan [[istimdad ettim|yard\u0131m istedim]]. Birden bir nur kalbime geldi. [[M\xfcdafaaya|Savunmaya]] [[kat\u2019\xee|kesin]] bir kuvvet verdi. O vakit \u015f\xf6ylece \u015feytana kar\u015f\u0131 [[m\xfcnazara|kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131kl\u0131 tart\u0131\u015fma]] ba\u015flad\u0131.\\n\\nDedim:\\n\\nEy \u015feytan! [[B\xeetarafane|Tarafs\u0131zca]] [[muhakeme|yarg\u0131lama]], iki taraf ortas\u0131nda bir vaziyettir. Halbuki hem senin hem insandaki senin [[\u015fakirdlerin|\xf6\u011frencilerin|takip\xe7ilerin]], dedi\u011finiz [[b\xeetarafane|tarafs\u0131zca]] [[muhakeme|yarg\u0131lama]] ise [[taraf-\u0131 muhalifi|kar\u015f\u0131 taraf\u0131]] [[iltizamd\u0131r|taraf\u0131n\u0131 tutmakt\u0131r|kabullenmektir]], [[b\xeetarafl\u0131k|tarafs\u0131zl\u0131k]] de\u011fildir. [[Muvakkaten|Ge\xe7ici olarak]] bir dinsizliktir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc Kur\u2019an\u2019a [[kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer|insan s\xf6z\xfc]] diye bakmak ve \xf6yle [[muhakeme etmek|de\u011ferlendirmek]], [[\u015f\u0131kk-\u0131 muhalifi|kar\u015f\u0131 se\xe7ene\u011fi]] esas tutmakt\u0131r. [[B\xe2t\u0131l\u0131|Do\u011fru olmayan\u0131]] [[iltizamd\u0131r|taraf\u0131n\u0131 tutmakt\u0131r]], [[b\xeetarafane|tarafs\u0131zca]] de\u011fildir, belki [[b\xe2t\u0131la|yanl\u0131\u015f olana]] [[tarafgirliktir|taraf tutmakt\u0131r]].\\n\\n\u015eeytan dedi ki:\\n\\n\xd6yle ise ne Allah\u2019\u0131n [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] ne de [[be\u015ferin|insan\u0131n]] [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] deme. Ortada [[farz et|varsay]], bak.\\n\\nBen dedim:\\n\\nO da olamaz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[m\xfcn\xe2zaun f\xeeh|anla\u015fmazl\u0131k konusu]] bir mal bulunsa e\u011fer iki [[m\xfcdde\xee|iddia sahibi|davac\u0131]] birbirine yak\u0131n ise ve [[kurbiyet-i mek\xe2n|mekan yak\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131]] varsa; o vakit o mal, ikisinden ba\u015fka birinin elinde veya ikisinin elleri yeti\u015fecek bir surette bir yere b\u0131rak\u0131lacak. Hangisi ispat etse o al\u0131r. E\u011fer o iki [[m\xfcdde\xee|iddia sahibi]] birbirinden gayet uzak, biri [[ma\u015fr\u0131kta|do\u011fuda]], biri [[ma\u011fribde|bat\u0131da]] ise o vakit [[kaideten|kural gere\u011fi]] [[sahib\xfc\u2019l-yed|mal\u0131n elinde bulundu\u011fu ki\u015fi]] kim ise onun elinde b\u0131rak\u0131lacakt\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ortada b\u0131rakmak [[kabil|m\xfcmk\xfcn]] de\u011fildir.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte Kur\u2019an [[k\u0131ymettar|de\u011ferli]] bir mald\u0131r. [[Be\u015fer|\u0130nsan]] [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] [[Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019\u0131n|Allah\'\u0131n]] [[kel\xe2m\u0131ndan|s\xf6z\xfcnden]] ne kadar uzaksa o iki taraf o kadar, belki hadsiz birbirinden uzakt\u0131r. \u0130\u015fte, [[ser\xe2dan|topraktan|yerden]] [[s\xfcreyyaya|\xdclker y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131na|g\xf6\u011fe]] kadar birbirinden uzak o iki taraf ortas\u0131nda b\u0131rakmak m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fildir. Hem ortas\u0131 yoktur. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[v\xfccud|varl\u0131k]] ve [[adem|yokluk]] gibi ve [[nak\xeezeyn|birbirinin z\u0131dd\u0131 olan iki \u015fey]] gibi iki z\u0131tt\u0131rlar. Ortas\u0131 olamaz.\\n\\n\xd6yle ise Kur\u2019an i\xe7in [[sahib\xfc\u2019l-yed|as\u0131l sahibi]], [[taraf-\u0131 \u0130lah\xeedir|Allah taraf\u0131d\u0131r]]. \xd6yle ise onun elinde kabul edilip \xf6ylece [[delail-i ispata|ispat delillerine]] bak\u0131lacak. E\u011fer \xf6teki taraf onun [[kel\xe2mullah|Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfc]] oldu\u011funa dair b\xfct\xfcn [[b\xfcrhanlar\u0131|delilleri|kan\u0131tlar\u0131]] birer birer \xe7\xfcr\xfctse elini ona uzatabilir. Yoksa uzatamaz. Heyhat! Binler [[berahin-i kat\u2019iyenin|kesin delillerin]] m\u0131hlar\u0131yla [[ar\u015f-\u0131 a\u2019zama|en y\xfcce makama]] \xe7ak\u0131lan bu muazzam p\u0131rlantay\u0131 hangi el b\xfct\xfcn o m\u0131hlar\u0131 s\xf6k\xfcp o direkleri kesip onu d\xfc\u015f\xfcrebilir?","modernText":"\u0130\u015fte y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi h\xfckm\xfcnde olan kafa fenerine [[g\xfcvenen|itimat eden|]] ve Kur\u2019an g\xfcne\u015finden g\xf6z\xfcn\xfc yuman kozmo\u011frafyac\u0131 efendi! \u015eu yedi basamaklarda i\u015faret edilen [[ger\xe7eklere|hakikatlere|]] birden bak. G\xf6z\xfcn\xfc a\xe7, kafa fenerini b\u0131rak, g\xfcnd\xfcz gibi [[mucizelik|i\u2019caz|benzersizlik, insan\u0131 aciz b\u0131rakan s\xf6z sanat\u0131]] \u0131\u015f\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7inde \u015fu \xe2yetin manas\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6r! O \xe2yetin [[g\xf6\u011f\xfcnden|semas\u0131ndan|]] bir [[ger\xe7ek|hakikat|]] y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131 al, senin ba\u015f\u0131ndaki \u015feytana at, kendi \u015feytan\u0131n\u0131 [[ta\u015fla|recmet|kov, uzakla\u015ft\u0131r]]! Biz dahi etmeliyiz ve [[Rabbim! \u015eeytanlar\u0131n k\u0131\u015fk\u0131rtmalar\u0131ndan Sana s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131r\u0131m (M\xfc\'min\xfbn, 23/97)|\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|]] beraber demeliyiz. [[\xdcst\xfcn delil ve kesin hikmet Allah\'\u0131nd\u0131r (En\'\xe2m, 6/149)|\u0641\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u062c\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u063a\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u0650\u0643\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0650\u0639\u064e\u0629\u064f|]]\\n\\n[[Seni her t\xfcrl\xfc eksiklikten tenzih ederiz. Senin bize \xf6\u011fretti\u011finden ba\u015fka bizim hi\xe7bir bilgimiz yoktur. \u015e\xfcphesiz her \u015feyi hakk\u0131yla bilen ve her i\u015fi hikmetle yapan Sensin (Bakara, 2/32)|\u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0643\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0643\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f|]]\\n\\n***\\n\\nOn Be\u015finci S\xf6z\u2019\xfcn [[Eki|Zeyli|\u0130lavesi]]\\n\\nYirmi Alt\u0131nc\u0131 Mektup\u2019un Birinci [[B\xf6l\xfcm\xfc|Mebhas\u0131|Bahsi, konusu]]\\n\\n[[O\'nu eksikliklerden tenzih ederiz ki, O\'nun ismiyle ba\u015flar\u0131m; hi\xe7bir \u015fey yoktur ki O\'nu hamd ile tesbih etmesin (\u0130sr\xe2, 17/44)|\u0628\u0650\u0627\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u0649\u0652\u0621\u064d \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u064a\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651\u062d\u064f \u0628\u0650\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0647\u0656|]]\\n\\n[[Rahm\xe2n ve Rah\xeem olan Allah\'\u0131n ad\u0131yla|\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|]]\\n\\n[[E\u011fer \u015feytandan bir k\u0131\u015fk\u0131rtma seni d\xfcrtecek olursa, hemen Allah\'a s\u0131\u011f\u0131n. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc O, her \u015feyi i\u015fitendir, her \u015feyi bilendir (Fussilet, 41/36)|\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0646\u0652z\u064e\u063a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0646\u064e\u0632\u0652\u063a\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0639\u0650\u0630\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0639\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f|]]\\n\\n[[Kur\'an\'\u0131n delili|H\xfcccet\xfc\u2019l-Kur\u2019an|]] [[\u015eeytana kar\u015f\u0131|Ale\u2019\u015f-\u015feytan|]] ve [[Onun taraftarlar\u0131na|Hizbihi|]]\\n\\n\u0130blisi [[susturan|ilzam|susturmak, cevap veremez hale getirmek]], \u015feytan\u0131 [[susturan|ifham|delil ile a\u011fz\u0131n\u0131 kapamak]], [[azg\u0131nlar\u0131|ehl-i tu\u011fyan\u0131|haktan sapanlar\u0131]] [[susturan|isk\xe2t eden|]] Birinci [[B\xf6l\xfcm|Mebhas|]]; [[tarafs\u0131zca|b\xeetarafane|]] [[yarg\u0131lama|muhakeme|zihinsel de\u011ferlendirme]] i\xe7inde \u015feytan\u0131n m\xfcthi\u015f bir [[tuza\u011f\u0131n\u0131|desisesini|hile ve aldatmacas\u0131n\u0131]] [[kesin|kat\u2019\xee|]] bir surette reddeden bir [[olayd\u0131r|vak\u0131ad\u0131r|]]. O [[olay\u0131n|vak\u0131an\u0131n|]] [[k\u0131sa ve \xf6z|m\xfccmel|]] bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 on sene evvel Lemaat\u2019ta yazm\u0131\u015ft\u0131m. \u015e\xf6yle ki:\\n\\nBu risalenin [[yaz\u0131lmas\u0131ndan|telifinden|]] on bir sene evvel [[m\xfcbarek ramazan ay\u0131nda|ramazan-\u0131 \u015ferifte|]] \u0130stanbul\u2019da Bayezid [[M\xfcbarek Camisi\'nde|Cami-i \u015eerifi\u2019nde|]] [[Kur\'an\'\u0131 ezbere okuyanlar\u0131|h\xe2f\u0131zlar\u0131|]] dinliyordum. Birden \u015fahs\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6rmedim fakat [[ruhsal|manev\xee|]] bir ses i\u015fittim gibi bana geldi. Zihnimi kendine \xe7evirdi. Hayalen dinledim.\\n\\nBakt\u0131m ki bana der:\\n\\nSen Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 pek [[y\xfcce|\xe2l\xee|]], \xe7ok parlak g\xf6r\xfcyorsun. [[Tarafs\u0131zca|B\xeetarafane|]] [[de\u011ferlendir|muhakeme et|]], \xf6yle bak. Yani bir [[insan|be\u015fer|]] [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] [[say|farz et|]], bak. Acaba o [[\xfcst\xfcn \xf6zellikleri|meziyetleri|]], o [[s\xfcsleri|ziynetleri|g\xfczellikleri]] g\xf6recek misin?\\n\\nHakikaten ben de ona aldand\u0131m. [[\u0130nsan|Be\u015fer|]] [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] [[say\u0131p|farz edip|]] \xf6yle bakt\u0131m. G\xf6rd\xfcm ki nas\u0131l Bayezid\u2019in elektrik d\xfc\u011fmesi \xe7evrilip s\xf6nd\xfcr\xfcl\xfcnce ortal\u0131k karanl\u0131\u011fa d\xfc\u015fer. \xd6yle de o [[varsay\u0131m|farz|]] ile Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n parlak \u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131 gizlenmeye ba\u015flad\u0131. O vakit anlad\u0131m ki benim ile konu\u015fan \u015feytand\u0131r. Beni [[tehlikeli u\xe7uruma|vartaya|hataya, tuza\u011fa]] yuvarland\u0131r\u0131yor. Kur\u2019an\u2019dan [[yard\u0131m istedim|istimdad ettim|]]. Birden bir nur kalbime geldi. [[Savunmaya|M\xfcdafaaya|]] [[kesin|kat\u2019\xee|]] bir kuvvet verdi. O vakit \u015f\xf6ylece \u015feytana kar\u015f\u0131 [[kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131kl\u0131 tart\u0131\u015fma|m\xfcnazara|]] ba\u015flad\u0131.\\n\\nDedim:\\n\\nEy \u015feytan! [[Tarafs\u0131zca|B\xeetarafane|]] [[yarg\u0131lama|muhakeme|]], iki taraf ortas\u0131nda bir vaziyettir. Halbuki hem senin hem insandaki senin [[\xf6\u011frencilerin|\u015fakirdlerin|takip\xe7ilerin]], dedi\u011finiz [[tarafs\u0131zca|b\xeetarafane|]] [[yarg\u0131lama|muhakeme|]] ise [[kar\u015f\u0131 taraf\u0131|taraf-\u0131 muhalifi|]] [[taraf\u0131n\u0131 tutmakt\u0131r|iltizamd\u0131r|kabullenmektir]], [[tarafs\u0131zl\u0131k|b\xeetarafl\u0131k|]] de\u011fildir. [[Ge\xe7ici olarak|Muvakkaten|]] bir dinsizliktir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc Kur\u2019an\u2019a [[insan s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer|]] diye bakmak ve \xf6yle [[de\u011ferlendirmek|muhakeme etmek|]], [[kar\u015f\u0131 se\xe7ene\u011fi|\u015f\u0131kk-\u0131 muhalifi|]] esas tutmakt\u0131r. [[Do\u011fru olmayan\u0131|B\xe2t\u0131l\u0131|]] [[taraf\u0131n\u0131 tutmakt\u0131r|iltizamd\u0131r|]], [[tarafs\u0131zca|b\xeetarafane|]] de\u011fildir, belki [[yanl\u0131\u015f olana|b\xe2t\u0131la|]] [[taraf tutmakt\u0131r|tarafgirliktir|]].\\n\\n\u015eeytan dedi ki:\\n\\n\xd6yle ise ne Allah\u2019\u0131n [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] ne de [[insan\u0131n|be\u015ferin|]] [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] deme. Ortada [[varsay|farz et|]], bak.\\n\\nBen dedim:\\n\\nO da olamaz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[anla\u015fmazl\u0131k konusu|m\xfcn\xe2zaun f\xeeh|]] bir mal bulunsa e\u011fer iki [[iddia sahibi|m\xfcdde\xee|davac\u0131]] birbirine yak\u0131n ise ve [[mekan yak\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131|kurbiyet-i mek\xe2n|]] varsa; o vakit o mal, ikisinden ba\u015fka birinin elinde veya ikisinin elleri yeti\u015fecek bir surette bir yere b\u0131rak\u0131lacak. Hangisi ispat etse o al\u0131r. E\u011fer o iki [[iddia sahibi|m\xfcdde\xee|]] birbirinden gayet uzak, biri [[do\u011fuda|ma\u015fr\u0131kta|]], biri [[bat\u0131da|ma\u011fribde|]] ise o vakit [[kural gere\u011fi|kaideten|]] [[mal\u0131n elinde bulundu\u011fu ki\u015fi|sahib\xfc\u2019l-yed|]] kim ise onun elinde b\u0131rak\u0131lacakt\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ortada b\u0131rakmak [[m\xfcmk\xfcn|kabil|]] de\u011fildir.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte Kur\u2019an [[de\u011ferli|k\u0131ymettar|]] bir mald\u0131r. [[\u0130nsan|Be\u015fer|]] [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] [[Allah\'\u0131n|Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019\u0131n|]] [[s\xf6z\xfcnden|kel\xe2m\u0131ndan|]] ne kadar uzaksa o iki taraf o kadar, belki hadsiz birbirinden uzakt\u0131r. \u0130\u015fte, [[topraktan|ser\xe2dan|yerden]] [[\xdclker y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131na|s\xfcreyyaya|g\xf6\u011fe]] kadar birbirinden uzak o iki taraf ortas\u0131nda b\u0131rakmak m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fildir. Hem ortas\u0131 yoktur. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[varl\u0131k|v\xfccud|]] ve [[yokluk|adem|]] gibi ve [[birbirinin z\u0131dd\u0131 olan iki \u015fey|nak\xeezeyn|]] gibi iki z\u0131tt\u0131rlar. Ortas\u0131 olamaz.\\n\\n\xd6yle ise Kur\u2019an i\xe7in [[as\u0131l sahibi|sahib\xfc\u2019l-yed|]], [[Allah taraf\u0131d\u0131r|taraf-\u0131 \u0130lah\xeedir|]]. \xd6yle ise onun elinde kabul edilip \xf6ylece [[ispat delillerine|delail-i ispata|]] bak\u0131lacak. E\u011fer \xf6teki taraf onun [[Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2mullah|]] oldu\u011funa dair b\xfct\xfcn [[delilleri|b\xfcrhanlar\u0131|kan\u0131tlar\u0131]] birer birer \xe7\xfcr\xfctse elini ona uzatabilir. Yoksa uzatamaz. Heyhat! Binler [[kesin delillerin|berahin-i kat\u2019iyenin|]] m\u0131hlar\u0131yla [[en y\xfcce makama|ar\u015f-\u0131 a\u2019zama|]] \xe7ak\u0131lan bu muazzam p\u0131rlantay\u0131 hangi el b\xfct\xfcn o m\u0131hlar\u0131 s\xf6k\xfcp o direkleri kesip onu d\xfc\u015f\xfcrebilir?","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.21-19:17","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"},{"pageId":6,"rawText":"\u0130\u015fte ey \u015feytan! Senin ra\u011fm\u0131na ehl-i hak ve insaf bu suretteki hakikatli muhakeme ile muhakeme ederler. Hatt\xe2 en k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir delilde dahi Kur\u2019an\u2019a kar\u015f\u0131 imanlar\u0131n\u0131 ziyadele\u015ftirirler.\\n\\nSenin ve \u015fakirdlerinin g\xf6sterdi\u011fi yol ise: Bir kere be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131 farz edilse yani ar\u015fa ba\u011flanan o muazzam p\u0131rlanta yere at\u0131lsa; b\xfct\xfcn m\u0131hlar\u0131n kuvvetinde ve \xe7ok b\xfcrhanlar\u0131n metanetinde bir tek b\xfcrhan l\xe2z\u0131m ki onu yerden kald\u0131r\u0131p ar\u015f-\u0131 manev\xeeye \xe7aks\u0131n. T\xe2 k\xfcfr\xfcn zul\xfcmat\u0131ndan kurtulup iman\u0131n envar\u0131na eri\u015fsin. Halbuki buna muvaffak olmak pek g\xfc\xe7t\xfcr. Onun i\xe7in senin desisen ile \u015fu zamanda, b\xeetarafane muhakeme sureti alt\u0131nda \xe7oklar\u0131 imanlar\u0131n\u0131 kaybediyorlar.\\n\\n\u015eeytan d\xf6nd\xfc ve dedi:\\n\\nKur\u2019an be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131na benziyor. Onlar\u0131n muhaveresi tarz\u0131ndad\u0131r. Demek, be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131d\u0131r. E\u011fer Allah\u2019\u0131n kel\xe2m\u0131 olsa ona yak\u0131\u015facak, her cihet\xe7e h\xe2rikul\xe2de bir tarz\u0131 olacakt\u0131. Onun sanat\u0131 nas\u0131l be\u015fer sanat\u0131na benzemiyor, kel\xe2m\u0131 da benzememeli?\\n\\nCevaben dedim:\\n\\nNas\u0131l ki Peygamberimiz (asm) mu\u2019cizat\u0131ndan ve hasaisinden ba\u015fka, ef\u2019al ve ahval ve etvar\u0131nda be\u015feriyette kal\u0131p be\u015fer gibi \xe2det-i \u0130lahiyeye ve evamir-i tekviniyesine m\xfcnkad ve mut\xee olmu\u015f. O da so\u011fuk \xe7eker, elem \xe7eker ve h\xe2keza\u2026 Her bir ahval ve etvar\u0131nda h\xe2rikul\xe2de bir vaziyet verilmemi\u015f. T\xe2 ki \xfcmmetine ef\u2019aliyle imam olsun, etvar\u0131yla rehber olsun, umum harek\xe2t\u0131yla ders versin. E\u011fer her etvar\u0131nda h\xe2rikul\xe2de olsa idi, bizzat her cihet\xe7e imam olamazd\u0131. Herkese m\xfcr\u015fid-i mutlak olamazd\u0131. B\xfct\xfcn ahvaliyle Rahmeten li\u2019l-\xe2lem\xeen olamazd\u0131.\\n\\nAynen \xf6yle de Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem ehl-i \u015fuura imamd\u0131r, cin ve inse m\xfcr\u015fiddir, ehl-i kemale rehberdir, ehl-i hakikate muallimdir. \xd6yle ise be\u015ferin muhaverat\u0131 ve \xfcslubu tarz\u0131nda olmak zarur\xee ve kat\u2019\xeedir.\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc cin ve ins m\xfcn\xe2cat\u0131n\u0131 ondan al\u0131yor, duas\u0131n\u0131 ondan \xf6\u011freniyor, mesailini onun lisan\u0131yla zikrediyor, edeb-i mua\u015fereti ondan taall\xfcm ediyor ve h\xe2keza\u2026 Herkes onu merci yap\u0131yor.\\n\\n\xd6yle ise e\u011fer Hazret-i Musa aleyhissel\xe2m\u0131n T\xfbr-i Sina\u2019da i\u015fitti\u011fi kel\xe2mullah tarz\u0131nda olsa idi, be\u015fer bunu dinlemekte ve i\u015fitmekte tahamm\xfcl edemezdi ve merci edemezdi. Hazret-i Musa aleyhissel\xe2m gibi bir ul\xfc\u2019l-azm ancak birka\xe7 kel\xe2m\u0131 i\u015fitmeye tahamm\xfcl etmi\u015ftir. Musa aleyhissel\xe2m demi\u015f: \u0627\u064e\u0647\u0670\u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0643\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f\u0643\u064e \u061f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f : \u0644\u0656\u0649 \u0642\u064f\u0648\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064f \u062c\u064e\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0639\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0633\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0629\u0650\\n\\n\u015eeytan yine d\xf6nd\xfc, dedi ki:\\n\\nKur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n mesaili gibi \xe7ok zatlar o \xe7e\u015fit mesaili din nam\u0131na s\xf6yl\xfcyorlar. Onun i\xe7in bir be\u015fer, din nam\u0131na b\xf6yle bir \u015fey yapmak m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fil mi?\\n\\nCevaben Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n nuruyla dedim ki:\\n\\nEvvela: Dindar bir adam din muhabbeti i\xe7in \u201cHak b\xf6yledir. Hakikat budur. Allah\u2019\u0131n emri b\xf6yledir.\u201d der. Yoksa Allah\u2019\u0131 kendi keyfine konu\u015fturmaz. Hadsiz derece haddinden tecav\xfcz edip Allah\u2019\u0131n taklidini yap\u0131p onun yerinde konu\u015fmaz. \u0641\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0638\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0645\u0651\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 d\xfcsturundan titrer.\\n\\nVe s\xe2niyen: Bir be\u015fer kendi ba\u015f\u0131na b\xf6yle yapmas\u0131 ve muvaffak olmas\u0131 hi\xe7bir cihetle m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fildir. Belki y\xfcz derece muhaldir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc birbirine yak\u0131n zatlar birbirini taklit edebilirler. Bir cinsten olanlar, birbirinin suretine girebilirler. Mertebece birbirine yak\u0131n olanlar, birbirinin makamlar\u0131n\u0131 taklit edebilirler. Muvakkaten insanlar\u0131 i\u011ffal ederler fakat daim\xee i\u011ffal edemezler. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ehl-i dikkat nazar\u0131nda al\xe2k\xfcllihal etvar ve ahvali i\xe7indeki tasannuatlar ve tekell\xfcfatlar sahtek\xe2rl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterecek, hilesi devam etmeyecek.\\n\\nE\u011fer sahtek\xe2rl\u0131kla taklide \xe7al\u0131\u015fan; \xf6tekinden gayet uzaksa mesela, \xe2di bir adam, \u0130bn-i Sina gibi bir d\xe2h\xeeyi ilimde taklit etmek istese ve bir \xe7oban bir padi\u015fah\u0131n vaziyetini tak\u0131nsa elbette hi\xe7 kimseyi aldatamayacak. Belki kendi maskara olacak. Her bir hali ba\u011f\u0131racak ki: Bu sahtek\xe2rd\u0131r!","oldText":"\u0130\u015fte ey \u015feytan! Senin [[ra\u011fm\u0131na|inat/kar\u015f\u0131|bir \u015feye ra\u011fmen, onun aksine, z\u0131dd\u0131na]] [[ehl-i hak ve insaf|hak ve insaf sahipleri|do\u011fruyu ve adaleti g\xf6zeten kimseler]] bu [[suretteki|bi\xe7imdeki/\u015fekildeki]] hakikatli [[muhakeme|yarg\u0131lama/ak\u0131l y\xfcr\xfctme]] ile [[muhakeme ederler|yarg\u0131larlar/de\u011ferlendirirler]]. Hatt\xe2 en k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir delilde dahi Kur\u2019an\u2019a kar\u015f\u0131 imanlar\u0131n\u0131 [[ziyadele\u015ftirirler|art\u0131r\u0131rlar]].\\n\\nSenin ve [[\u015fakirdlerinin|\xf6\u011frencilerinin/takip\xe7ilerinin]] g\xf6sterdi\u011fi yol ise: Bir kere [[be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131|insan s\xf6z\xfc]] [[farz edilse|varsay\u0131lsa/kabul edilse]] yani [[ar\u015fa|g\xf6\u011f\xfcn en y\xfcksek kat\u0131na/Allah\'\u0131n kudret makam\u0131na]] ba\u011flanan o [[muazzam|\xe7ok b\xfcy\xfck/ulu]] p\u0131rlanta yere at\u0131lsa; b\xfct\xfcn m\u0131hlar\u0131n kuvvetinde ve \xe7ok [[b\xfcrhanlar\u0131n|delillerin/kan\u0131tlar\u0131n]] [[metanetinde|sa\u011flaml\u0131\u011f\u0131nda/dayan\u0131kl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda]] bir tek [[b\xfcrhan|delil/kan\u0131t]] l\xe2z\u0131m ki onu yerden kald\u0131r\u0131p [[ar\u015f-\u0131 manev\xeeye|manevi ar\u015fa/y\xfcce makama]] \xe7aks\u0131n. T\xe2 [[k\xfcfr\xfcn|inkar\u0131n/inan\xe7s\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n]] [[zul\xfcmat\u0131ndan|karanl\u0131klar\u0131ndan]] kurtulup iman\u0131n [[envar\u0131na|nurlar\u0131na/\u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131na]] eri\u015fsin. Halbuki buna [[muvaffak olmak|ba\u015farmak/\xfcstesinden gelmek]] pek g\xfc\xe7t\xfcr. Onun i\xe7in senin [[desisen|hilen/oyunun|gizli hile, entrika]] ile \u015fu zamanda, [[b\xeetarafane|tarafs\u0131zca]] [[muhakeme|yarg\u0131lama/de\u011ferlendirme]] [[sureti|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfc/bi\xe7imi]] alt\u0131nda \xe7oklar\u0131 imanlar\u0131n\u0131 kaybediyorlar.\\n\\n\u015eeytan d\xf6nd\xfc ve dedi:\\n\\nKur\u2019an [[be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131na|insan s\xf6z\xfcne]] benziyor. Onlar\u0131n [[muhaveresi|kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131kl\u0131 konu\u015fmas\u0131/diyalo\u011fu]] tarz\u0131ndad\u0131r. Demek, [[be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131d\u0131r|insan s\xf6z\xfcd\xfcr]]. E\u011fer Allah\u2019\u0131n [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] olsa ona yak\u0131\u015facak, her [[cihet\xe7e|y\xf6n\xfcyle/a\xe7\u0131dan]] [[h\xe2rikul\xe2de|ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc/e\u015fsiz]] bir tarz\u0131 olacakt\u0131. Onun sanat\u0131 nas\u0131l be\u015fer sanat\u0131na benzemiyor, [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] da benzememeli?\\n\\n[[Cevaben|Cevap olarak]] dedim:\\n\\nNas\u0131l ki Peygamberimiz (asm) [[mu\u2019cizat\u0131ndan|mucizelerinden]] ve [[hasaisinden|kendine has \xf6zelliklerinden/hususiyetlerinden]] ba\u015fka, [[ef\u2019al ve ahval ve etvar\u0131nda|fiilleri, halleri ve tav\u0131rlar\u0131nda|yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u015fler, durumlar\u0131 ve davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131nda]] [[be\u015feriyette|insanl\u0131kta/insanl\u0131k hallerinde]] kal\u0131p be\u015fer gibi [[\xe2det-i \u0130lahiyeye|Allah\'\u0131n kanunlar\u0131na/do\u011fa yasalar\u0131na]] ve [[evamir-i tekviniyesine|yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f emirlerine|Allah\'\u0131n kainata koydu\u011fu fiziksel ve biyolojik yasalara]] [[m\xfcnkad|boyun e\u011fmi\u015f/uymu\u015f]] ve [[mut\xee|itaat eden]] olmu\u015f. O da so\u011fuk \xe7eker, [[elem \xe7eker|ac\u0131 \xe7eker/\xfcz\xfcnt\xfc duyar]] ve [[h\xe2keza|bunun gibi/b\xf6ylece]]\u2026 Her bir [[ahval ve etvar\u0131nda|hallerinde ve tav\u0131rlar\u0131nda]] [[h\xe2rikul\xe2de|ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc]] bir [[vaziyet|durum/hal]] verilmemi\u015f. T\xe2 ki \xfcmmetine [[ef\u2019aliyle|fiilleriyle/davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131yla]] imam olsun, [[etvar\u0131yla|tav\u0131rlar\u0131yla]] rehber olsun, [[umum|b\xfct\xfcn/genel]] [[harek\xe2t\u0131yla|hareketleriyle]] ders versin. E\u011fer her [[etvar\u0131nda|tav\u0131rlar\u0131nda]] [[h\xe2rikul\xe2de|ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc]] olsa idi, bizzat her [[cihet\xe7e|y\xf6n\xfcyle]] imam olamazd\u0131. Herkese [[m\xfcr\u015fid-i mutlak|kusursuz yol g\xf6sterici/mutlak rehber]] olamazd\u0131. B\xfct\xfcn [[ahvaliyle|halleriyle/durumlar\u0131yla]] [[Rahmeten li\u2019l-\xe2lem\xeen|\xc2lemlere Rahmet]] olamazd\u0131.\\n\\nAynen \xf6yle de [[Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem|hikmetli Kur\'an]] [[ehl-i \u015fuura|bilin\xe7 sahiplerine/ak\u0131l sahiplerine]] imamd\u0131r, cin ve [[inse|insanlara]] [[m\xfcr\u015fiddir|yol g\xf6stericidir]], [[ehl-i kemale|olgunluk sahiplerine/kemal ehline]] rehberdir, [[ehl-i hakikate|hakikat ehline/ger\xe7e\u011fi arayanlara]] [[muallimdir|\xf6\u011fretmendir]]. \xd6yle ise be\u015ferin [[muhaverat\u0131|konu\u015fmalar\u0131/diyaloglar\u0131]] ve \xfcslubu tarz\u0131nda olmak [[zarur\xee|zorunlu/gerekli]] ve [[kat\u2019\xeedir|kesindir]].\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc cin ve [[ins|insan]] [[m\xfcn\xe2cat\u0131n\u0131|yalvar\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131/duas\u0131n\u0131]] ondan al\u0131yor, duas\u0131n\u0131 ondan \xf6\u011freniyor, [[mesailini|meselelerini/konular\u0131n\u0131]] onun lisan\u0131yla [[zikrediyor|an\u0131yor/dile getiriyor]], [[edeb-i mua\u015fereti|g\xf6rg\xfc kurallar\u0131n\u0131/sosyal hayat adab\u0131n\u0131]] ondan [[taall\xfcm ediyor|\xf6\u011freniyor]] ve [[h\xe2keza|bunun gibi]]\u2026 Herkes onu [[merci|ba\u015fvuru kayna\u011f\u0131]] yap\u0131yor.\\n\\n\xd6yle ise e\u011fer Hazret-i Musa aleyhissel\xe2m\u0131n [[T\xfbr-i Sina\u2019da|Sina Da\u011f\u0131\'nda]] i\u015fitti\u011fi [[kel\xe2mullah|Allah kelam\u0131/Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfc]] tarz\u0131nda olsa idi, be\u015fer bunu dinlemekte ve i\u015fitmekte [[tahamm\xfcl edemezdi|dayanamazd\u0131/kald\u0131ramazd\u0131]] ve [[merci edemezdi|ba\u015fvuru kayna\u011f\u0131 yapamazd\u0131]]. Hazret-i Musa aleyhissel\xe2m gibi bir [[ul\xfc\u2019l-azm|azim ve sebat sahibi (peygamber)]] ancak birka\xe7 [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] i\u015fitmeye [[tahamm\xfcl etmi\u015ftir|dayanabilmi\u015ftir]]. Musa aleyhissel\xe2m demi\u015f: [[\u0627\u064e\u0647\u0670\u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0643\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f\u0643\u064e \u061f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f : \u0644\u0656\u0649 \u0642\u064f\u0648\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064f \u062c\u064e\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0639\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0633\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0629\u0650|Senin kelam\u0131n hep b\xf6yle midir? Allah buyurdu: Ben b\xfct\xfcn dillerin kuvvetine sahibim (yani her dille ve tarzla konu\u015fabilirim).|Hadis-i Kudsi meali]]\\n\\n\u015eeytan yine d\xf6nd\xfc, dedi ki:\\n\\nKur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n [[mesaili|meseleleri/konular\u0131]] gibi \xe7ok zatlar o \xe7e\u015fit [[mesaili|meseleleri]] din [[nam\u0131na|ad\u0131na]] s\xf6yl\xfcyorlar. Onun i\xe7in bir be\u015fer, din [[nam\u0131na|ad\u0131na]] b\xf6yle bir \u015fey yapmak m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fil mi?\\n\\n[[Cevaben|Cevap olarak]] Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n nuruyla dedim ki:\\n\\n[[Evvela|\xd6ncelikle/\u0130lk olarak]]: Dindar bir adam din [[muhabbeti|sevgisi]] i\xe7in \u201cHak b\xf6yledir. Hakikat budur. Allah\u2019\u0131n emri b\xf6yledir.\u201d der. Yoksa Allah\u2019\u0131 kendi keyfine konu\u015fturmaz. [[Hadsiz|S\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z/Say\u0131s\u0131z]] derece haddinden [[tecav\xfcz edip|a\u015f\u0131p/sald\u0131r\u0131p]] Allah\u2019\u0131n taklidini yap\u0131p onun yerinde konu\u015fmaz. [[\u0641\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0638\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650|Allah\'a kar\u015f\u0131 yalan uydurandan daha zalim kim olabilir?|Z\xfcmer Suresi, 32. Ayet]] [[d\xfcsturundan|ilkesinden/prensibinden]] titrer.\\n\\nVe [[s\xe2niyen|ikinci olarak]]: Bir be\u015fer kendi ba\u015f\u0131na b\xf6yle yapmas\u0131 ve [[muvaffak olmas\u0131|ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 olmas\u0131]] hi\xe7bir [[cihetle|y\xf6nle/\u015fekilde]] m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fildir. Belki y\xfcz derece [[muhaldir|imkans\u0131zd\u0131r]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc birbirine yak\u0131n zatlar birbirini taklit edebilirler. Bir cinsten olanlar, birbirinin [[suretine|\u015fekline/g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfcne]] girebilirler. [[Mertebece|Derece bak\u0131m\u0131ndan/R\xfctbece]] birbirine yak\u0131n olanlar, birbirinin makamlar\u0131n\u0131 taklit edebilirler. [[Muvakkaten|Ge\xe7ici olarak]] insanlar\u0131 [[i\u011ffal ederler|aldat\u0131rlar/kand\u0131r\u0131rlar]] fakat [[daim\xee|s\xfcrekli]] [[i\u011ffal edemezler|aldatamazlar]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[ehl-i dikkat|dikkat sahipleri]] [[nazar\u0131nda|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda/g\xf6z\xfcnde]] [[al\xe2k\xfcllihal|her hal\xfckarda/ne olursa olsun]] [[etvar ve ahvali|tav\u0131rlar\u0131 ve halleri]] i\xe7indeki [[tasannuatlar|yapmac\u0131k hareketler/sanatl\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcnme \xe7abalar\u0131]] ve [[tekell\xfcfatlar|zorlamalar/k\xfclfetli tav\u0131rlar]] sahtek\xe2rl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterecek, hilesi devam etmeyecek.\\n\\nE\u011fer sahtek\xe2rl\u0131kla taklide \xe7al\u0131\u015fan; \xf6tekinden gayet uzaksa mesela, [[\xe2di|s\u0131radan/basit]] bir adam, \u0130bn-i Sina gibi bir d\xe2h\xeeyi ilimde taklit etmek istese ve bir \xe7oban bir padi\u015fah\u0131n [[vaziyetini tak\u0131nsa|durumunu tak\u0131nsa/tavr\u0131na b\xfcr\xfcnse]] elbette hi\xe7 kimseyi aldatamayacak. Belki kendi maskara olacak. Her bir hali ba\u011f\u0131racak ki: Bu sahtek\xe2rd\u0131r!","modernText":"\u0130\u015fte ey \u015feytan! Senin [[inat/kar\u015f\u0131|ra\u011fm\u0131na|bir \u015feye ra\u011fmen, onun aksine, z\u0131dd\u0131na]] [[hak ve insaf sahipleri|ehl-i hak ve insaf|do\u011fruyu ve adaleti g\xf6zeten kimseler]] bu [[bi\xe7imdeki/\u015fekildeki|suretteki|]] hakikatli [[yarg\u0131lama/ak\u0131l y\xfcr\xfctme|muhakeme|]] ile [[yarg\u0131larlar/de\u011ferlendirirler|muhakeme ederler|]]. Hatt\xe2 en k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir delilde dahi Kur\u2019an\u2019a kar\u015f\u0131 imanlar\u0131n\u0131 [[art\u0131r\u0131rlar|ziyadele\u015ftirirler|]].\\n\\nSenin ve [[\xf6\u011frencilerinin/takip\xe7ilerinin|\u015fakirdlerinin|]] g\xf6sterdi\u011fi yol ise: Bir kere [[insan s\xf6z\xfc|be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131|]] [[varsay\u0131lsa/kabul edilse|farz edilse|]] yani [[g\xf6\u011f\xfcn en y\xfcksek kat\u0131na/Allah\'\u0131n kudret makam\u0131na|ar\u015fa|]] ba\u011flanan o [[\xe7ok b\xfcy\xfck/ulu|muazzam|]] p\u0131rlanta yere at\u0131lsa; b\xfct\xfcn m\u0131hlar\u0131n kuvvetinde ve \xe7ok [[delillerin/kan\u0131tlar\u0131n|b\xfcrhanlar\u0131n|]] [[sa\u011flaml\u0131\u011f\u0131nda/dayan\u0131kl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda|metanetinde|]] bir tek [[delil/kan\u0131t|b\xfcrhan|]] l\xe2z\u0131m ki onu yerden kald\u0131r\u0131p [[manevi ar\u015fa/y\xfcce makama|ar\u015f-\u0131 manev\xeeye|]] \xe7aks\u0131n. T\xe2 [[inkar\u0131n/inan\xe7s\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n|k\xfcfr\xfcn|]] [[karanl\u0131klar\u0131ndan|zul\xfcmat\u0131ndan|]] kurtulup iman\u0131n [[nurlar\u0131na/\u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131na|envar\u0131na|]] eri\u015fsin. Halbuki buna [[ba\u015farmak/\xfcstesinden gelmek|muvaffak olmak|]] pek g\xfc\xe7t\xfcr. Onun i\xe7in senin [[hilen/oyunun|desisen|gizli hile, entrika]] ile \u015fu zamanda, [[tarafs\u0131zca|b\xeetarafane|]] [[yarg\u0131lama/de\u011ferlendirme|muhakeme|]] [[g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfc/bi\xe7imi|sureti|]] alt\u0131nda \xe7oklar\u0131 imanlar\u0131n\u0131 kaybediyorlar.\\n\\n\u015eeytan d\xf6nd\xfc ve dedi:\\n\\nKur\u2019an [[insan s\xf6z\xfcne|be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131na|]] benziyor. Onlar\u0131n [[kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131kl\u0131 konu\u015fmas\u0131/diyalo\u011fu|muhaveresi|]] tarz\u0131ndad\u0131r. Demek, [[insan s\xf6z\xfcd\xfcr|be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131d\u0131r|]]. E\u011fer Allah\u2019\u0131n [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] olsa ona yak\u0131\u015facak, her [[y\xf6n\xfcyle/a\xe7\u0131dan|cihet\xe7e|]] [[ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc/e\u015fsiz|h\xe2rikul\xe2de|]] bir tarz\u0131 olacakt\u0131. Onun sanat\u0131 nas\u0131l be\u015fer sanat\u0131na benzemiyor, [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] da benzememeli?\\n\\n[[Cevap olarak|Cevaben|]] dedim:\\n\\nNas\u0131l ki Peygamberimiz (asm) [[mucizelerinden|mu\u2019cizat\u0131ndan|]] ve [[kendine has \xf6zelliklerinden/hususiyetlerinden|hasaisinden|]] ba\u015fka, [[fiilleri, halleri ve tav\u0131rlar\u0131nda|ef\u2019al ve ahval ve etvar\u0131nda|yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u015fler, durumlar\u0131 ve davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131nda]] [[insanl\u0131kta/insanl\u0131k hallerinde|be\u015feriyette|]] kal\u0131p be\u015fer gibi [[Allah\'\u0131n kanunlar\u0131na/do\u011fa yasalar\u0131na|\xe2det-i \u0130lahiyeye|]] ve [[yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f emirlerine|evamir-i tekviniyesine|Allah\'\u0131n kainata koydu\u011fu fiziksel ve biyolojik yasalara]] [[boyun e\u011fmi\u015f/uymu\u015f|m\xfcnkad|]] ve [[itaat eden|mut\xee|]] olmu\u015f. O da so\u011fuk \xe7eker, [[ac\u0131 \xe7eker/\xfcz\xfcnt\xfc duyar|elem \xe7eker|]] ve [[bunun gibi/b\xf6ylece|h\xe2keza|]]\u2026 Her bir [[hallerinde ve tav\u0131rlar\u0131nda|ahval ve etvar\u0131nda|]] [[ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc|h\xe2rikul\xe2de|]] bir [[durum/hal|vaziyet|]] verilmemi\u015f. T\xe2 ki \xfcmmetine [[fiilleriyle/davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131yla|ef\u2019aliyle|]] imam olsun, [[tav\u0131rlar\u0131yla|etvar\u0131yla|]] rehber olsun, [[b\xfct\xfcn/genel|umum|]] [[hareketleriyle|harek\xe2t\u0131yla|]] ders versin. E\u011fer her [[tav\u0131rlar\u0131nda|etvar\u0131nda|]] [[ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc|h\xe2rikul\xe2de|]] olsa idi, bizzat her [[y\xf6n\xfcyle|cihet\xe7e|]] imam olamazd\u0131. Herkese [[kusursuz yol g\xf6sterici/mutlak rehber|m\xfcr\u015fid-i mutlak|]] olamazd\u0131. B\xfct\xfcn [[halleriyle/durumlar\u0131yla|ahvaliyle|]] [[\xc2lemlere Rahmet|Rahmeten li\u2019l-\xe2lem\xeen|]] olamazd\u0131.\\n\\nAynen \xf6yle de [[hikmetli Kur\'an|Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem|]] [[bilin\xe7 sahiplerine/ak\u0131l sahiplerine|ehl-i \u015fuura|]] imamd\u0131r, cin ve [[insanlara|inse|]] [[yol g\xf6stericidir|m\xfcr\u015fiddir|]], [[olgunluk sahiplerine/kemal ehline|ehl-i kemale|]] rehberdir, [[hakikat ehline/ger\xe7e\u011fi arayanlara|ehl-i hakikate|]] [[\xf6\u011fretmendir|muallimdir|]]. \xd6yle ise be\u015ferin [[konu\u015fmalar\u0131/diyaloglar\u0131|muhaverat\u0131|]] ve \xfcslubu tarz\u0131nda olmak [[zorunlu/gerekli|zarur\xee|]] ve [[kesindir|kat\u2019\xeedir|]].\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc cin ve [[insan|ins|]] [[yalvar\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131/duas\u0131n\u0131|m\xfcn\xe2cat\u0131n\u0131|]] ondan al\u0131yor, duas\u0131n\u0131 ondan \xf6\u011freniyor, [[meselelerini/konular\u0131n\u0131|mesailini|]] onun lisan\u0131yla [[an\u0131yor/dile getiriyor|zikrediyor|]], [[g\xf6rg\xfc kurallar\u0131n\u0131/sosyal hayat adab\u0131n\u0131|edeb-i mua\u015fereti|]] ondan [[\xf6\u011freniyor|taall\xfcm ediyor|]] ve [[bunun gibi|h\xe2keza|]]\u2026 Herkes onu [[ba\u015fvuru kayna\u011f\u0131|merci|]] yap\u0131yor.\\n\\n\xd6yle ise e\u011fer Hazret-i Musa aleyhissel\xe2m\u0131n [[Sina Da\u011f\u0131\'nda|T\xfbr-i Sina\u2019da|]] i\u015fitti\u011fi [[Allah kelam\u0131/Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2mullah|]] tarz\u0131nda olsa idi, be\u015fer bunu dinlemekte ve i\u015fitmekte [[dayanamazd\u0131/kald\u0131ramazd\u0131|tahamm\xfcl edemezdi|]] ve [[ba\u015fvuru kayna\u011f\u0131 yapamazd\u0131|merci edemezdi|]]. Hazret-i Musa aleyhissel\xe2m gibi bir [[azim ve sebat sahibi (peygamber)|ul\xfc\u2019l-azm|]] ancak birka\xe7 [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] i\u015fitmeye [[dayanabilmi\u015ftir|tahamm\xfcl etmi\u015ftir|]]. Musa aleyhissel\xe2m demi\u015f: [[Senin kelam\u0131n hep b\xf6yle midir? Allah buyurdu: Ben b\xfct\xfcn dillerin kuvvetine sahibim (yani her dille ve tarzla konu\u015fabilirim).|\u0627\u064e\u0647\u0670\u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0643\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f\u0643\u064e \u061f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f : \u0644\u0656\u0649 \u0642\u064f\u0648\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064f \u062c\u064e\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0639\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0633\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0629\u0650|Hadis-i Kudsi meali]]\\n\\n\u015eeytan yine d\xf6nd\xfc, dedi ki:\\n\\nKur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n [[meseleleri/konular\u0131|mesaili|]] gibi \xe7ok zatlar o \xe7e\u015fit [[meseleleri|mesaili|]] din [[ad\u0131na|nam\u0131na|]] s\xf6yl\xfcyorlar. Onun i\xe7in bir be\u015fer, din [[ad\u0131na|nam\u0131na|]] b\xf6yle bir \u015fey yapmak m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fil mi?\\n\\n[[Cevap olarak|Cevaben|]] Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n nuruyla dedim ki:\\n\\n[[\xd6ncelikle/\u0130lk olarak|Evvela|]]: Dindar bir adam din [[sevgisi|muhabbeti|]] i\xe7in \u201cHak b\xf6yledir. Hakikat budur. Allah\u2019\u0131n emri b\xf6yledir.\u201d der. Yoksa Allah\u2019\u0131 kendi keyfine konu\u015fturmaz. [[S\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z/Say\u0131s\u0131z|Hadsiz|]] derece haddinden [[a\u015f\u0131p/sald\u0131r\u0131p|tecav\xfcz edip|]] Allah\u2019\u0131n taklidini yap\u0131p onun yerinde konu\u015fmaz. [[Allah\'a kar\u015f\u0131 yalan uydurandan daha zalim kim olabilir?|\u0641\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0638\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650|Z\xfcmer Suresi, 32. Ayet]] [[ilkesinden/prensibinden|d\xfcsturundan|]] titrer.\\n\\nVe [[ikinci olarak|s\xe2niyen|]]: Bir be\u015fer kendi ba\u015f\u0131na b\xf6yle yapmas\u0131 ve [[ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 olmas\u0131|muvaffak olmas\u0131|]] hi\xe7bir [[y\xf6nle/\u015fekilde|cihetle|]] m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fildir. Belki y\xfcz derece [[imkans\u0131zd\u0131r|muhaldir|]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc birbirine yak\u0131n zatlar birbirini taklit edebilirler. Bir cinsten olanlar, birbirinin [[\u015fekline/g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfcne|suretine|]] girebilirler. [[Derece bak\u0131m\u0131ndan/R\xfctbece|Mertebece|]] birbirine yak\u0131n olanlar, birbirinin makamlar\u0131n\u0131 taklit edebilirler. [[Ge\xe7ici olarak|Muvakkaten|]] insanlar\u0131 [[aldat\u0131rlar/kand\u0131r\u0131rlar|i\u011ffal ederler|]] fakat [[s\xfcrekli|daim\xee|]] [[aldatamazlar|i\u011ffal edemezler|]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[dikkat sahipleri|ehl-i dikkat|]] [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda/g\xf6z\xfcnde|nazar\u0131nda|]] [[her hal\xfckarda/ne olursa olsun|al\xe2k\xfcllihal|]] [[tav\u0131rlar\u0131 ve halleri|etvar ve ahvali|]] i\xe7indeki [[yapmac\u0131k hareketler/sanatl\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcnme \xe7abalar\u0131|tasannuatlar|]] ve [[zorlamalar/k\xfclfetli tav\u0131rlar|tekell\xfcfatlar|]] sahtek\xe2rl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6sterecek, hilesi devam etmeyecek.\\n\\nE\u011fer sahtek\xe2rl\u0131kla taklide \xe7al\u0131\u015fan; \xf6tekinden gayet uzaksa mesela, [[s\u0131radan/basit|\xe2di|]] bir adam, \u0130bn-i Sina gibi bir d\xe2h\xeeyi ilimde taklit etmek istese ve bir \xe7oban bir padi\u015fah\u0131n [[durumunu tak\u0131nsa/tavr\u0131na b\xfcr\xfcnse|vaziyetini tak\u0131nsa|]] elbette hi\xe7 kimseyi aldatamayacak. Belki kendi maskara olacak. Her bir hali ba\u011f\u0131racak ki: Bu sahtek\xe2rd\u0131r!","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.21-19:17","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"},{"pageId":7,"rawText":"\u0130\u015fte \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2 y\xfcz bin defa h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 Kur\u2019an, be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131 farz edildi\u011fi vakit nas\u0131l ki bir y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi bin sene tekell\xfcfs\xfcz hakiki bir y\u0131ld\u0131z olarak rasad ehline g\xf6r\xfcns\xfcn. Hem bir sinek bir sene tamamen tavus suretini tasannusuz, tema\u015fa ehline g\xf6stersin. Hem sahtek\xe2r, \xe2m\xee bir nefer; namdar, \xe2l\xee bir m\xfc\u015firin tavr\u0131n\u0131 tak\u0131ns\u0131n, makam\u0131nda otursun, \xe7ok zaman \xf6yle kals\u0131n, hilesini ihsas etmesin. Hem m\xfcfteri, yalanc\u0131 itikads\u0131z bir adam; m\xfcddet-i \xf6mr\xfcnde daima en sad\u0131k en emin en mutekid bir zat\u0131n keyfiyetini ve vaziyetini en m\xfcdakkik nazarlara kar\u015f\u0131 tela\u015fs\u0131z g\xf6stersin, d\xe2h\xeelerin nazar\u0131nda tasannuu saklans\u0131n?\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece muhaldir, ona hi\xe7bir z\xeeak\u0131l m\xfcmk\xfcn diyemez ve \xf6yle de farz etmek, bedih\xee bir muhali vaki farz etmek gibi bir hezeyand\u0131r.\\n\\nAynen \xf6yle de Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer farz etmek; l\xe2z\u0131m gelir ki \xe2lem-i \u0130sl\xe2m\u2019\u0131n semas\u0131nda bilm\xfc\u015fahede pek parlak ve daima envar-\u0131 hakaiki ne\u015freden bir y\u0131ld\u0131z-\u0131 hakikat, belki bir \u015fems-i kemal\xe2t telakki edilen Kitab-\u0131 M\xfcbin\u2019in mahiyeti \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 bir y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi h\xfckm\xfcnde tasannucu bir be\u015ferin hurafatl\u0131 bir d\xfczmesi olsun ve en yak\u0131n\u0131nda olanlar ve dikkatle ona bakanlar fark\u0131nda bulunmas\u0131n ve onu daima \xe2l\xee ve menba-\u0131 hakaik bir y\u0131ld\u0131z bilsin.\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece muhal olmakla beraber, sen ey \u015feytan y\xfcz derece \u015feytanetinde ileri gitsen buna imk\xe2n verdiremezsin, bozulmam\u0131\u015f hi\xe7bir akl\u0131 kand\u0131ramazs\u0131n! Yaln\u0131z manen pek uzaktan bakt\u0131rmakla aldat\u0131yorsun! Y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131, y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi gibi k\xfc\xe7\xfck g\xf6steriyorsun.\\n\\nS\xe2lisen: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131 farz etmek, l\xe2z\u0131m gelir ki \xe2s\xe2r\u0131yla, tesirat\u0131yla, netaiciyle \xe2lem-i insaniyetin bilm\xfc\u015fahede en ruhlu ve hayat-fe\u015fan, en hakikatli ve saadet-resan, en cem\u2019iyetli ve mu\u2019ciz-beyan, \xe2l\xee meziyetleriyle yald\u0131zl\u0131 bir Furkan\u2019\u0131n gizli hakikati \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 muavenetsiz, ilimsiz bir tek insan\u0131n fikrinin tasniat\u0131 olsun ve yak\u0131n\u0131nda onu tema\u015fa eden ve merakla dikkat eden b\xfcy\xfck zek\xe2lar, ulvi dehalar onda hi\xe7bir zaman hi\xe7bir cihette sahtek\xe2rl\u0131k ve tasannu eserini g\xf6rmesin; daima ciddiyeti, samimiyeti, ihlas\u0131 bulsun!\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece muhal olmakla beraber, b\xfct\xfcn ahvaliyle, akvaliyle, harek\xe2t\u0131yla b\xfct\xfcn hayat\u0131nda emaneti, iman\u0131, emniyeti, ihlas\u0131, ciddiyeti, istikameti g\xf6steren ve ders veren ve s\u0131dd\u0131k\xeenleri yeti\u015ftiren en y\xfcksek en parlak en \xe2l\xee haslet telakki edilen ve kabul edilen bir zat\u0131; en emniyetsiz en ihlass\u0131z en itikads\u0131z farz etmekle, muzaaf bir muhali vaki g\xf6rmek gibi \u015feytan\u0131 dahi utand\u0131racak bir hezeyan-\u0131 fikr\xeedir.\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc \u015fu meselenin ortas\u0131 yoktur. Zira farz-\u0131 muhal olarak Kur\u2019an, kel\xe2mullah olmazsa ar\u015ftan fer\u015fe d\xfc\u015fer gibi sukut eder. Ortada kalmaz. Mecma-\u0131 hakaik iken, menba-\u0131 hurafat olur. Ve o h\xe2rika ferman\u0131 g\xf6steren zat, h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2 e\u011fer Resulullah olmazsa a\u2019l\xe2-y\u0131 illiyy\xeenden esfel-i safil\xeene sukut etmek ve menba-\u0131 kemal\xe2t derecesinden maden-i desais makam\u0131na d\xfc\u015fmek l\xe2z\u0131m gelir. Ortada kalamaz. Zira Allah nam\u0131na iftira eden, yalan s\xf6yleyen en edna bir dereceye d\xfc\u015fer.\\n\\nBir sine\u011fi, daim\xee bir surette tavus g\xf6rmek ve tavusun b\xfcy\xfck evsaf\u0131n\u0131 onda her vakit m\xfc\u015fahede etmek ne kadar muhal ise \u015fu mesele de \xf6yle muhaldir. F\u0131traten ak\u0131ls\u0131z, sarho\u015f bir divane l\xe2z\u0131m ki buna ihtimal versin.\\n\\nR\xe2bian: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer farz etmek l\xe2z\u0131m gelir ki ben\xee-\xc2dem\u2019in en b\xfcy\xfck ve muhte\u015fem ordusu olan \xfcmmet-i Muhammediyenin (asm) mukaddes bir kumandan\u0131 olan Kur\u2019an, bilm\xfc\u015fahede kuvvetli kanunlar\u0131yla, esasl\u0131 d\xfcsturlar\u0131yla, n\xe2fiz emirleriyle o pek b\xfcy\xfck orduyu, iki cihan\u0131 fethedecek bir derecede bir intizam verdi\u011fi ve bir inzibat alt\u0131na ald\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve madd\xee ve manev\xee te\xe7hiz etti\u011fi ve umum efrad\u0131n derecat\u0131na g\xf6re ak\u0131llar\u0131n\u0131 talim ve kalplerini terbiye ve ruhlar\u0131n\u0131 teshir ve vicdanlar\u0131n\u0131 tathir, aza ve cevarihlerini istimal ve istihdam etti\u011fi halde \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2, y\xfcz bin h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 kuvvetsiz, k\u0131ymetsiz, as\u0131ls\u0131z bir d\xfczme farz edip y\xfcz derece muhali kabul etmek l\xe2z\u0131m gelmekle beraber\u2026","oldText":"\u0130\u015fte \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla/kesinlikle \xf6yle de\u011fil]] y\xfcz bin defa [[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]]\u2013 Kur\u2019an, [[be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131|insan s\xf6z\xfc]] [[farz edildi\u011fi vakit|varsay\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 zaman]] nas\u0131l ki bir [[y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi|ate\u015f b\xf6ce\u011fi]] bin sene [[tekell\xfcfs\xfcz|zorlanmadan/do\u011fal bir \u015fekilde]] [[hakiki|ger\xe7ek]] bir y\u0131ld\u0131z olarak [[rasad ehline|g\xf6zlem yapanlara/astronomlara]] g\xf6r\xfcns\xfcn. Hem bir sinek bir sene tamamen [[tavus suretini|tavus ku\u015fu g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcs\xfcn\xfc]] [[tasannusuz|yapmac\u0131ks\u0131z/sanatl\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcnmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015fmadan]], [[tema\u015fa ehline|seyredenlere/izleyenlere]] g\xf6stersin. Hem sahtek\xe2r, [[\xe2m\xee|s\u0131radan/cahil]] bir [[nefer|asker/er]]; [[namdar|\xfcnl\xfc/naml\u0131]], [[\xe2l\xee|y\xfcce/y\xfcksek]] bir [[m\xfc\u015firin|mare\u015falin/pa\u015fan\u0131n]] tavr\u0131n\u0131 tak\u0131ns\u0131n, makam\u0131nda otursun, \xe7ok zaman \xf6yle kals\u0131n, hilesini [[ihsas etmesin|hissettirmesin/sezdirmesin]]. Hem [[m\xfcfteri|iftirac\u0131]], yalanc\u0131 [[itikads\u0131z|inan\xe7s\u0131z]] bir adam; [[m\xfcddet-i \xf6mr\xfcnde|\xf6mr\xfc boyunca]] daima en [[sad\u0131k|do\u011fru s\xf6zl\xfc]] en [[emin|g\xfcvenilir]] en [[mutekid|inan\xe7l\u0131/imanl\u0131]] bir zat\u0131n [[keyfiyetini|niteli\u011fini/durumunu]] ve [[vaziyetini|halini/durumunu]] en [[m\xfcdakkik|dikkatli/inceleyen]] [[nazarlara|bak\u0131\u015flara]] kar\u015f\u0131 tela\u015fs\u0131z g\xf6stersin, d\xe2h\xeelerin [[nazar\u0131nda|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda/g\xf6z\xfcnde]] [[tasannuu|yapmac\u0131kl\u0131\u011f\u0131/sanatl\u0131 g\xf6sterme \xe7abas\u0131]] saklans\u0131n?\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece [[muhaldir|imkans\u0131zd\u0131r]], ona hi\xe7bir [[z\xeeak\u0131l|ak\u0131l sahibi]] m\xfcmk\xfcn diyemez ve \xf6yle de [[farz etmek|varsaymak]], [[bedih\xee|apa\xe7\u0131k/belli]] bir [[muhali|imkans\u0131z\u0131]] [[vaki|olmu\u015f/ger\xe7ekle\u015fmi\u015f]] [[farz etmek|varsaymak]] gibi bir [[hezeyand\u0131r|sa\xe7mal\u0131k/say\u0131klama]].\\n\\nAynen \xf6yle de Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 [[kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer|insan s\xf6z\xfc]] [[farz etmek|varsaymak]]; [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]] ki [[\xe2lem-i \u0130sl\xe2m\u2019\u0131n|\u0130slam d\xfcnyas\u0131n\u0131n]] semas\u0131nda [[bilm\xfc\u015fahede|g\xf6rerek/g\xf6zlemleyerek]] pek parlak ve daima [[envar-\u0131 hakaiki|hakikat nurlar\u0131n\u0131/ger\xe7eklerin \u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131]] [[ne\u015freden|yayan/sa\xe7an]] bir [[y\u0131ld\u0131z-\u0131 hakikat|hakikat y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131]], belki bir [[\u015fems-i kemal\xe2t|olgunluklar g\xfcne\u015fi/m\xfckemmellikler kayna\u011f\u0131]] [[telakki edilen|kabul edilen/anla\u015f\u0131lan]] [[Kitab-\u0131 M\xfcbin\u2019in|Apa\xe7\u0131k Kitab\u0131n (Kur\'an\'\u0131n)]] [[mahiyeti|i\xe7 y\xfcz\xfc/niteli\u011fi]] \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla ve sonra yine asla]]\u2013 bir [[y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi|ate\u015f b\xf6ce\u011fi]] h\xfckm\xfcnde [[tasannucu|yapmac\u0131k\xe7\u0131/sahte sanat\xe7\u0131]] bir be\u015ferin [[hurafatl\u0131|bat\u0131l inan\xe7l\u0131/uydurma]] bir d\xfczmesi olsun ve en yak\u0131n\u0131nda olanlar ve dikkatle ona bakanlar fark\u0131nda bulunmas\u0131n ve onu daima [[\xe2l\xee|y\xfcce]] ve [[menba-\u0131 hakaik|hakikatlerin kayna\u011f\u0131]] bir y\u0131ld\u0131z bilsin.\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece [[muhal|imkans\u0131z]] olmakla beraber, sen ey \u015feytan y\xfcz derece [[\u015feytanetinde|\u015feytanl\u0131\u011f\u0131nda]] ileri gitsen buna imk\xe2n verdiremezsin, bozulmam\u0131\u015f hi\xe7bir akl\u0131 kand\u0131ramazs\u0131n! Yaln\u0131z [[manen|manevi olarak/hayalen]] pek uzaktan bakt\u0131rmakla aldat\u0131yorsun! Y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131, [[y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi|ate\u015f b\xf6ce\u011fi]] gibi k\xfc\xe7\xfck g\xf6steriyorsun.\\n\\n[[S\xe2lisen|\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc olarak]]: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 be\u015fer [[kel\xe2m\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc]] [[farz etmek|varsaymak]], [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]] ki [[\xe2s\xe2r\u0131yla|eserleriyle]], [[tesirat\u0131yla|etkileriyle]], [[netaiciyle|sonu\xe7lar\u0131yla]] [[\xe2lem-i insaniyetin|insanl\u0131k d\xfcnyas\u0131n\u0131n]] [[bilm\xfc\u015fahede|g\xf6zlemleyerek/apa\xe7\u0131k]] en ruhlu ve [[hayat-fe\u015fan|hayat sa\xe7an/can veren]], en hakikatli ve [[saadet-resan|mutluluk veren/saadet ula\u015ft\u0131ran]], en [[cem\u2019iyetli|kapsaml\u0131/bir\xe7ok hakikati toplayan]] ve [[mu\u2019ciz-beyan|ifadesi mucize olan/s\xf6z\xfc aciz b\u0131rakan]], [[\xe2l\xee|y\xfcce]] [[meziyetleriyle|\xfcst\xfcn \xf6zellikleriyle]] yald\u0131zl\u0131 bir [[Furkan\u2019\u0131n|Hak ile bat\u0131l\u0131 ay\u0131ran Kur\'an\'\u0131n]] gizli hakikati \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]]\u2013 [[muavenetsiz|yard\u0131ms\u0131z]], ilimsiz bir tek insan\u0131n fikrinin [[tasniat\u0131|uydurmas\u0131/yapmas\u0131]] olsun ve yak\u0131n\u0131nda onu [[tema\u015fa eden|seyreden/izleyen]] ve merakla dikkat eden b\xfcy\xfck zek\xe2lar, [[ulvi|y\xfcce]] dehalar onda hi\xe7bir zaman hi\xe7bir [[cihette|y\xf6nde/a\xe7\u0131dan]] sahtek\xe2rl\u0131k ve [[tasannu|yapmac\u0131kl\u0131k]] eserini g\xf6rmesin; daima ciddiyeti, samimiyeti, [[ihlas\u0131|i\xe7tenli\u011fi]] bulsun!\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece [[muhal|imkans\u0131z]] olmakla beraber, b\xfct\xfcn [[ahvaliyle|halleriyle]], [[akvaliyle|s\xf6zleriyle]], [[harek\xe2t\u0131yla|hareketleriyle/davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131yla]] b\xfct\xfcn hayat\u0131nda [[emaneti|g\xfcvenilirli\u011fi]], iman\u0131, [[emniyeti|g\xfcveni]], [[ihlas\u0131|samimiyeti]], ciddiyeti, [[istikameti|do\u011frulu\u011fu]] g\xf6steren ve ders veren ve [[s\u0131dd\u0131k\xeenleri|dosdo\u011fru olanlar\u0131/sad\u0131klar\u0131]] yeti\u015ftiren en y\xfcksek en parlak en [[\xe2l\xee|y\xfcce]] [[haslet|huy/karakter \xf6zelli\u011fi]] [[telakki edilen|kabul edilen]] ve kabul edilen bir zat\u0131; en [[emniyetsiz|g\xfcvensiz]] en [[ihlass\u0131z|samimiyetsiz]] en [[itikads\u0131z|inan\xe7s\u0131z]] [[farz etmekle|varsaymakla]], [[muzaaf|kat kat/katlanm\u0131\u015f]] bir [[muhali|imkans\u0131z\u0131]] [[vaki|olmu\u015f/ger\xe7ekle\u015fmi\u015f]] g\xf6rmek gibi \u015feytan\u0131 dahi utand\u0131racak bir [[hezeyan-\u0131 fikr\xeedir|fikir sa\xe7mal\u0131\u011f\u0131d\u0131r/d\xfc\u015f\xfcnce hezeyan\u0131d\u0131r]].\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc \u015fu meselenin ortas\u0131 yoktur. [[Zira|\xc7\xfcnk\xfc]] [[farz-\u0131 muhal|imkans\u0131z oldu\u011fu halde varsayarak]] olarak Kur\u2019an, [[kel\xe2mullah|Allah kelam\u0131/Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfc]] olmazsa [[ar\u015ftan fer\u015fe|g\xf6\u011f\xfcn en y\xfcksek kat\u0131ndan yery\xfcz\xfcne]] d\xfc\u015fer gibi [[sukut eder|d\xfc\u015fer]]. Ortada kalmaz. [[Mecma-\u0131 hakaik|hakikatlerin toplanma yeri]] iken, [[menba-\u0131 hurafat|hurafelerin kayna\u011f\u0131]] olur. Ve o [[h\xe2rika|harikulade]] [[ferman\u0131|buyru\u011fu (Kur\'an\'\u0131)]] g\xf6steren zat, [[h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla ve sonra yine asla]] e\u011fer [[Resulullah|Allah\'\u0131n El\xe7isi]] olmazsa [[a\u2019l\xe2-y\u0131 illiyy\xeenden|y\xfccelerin en y\xfccesinden/cennetin en y\xfcksek tabakas\u0131ndan]] [[esfel-i safil\xeene|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131lar\u0131n en a\u015fa\u011f\u0131s\u0131na/cehennemin en derin yerine]] [[sukut etmek|d\xfc\u015fmek]] ve [[menba-\u0131 kemal\xe2t|m\xfckemmelliklerin kayna\u011f\u0131]] derecesinden [[maden-i desais|hilelerin kayna\u011f\u0131]] makam\u0131na d\xfc\u015fmek [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]]. Ortada kalamaz. [[Zira|\xc7\xfcnk\xfc]] Allah [[nam\u0131na|ad\u0131na]] iftira eden, yalan s\xf6yleyen en [[edna|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131/al\xe7ak]] bir dereceye d\xfc\u015fer.\\n\\n\\n\\nBir sine\u011fi, [[daim\xee|s\xfcrekli]] bir [[surette|bi\xe7imde]] tavus g\xf6rmek ve tavusun b\xfcy\xfck [[evsaf\u0131n\u0131|niteliklerini/vas\u0131flar\u0131n\u0131]] onda her vakit [[m\xfc\u015fahede etmek|g\xf6rmek/g\xf6zlemlemek]] ne kadar [[muhal|imkans\u0131z]] ise \u015fu mesele de \xf6yle [[muhaldir|imkans\u0131zd\u0131r]]. [[F\u0131traten|Yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f\xe7a]] ak\u0131ls\u0131z, sarho\u015f bir [[divane|deli]] l\xe2z\u0131m ki buna ihtimal versin.\\n\\n[[R\xe2bian|D\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc olarak]]: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 [[kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer|insan s\xf6z\xfc]] [[farz etmek|varsaymak]] [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]] ki [[ben\xee-\xc2dem\u2019in|\xc2demo\u011fullar\u0131n\u0131n/insano\u011flunun]] en b\xfcy\xfck ve muhte\u015fem ordusu olan [[\xfcmmet-i Muhammediyenin|Hz. Muhammed\'in \xfcmmetinin]] (asm) mukaddes bir kumandan\u0131 olan Kur\u2019an, [[bilm\xfc\u015fahede|g\xf6zlemleyerek/apa\xe7\u0131k]] kuvvetli kanunlar\u0131yla, esasl\u0131 [[d\xfcsturlar\u0131yla|prensipleriyle]], [[n\xe2fiz|s\xf6z\xfc ge\xe7en/etkili]] emirleriyle o pek b\xfcy\xfck orduyu, iki [[cihan\u0131|d\xfcnyay\u0131]] fethedecek bir derecede bir [[intizam|d\xfczen]] verdi\u011fi ve bir [[inzibat|disiplin]] alt\u0131na ald\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve madd\xee ve manev\xee [[te\xe7hiz etti\u011fi|donatt\u0131\u011f\u0131]] ve [[umum efrad\u0131n|b\xfct\xfcn fertlerin/bireylerin]] [[derecat\u0131na|derecelerine]] g\xf6re ak\u0131llar\u0131n\u0131 [[talim|e\u011fitim/\xf6\u011fretim]] ve kalplerini terbiye ve ruhlar\u0131n\u0131 [[teshir|etkisi alt\u0131na alma/b\xfcy\xfcleme]] ve vicdanlar\u0131n\u0131 [[tathir|temizleme/ar\u0131nd\u0131rma]], aza ve [[cevarihlerini|organlar\u0131n\u0131/uzuvlar\u0131n\u0131]] [[istimal|kullanma]] ve [[istihdam etti\u011fi|hizmette kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131/\xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131]] halde \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]], y\xfcz bin [[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]]\u2013 kuvvetsiz, k\u0131ymetsiz, as\u0131ls\u0131z bir d\xfczme [[farz edip|varsay\u0131p]] y\xfcz derece [[muhali|imkans\u0131z\u0131]] kabul etmek [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelmekle|gerekmekle]] beraber\u2026","modernText":"\u0130\u015fte \u2013[[asla/kesinlikle \xf6yle de\u011fil|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]] y\xfcz bin defa [[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 Kur\u2019an, [[insan s\xf6z\xfc|be\u015fer kel\xe2m\u0131|]] [[varsay\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 zaman|farz edildi\u011fi vakit|]] nas\u0131l ki bir [[ate\u015f b\xf6ce\u011fi|y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi|]] bin sene [[zorlanmadan/do\u011fal bir \u015fekilde|tekell\xfcfs\xfcz|]] [[ger\xe7ek|hakiki|]] bir y\u0131ld\u0131z olarak [[g\xf6zlem yapanlara/astronomlara|rasad ehline|]] g\xf6r\xfcns\xfcn. Hem bir sinek bir sene tamamen [[tavus ku\u015fu g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcs\xfcn\xfc|tavus suretini|]] [[yapmac\u0131ks\u0131z/sanatl\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcnmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015fmadan|tasannusuz|]], [[seyredenlere/izleyenlere|tema\u015fa ehline|]] g\xf6stersin. Hem sahtek\xe2r, [[s\u0131radan/cahil|\xe2m\xee|]] bir [[asker/er|nefer|]]; [[\xfcnl\xfc/naml\u0131|namdar|]], [[y\xfcce/y\xfcksek|\xe2l\xee|]] bir [[mare\u015falin/pa\u015fan\u0131n|m\xfc\u015firin|]] tavr\u0131n\u0131 tak\u0131ns\u0131n, makam\u0131nda otursun, \xe7ok zaman \xf6yle kals\u0131n, hilesini [[hissettirmesin/sezdirmesin|ihsas etmesin|]]. Hem [[iftirac\u0131|m\xfcfteri|]], yalanc\u0131 [[inan\xe7s\u0131z|itikads\u0131z|]] bir adam; [[\xf6mr\xfc boyunca|m\xfcddet-i \xf6mr\xfcnde|]] daima en [[do\u011fru s\xf6zl\xfc|sad\u0131k|]] en [[g\xfcvenilir|emin|]] en [[inan\xe7l\u0131/imanl\u0131|mutekid|]] bir zat\u0131n [[niteli\u011fini/durumunu|keyfiyetini|]] ve [[halini/durumunu|vaziyetini|]] en [[dikkatli/inceleyen|m\xfcdakkik|]] [[bak\u0131\u015flara|nazarlara|]] kar\u015f\u0131 tela\u015fs\u0131z g\xf6stersin, d\xe2h\xeelerin [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda/g\xf6z\xfcnde|nazar\u0131nda|]] [[yapmac\u0131kl\u0131\u011f\u0131/sanatl\u0131 g\xf6sterme \xe7abas\u0131|tasannuu|]] saklans\u0131n?\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece [[imkans\u0131zd\u0131r|muhaldir|]], ona hi\xe7bir [[ak\u0131l sahibi|z\xeeak\u0131l|]] m\xfcmk\xfcn diyemez ve \xf6yle de [[varsaymak|farz etmek|]], [[apa\xe7\u0131k/belli|bedih\xee|]] bir [[imkans\u0131z\u0131|muhali|]] [[olmu\u015f/ger\xe7ekle\u015fmi\u015f|vaki|]] [[varsaymak|farz etmek|]] gibi bir [[sa\xe7mal\u0131k/say\u0131klama|hezeyand\u0131r|]].\\n\\nAynen \xf6yle de Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 [[insan s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer|]] [[varsaymak|farz etmek|]]; [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]] ki [[\u0130slam d\xfcnyas\u0131n\u0131n|\xe2lem-i \u0130sl\xe2m\u2019\u0131n|]] semas\u0131nda [[g\xf6rerek/g\xf6zlemleyerek|bilm\xfc\u015fahede|]] pek parlak ve daima [[hakikat nurlar\u0131n\u0131/ger\xe7eklerin \u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131|envar-\u0131 hakaiki|]] [[yayan/sa\xe7an|ne\u015freden|]] bir [[hakikat y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131|y\u0131ld\u0131z-\u0131 hakikat|]], belki bir [[olgunluklar g\xfcne\u015fi/m\xfckemmellikler kayna\u011f\u0131|\u015fems-i kemal\xe2t|]] [[kabul edilen/anla\u015f\u0131lan|telakki edilen|]] [[Apa\xe7\u0131k Kitab\u0131n (Kur\'an\'\u0131n)|Kitab-\u0131 M\xfcbin\u2019in|]] [[i\xe7 y\xfcz\xfc/niteli\u011fi|mahiyeti|]] \u2013[[asla ve sonra yine asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 bir [[ate\u015f b\xf6ce\u011fi|y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi|]] h\xfckm\xfcnde [[yapmac\u0131k\xe7\u0131/sahte sanat\xe7\u0131|tasannucu|]] bir be\u015ferin [[bat\u0131l inan\xe7l\u0131/uydurma|hurafatl\u0131|]] bir d\xfczmesi olsun ve en yak\u0131n\u0131nda olanlar ve dikkatle ona bakanlar fark\u0131nda bulunmas\u0131n ve onu daima [[y\xfcce|\xe2l\xee|]] ve [[hakikatlerin kayna\u011f\u0131|menba-\u0131 hakaik|]] bir y\u0131ld\u0131z bilsin.\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece [[imkans\u0131z|muhal|]] olmakla beraber, sen ey \u015feytan y\xfcz derece [[\u015feytanl\u0131\u011f\u0131nda|\u015feytanetinde|]] ileri gitsen buna imk\xe2n verdiremezsin, bozulmam\u0131\u015f hi\xe7bir akl\u0131 kand\u0131ramazs\u0131n! Yaln\u0131z [[manevi olarak/hayalen|manen|]] pek uzaktan bakt\u0131rmakla aldat\u0131yorsun! Y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131, [[ate\u015f b\xf6ce\u011fi|y\u0131ld\u0131z b\xf6ce\u011fi|]] gibi k\xfc\xe7\xfck g\xf6steriyorsun.\\n\\n[[\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc olarak|S\xe2lisen|]]: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 be\u015fer [[s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m\u0131|]] [[varsaymak|farz etmek|]], [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]] ki [[eserleriyle|\xe2s\xe2r\u0131yla|]], [[etkileriyle|tesirat\u0131yla|]], [[sonu\xe7lar\u0131yla|netaiciyle|]] [[insanl\u0131k d\xfcnyas\u0131n\u0131n|\xe2lem-i insaniyetin|]] [[g\xf6zlemleyerek/apa\xe7\u0131k|bilm\xfc\u015fahede|]] en ruhlu ve [[hayat sa\xe7an/can veren|hayat-fe\u015fan|]], en hakikatli ve [[mutluluk veren/saadet ula\u015ft\u0131ran|saadet-resan|]], en [[kapsaml\u0131/bir\xe7ok hakikati toplayan|cem\u2019iyetli|]] ve [[ifadesi mucize olan/s\xf6z\xfc aciz b\u0131rakan|mu\u2019ciz-beyan|]], [[y\xfcce|\xe2l\xee|]] [[\xfcst\xfcn \xf6zellikleriyle|meziyetleriyle|]] yald\u0131zl\u0131 bir [[Hak ile bat\u0131l\u0131 ay\u0131ran Kur\'an\'\u0131n|Furkan\u2019\u0131n|]] gizli hakikati \u2013[[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 [[yard\u0131ms\u0131z|muavenetsiz|]], ilimsiz bir tek insan\u0131n fikrinin [[uydurmas\u0131/yapmas\u0131|tasniat\u0131|]] olsun ve yak\u0131n\u0131nda onu [[seyreden/izleyen|tema\u015fa eden|]] ve merakla dikkat eden b\xfcy\xfck zek\xe2lar, [[y\xfcce|ulvi|]] dehalar onda hi\xe7bir zaman hi\xe7bir [[y\xf6nde/a\xe7\u0131dan|cihette|]] sahtek\xe2rl\u0131k ve [[yapmac\u0131kl\u0131k|tasannu|]] eserini g\xf6rmesin; daima ciddiyeti, samimiyeti, [[i\xe7tenli\u011fi|ihlas\u0131|]] bulsun!\\n\\nBu ise y\xfcz derece [[imkans\u0131z|muhal|]] olmakla beraber, b\xfct\xfcn [[halleriyle|ahvaliyle|]], [[s\xf6zleriyle|akvaliyle|]], [[hareketleriyle/davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131yla|harek\xe2t\u0131yla|]] b\xfct\xfcn hayat\u0131nda [[g\xfcvenilirli\u011fi|emaneti|]], iman\u0131, [[g\xfcveni|emniyeti|]], [[samimiyeti|ihlas\u0131|]], ciddiyeti, [[do\u011frulu\u011fu|istikameti|]] g\xf6steren ve ders veren ve [[dosdo\u011fru olanlar\u0131/sad\u0131klar\u0131|s\u0131dd\u0131k\xeenleri|]] yeti\u015ftiren en y\xfcksek en parlak en [[y\xfcce|\xe2l\xee|]] [[huy/karakter \xf6zelli\u011fi|haslet|]] [[kabul edilen|telakki edilen|]] ve kabul edilen bir zat\u0131; en [[g\xfcvensiz|emniyetsiz|]] en [[samimiyetsiz|ihlass\u0131z|]] en [[inan\xe7s\u0131z|itikads\u0131z|]] [[varsaymakla|farz etmekle|]], [[kat kat/katlanm\u0131\u015f|muzaaf|]] bir [[imkans\u0131z\u0131|muhali|]] [[olmu\u015f/ger\xe7ekle\u015fmi\u015f|vaki|]] g\xf6rmek gibi \u015feytan\u0131 dahi utand\u0131racak bir [[fikir sa\xe7mal\u0131\u011f\u0131d\u0131r/d\xfc\u015f\xfcnce hezeyan\u0131d\u0131r|hezeyan-\u0131 fikr\xeedir|]].\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc \u015fu meselenin ortas\u0131 yoktur. [[\xc7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] [[imkans\u0131z oldu\u011fu halde varsayarak|farz-\u0131 muhal|]] olarak Kur\u2019an, [[Allah kelam\u0131/Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2mullah|]] olmazsa [[g\xf6\u011f\xfcn en y\xfcksek kat\u0131ndan yery\xfcz\xfcne|ar\u015ftan fer\u015fe|]] d\xfc\u015fer gibi [[d\xfc\u015fer|sukut eder|]]. Ortada kalmaz. [[hakikatlerin toplanma yeri|Mecma-\u0131 hakaik|]] iken, [[hurafelerin kayna\u011f\u0131|menba-\u0131 hurafat|]] olur. Ve o [[harikulade|h\xe2rika|]] [[buyru\u011fu (Kur\'an\'\u0131)|ferman\u0131|]] g\xf6steren zat, [[asla ve sonra yine asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]] e\u011fer [[Allah\'\u0131n El\xe7isi|Resulullah|]] olmazsa [[y\xfccelerin en y\xfccesinden/cennetin en y\xfcksek tabakas\u0131ndan|a\u2019l\xe2-y\u0131 illiyy\xeenden|]] [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131lar\u0131n en a\u015fa\u011f\u0131s\u0131na/cehennemin en derin yerine|esfel-i safil\xeene|]] [[d\xfc\u015fmek|sukut etmek|]] ve [[m\xfckemmelliklerin kayna\u011f\u0131|menba-\u0131 kemal\xe2t|]] derecesinden [[hilelerin kayna\u011f\u0131|maden-i desais|]] makam\u0131na d\xfc\u015fmek [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]]. Ortada kalamaz. [[\xc7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] Allah [[ad\u0131na|nam\u0131na|]] iftira eden, yalan s\xf6yleyen en [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131/al\xe7ak|edna|]] bir dereceye d\xfc\u015fer.\\n\\n\\n\\nBir sine\u011fi, [[s\xfcrekli|daim\xee|]] bir [[bi\xe7imde|surette|]] tavus g\xf6rmek ve tavusun b\xfcy\xfck [[niteliklerini/vas\u0131flar\u0131n\u0131|evsaf\u0131n\u0131|]] onda her vakit [[g\xf6rmek/g\xf6zlemlemek|m\xfc\u015fahede etmek|]] ne kadar [[imkans\u0131z|muhal|]] ise \u015fu mesele de \xf6yle [[imkans\u0131zd\u0131r|muhaldir|]]. [[Yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f\xe7a|F\u0131traten|]] ak\u0131ls\u0131z, sarho\u015f bir [[deli|divane|]] l\xe2z\u0131m ki buna ihtimal versin.\\n\\n[[D\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc olarak|R\xe2bian|]]: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 [[insan s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer|]] [[varsaymak|farz etmek|]] [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]] ki [[\xc2demo\u011fullar\u0131n\u0131n/insano\u011flunun|ben\xee-\xc2dem\u2019in|]] en b\xfcy\xfck ve muhte\u015fem ordusu olan [[Hz. Muhammed\'in \xfcmmetinin|\xfcmmet-i Muhammediyenin|]] (asm) mukaddes bir kumandan\u0131 olan Kur\u2019an, [[g\xf6zlemleyerek/apa\xe7\u0131k|bilm\xfc\u015fahede|]] kuvvetli kanunlar\u0131yla, esasl\u0131 [[prensipleriyle|d\xfcsturlar\u0131yla|]], [[s\xf6z\xfc ge\xe7en/etkili|n\xe2fiz|]] emirleriyle o pek b\xfcy\xfck orduyu, iki [[d\xfcnyay\u0131|cihan\u0131|]] fethedecek bir derecede bir [[d\xfczen|intizam|]] verdi\u011fi ve bir [[disiplin|inzibat|]] alt\u0131na ald\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve madd\xee ve manev\xee [[donatt\u0131\u011f\u0131|te\xe7hiz etti\u011fi|]] ve [[b\xfct\xfcn fertlerin/bireylerin|umum efrad\u0131n|]] [[derecelerine|derecat\u0131na|]] g\xf6re ak\u0131llar\u0131n\u0131 [[e\u011fitim/\xf6\u011fretim|talim|]] ve kalplerini terbiye ve ruhlar\u0131n\u0131 [[etkisi alt\u0131na alma/b\xfcy\xfcleme|teshir|]] ve vicdanlar\u0131n\u0131 [[temizleme/ar\u0131nd\u0131rma|tathir|]], aza ve [[organlar\u0131n\u0131/uzuvlar\u0131n\u0131|cevarihlerini|]] [[kullanma|istimal|]] ve [[hizmette kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131/\xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131|istihdam etti\u011fi|]] halde \u2013[[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]], y\xfcz bin [[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 kuvvetsiz, k\u0131ymetsiz, as\u0131ls\u0131z bir d\xfczme [[varsay\u0131p|farz edip|]] y\xfcz derece [[imkans\u0131z\u0131|muhali|]] kabul etmek [[gerekmekle|l\xe2z\u0131m gelmekle|]] beraber\u2026","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.21-19:20","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"},{"pageId":8,"rawText":"M\xfcddet-i hayat\u0131nda ciddi harek\xe2t\u0131yla Hakk\u2019\u0131n kanunlar\u0131n\u0131 ben\xee-\xc2dem\u2019e ders veren ve samimi ef\u2019aliyle hakikatin d\xfcsturlar\u0131n\u0131 be\u015fere talim eden ve h\xe2lis ve makul akvaliyle istikametin ve saadetin us\xfbllerini g\xf6steren ve tesis eden ve b\xfct\xfcn tarih\xe7e-i hayat\u0131n\u0131n \u015fehadetiyle Allah\u2019\u0131n azab\u0131ndan \xe7ok havf eden ve herkesten ziyade Allah\u2019\u0131 bilen ve bildiren ve nev-i be\u015ferin be\u015ften birisine ve k\xfcre-i arz\u0131n yar\u0131s\u0131na bin \xfc\xe7 y\xfcz elli sene kemal-i ha\u015fmetle kumandanl\u0131k eden ve cihan\u0131 velveleye veren \u015f\xf6hret-\u015fiar \u015fuunat\u0131yla nev-i be\u015ferin belki k\xe2inat\u0131n elhak medar-\u0131 fahri olan bir zat\u0131 \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2 y\xfcz bin defa h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 Allah\u2019tan korkmaz ve bilmez ve yalandan \xe7ekinmez, haysiyetini tan\u0131maz farz etmekle, y\xfcz derece muhali birden irtik\xe2b etmek l\xe2z\u0131m gelir.\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc \u015fu meselenin ortas\u0131 yoktur. Zira farz-\u0131 muhal olarak Kur\u2019an kel\xe2mullah olmazsa ar\u015ftan d\xfc\u015fse orta yerde kalamaz. Belki yerde en yalanc\u0131 birinin mal\u0131 oldu\u011funu kabul etmek l\xe2z\u0131m gelir. Bu ise ey \u015feytan, y\xfcz derece sen katmerli bir \u015feytan olsan bozulmam\u0131\u015f hi\xe7bir akl\u0131 kand\u0131ramazs\u0131n ve \xe7\xfcr\xfcmemi\u015f hi\xe7bir kalbi ikna edemezsin.\\n\\n\u015eeytan d\xf6nd\xfc, dedi:\\n\\nNas\u0131l kand\u0131ramam? Ekser insanlara ve insan\u0131n me\u015fhur \xe2k\u0131llar\u0131na Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 ve Muhammed\u2019i ink\xe2r ettirdim ve kand\u0131rd\u0131m.\\n\\nElcevap:\\n\\nEvvela: Gayet uzak mesafeden bak\u0131lsa en b\xfcy\xfck bir \u015fey, en k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir \u015fey gibi g\xf6r\xfcnebilir. Bir y\u0131ld\u0131z, bir mum kadard\u0131r denilebilir.\\n\\nS\xe2niyen: Hem tebe\xee ve sath\xee bir nazarla bak\u0131lsa gayet muhal bir \u015fey, m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6r\xfcnebilir. Bir zaman bir ihtiyar adam ramazan hil\xe2lini g\xf6rmek i\xe7in semaya bakm\u0131\u015f. G\xf6z\xfcne bir beyaz k\u0131l inmi\u015f. O k\u0131l\u0131 ay zannetmi\u015f. \u201cAy\u2019\u0131 g\xf6rd\xfcm.\u201d demi\u015f. \u0130\u015fte muhaldir ki hil\xe2l, o beyaz k\u0131l olsun. Fakat kasden ve bizzat aya bakt\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve o sa\xe7\u0131 tebe\xee ve dolay\u0131s\u0131yla ve ikinci derecede g\xf6r\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc i\xe7in o muhali m\xfcmk\xfcn telakki etmi\u015f.\\n\\nS\xe2lisen: Hem kabul etmemek ba\u015fkad\u0131r, ink\xe2r etmek ba\u015fkad\u0131r. Adem-i kabul bir l\xe2kaytl\u0131kt\u0131r, bir g\xf6z kapamakt\u0131r ve cahilane bir h\xfck\xfcms\xfczl\xfckt\xfcr. Bu surette \xe7ok muhal \u015feyler onun i\xe7inde gizlenebilir. Onun akl\u0131 onlarla u\u011fra\u015fmaz. Amma ink\xe2r ise o adem-i kabul de\u011fil belki o kabul-\xfc ademdir, bir h\xfck\xfcmd\xfcr. Onun akl\u0131 hareket etmeye mecburdur. O halde senin gibi bir \u015feytan onun akl\u0131n\u0131 elinden al\u0131r. Sonra ink\xe2r\u0131 ona yutturur.\\n\\nHem ey \u015feytan! B\xe2t\u0131l\u0131 hak ve muhali m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6steren gaflet ve dalalet ve safsata ve inat ve ma\u011flata ve m\xfck\xe2bere ve i\u011ffal ve g\xf6renek gibi \u015feytan\xee desiselerle, \xe7ok muhalat\u0131 intac eden k\xfcf\xfcr ve ink\xe2r\u0131 o bedbaht insan suretindeki hayvanlara yutturmu\u015fsun.\\n\\nR\xe2bian: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer farz etmek, l\xe2z\u0131m gelir ki: \xc2lem-i insaniyetin semas\u0131nda y\u0131ld\u0131zlar gibi parlayan asfiyalara, s\u0131dd\u0131k\xeenlere, aktablara bilm\xfc\u015fahede rehberlik eden ve bilbedahe m\xfctemadiyen hak ve hakkaniyeti, s\u0131dk ve sadakati, emn ve emaneti umum tabakat-\u0131 ehl-i kemale talim eden ve erk\xe2n-\u0131 imaniyenin hakaikiyle ve erk\xe2n-\u0131 \u0130sl\xe2miyenin desatiriyle iki cihan\u0131n saadetini temin eden ve bu icraat\u0131n\u0131n \u015fehadetiyle bizzarure h\xe2lis hak ve safi hakikat ve gayet do\u011fru ve pek ciddi olmak l\xe2z\u0131m gelen bir kitab\u0131; kendi evsaf\u0131n\u0131n ve tesirat\u0131n\u0131n ve envar\u0131n\u0131n z\u0131dd\u0131yla muttas\u0131f tasavvur edip \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2 h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 tasniat ve iftiralar\u0131n mecmuas\u0131 nazar\u0131yla bakmak; sofesta\xeeleri ve \u015feytanlar\u0131 dahi utand\u0131racak ve titretecek \u015fen\xee\u2019 bir hezeyan-\u0131 k\xfcfr\xee olmakla beraber\u2026\\n\\n\u0130zhar etti\u011fi din ve \u015feriat-\u0131 \u0130sl\xe2miyenin \u015fehadetiyle ve m\xfcddet-i hayat\u0131nda g\xf6sterdi\u011fi bi\u2019l-ittifak fevkal\xe2de takvas\u0131n\u0131n ve h\xe2lis ve safi ubudiyetinin del\xe2letiyle ve bi\u2019l-ittifak kendinde g\xf6r\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc ahl\xe2k-\u0131 hasenesinin iktizas\u0131yla ve yeti\u015ftirdi\u011fi b\xfct\xfcn ehl-i hakikatin ve sahib-i kemal\xe2t\u0131n tasdikiyle en mutekid en metin en emin en sad\u0131k bir zat\u0131 \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2 y\xfcz bin kere h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 itikads\u0131z, en emniyetsiz, Allah\u2019tan korkmaz, yalandan \xe7ekinmez bir vaziyette farz edip muhalat\u0131n en \xe7irkin ve menfur bir suretini ve dalaletin en zul\xfcml\xfc ve zul\xfcmatl\u0131 bir tarz\u0131n\u0131 irtik\xe2b etmek l\xe2z\u0131m gelir.","oldText":"[[M\xfcddet-i hayat\u0131nda|hayat\u0131 boyunca/\xf6mr\xfc s\xfcresince]] ciddi [[harek\xe2t\u0131yla|hareketleriyle/davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131yla]] [[Hakk\u2019\u0131n|Allah\'\u0131n/Hakk olan\u0131n]] kanunlar\u0131n\u0131 [[ben\xee-\xc2dem\u2019e|insano\u011fluna/\xc2demo\u011fullar\u0131na]] ders veren ve samimi [[ef\u2019aliyle|fiilleriyle/yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u015flerle]] hakikatin [[d\xfcsturlar\u0131n\u0131|prensiplerini/kurallar\u0131n\u0131]] [[be\u015fere|insanl\u0131\u011fa]] [[talim eden|\xf6\u011freten/ders veren]] ve [[h\xe2lis|saf/i\xe7ten]] ve [[makul|akla uygun/mant\u0131kl\u0131]] [[akvaliyle|s\xf6zleriyle]] [[istikametin|do\u011frulu\u011fun/do\u011fru yolun]] ve [[saadetin|mutlulu\u011fun]] [[us\xfbllerini|y\xf6ntemlerini/yollar\u0131n\u0131]] g\xf6steren ve [[tesis eden|kuran/yerle\u015ftiren]] ve b\xfct\xfcn [[tarih\xe7e-i hayat\u0131n\u0131n|hayat hikayesinin/biyografisinin]] [[\u015fehadetiyle|\u015fahitli\u011fiyle/kan\u0131t\u0131yla]] Allah\u2019\u0131n azab\u0131ndan \xe7ok [[havf eden|korkan]] ve herkesten [[ziyade|fazla/\xe7ok]] Allah\u2019\u0131 bilen ve bildiren ve [[nev-i be\u015ferin|insan t\xfcr\xfcn\xfcn/insanl\u0131\u011f\u0131n]] be\u015ften birisine ve [[k\xfcre-i arz\u0131n|yery\xfcz\xfcn\xfcn/yerk\xfcrenin]] yar\u0131s\u0131na bin \xfc\xe7 y\xfcz elli sene [[kemal-i ha\u015fmetle|tam bir ihti\u015famla/m\xfckemmel bir heybetle]] kumandanl\u0131k eden ve [[cihan\u0131|d\xfcnyay\u0131/\xe2lemi]] [[velveleye veren|aya\u011fa kald\u0131ran/yank\u0131land\u0131ran]] [[\u015f\xf6hret-\u015fiar|\xfcn\xfc yay\u0131lm\u0131\u015f/me\u015fhur olan]] [[\u015fuunat\u0131yla|i\u015fleriyle/icraatlar\u0131yla|Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\'\u0131n emir ve iradesiyle ortaya \xe7\u0131kan haller]] [[nev-i be\u015ferin|insanl\u0131\u011f\u0131n]] belki k\xe2inat\u0131n [[elhak|do\u011frusu/hakikaten]] [[medar-\u0131 fahri|\xf6v\xfcn\xe7 kayna\u011f\u0131]] olan bir zat\u0131 \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla/kesinlikle \xf6yle de\u011fil]] y\xfcz bin defa [[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]]\u2013 Allah\u2019tan korkmaz ve bilmez ve yalandan \xe7ekinmez, haysiyetini tan\u0131maz [[farz etmekle|varsaymakla/kabul etmekle]], y\xfcz derece [[muhali|imkans\u0131z\u0131]] birden [[irtik\xe2b etmek|i\u015flemek/yapmak]] [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]].\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc \u015fu meselenin ortas\u0131 yoktur. [[Zira|\xe7\xfcnk\xfc]] [[farz-\u0131 muhal|imkans\u0131z oldu\u011fu halde varsayarak]] olarak Kur\u2019an [[kel\xe2mullah|Allah kelam\u0131/Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfc]] olmazsa [[ar\u015ftan|g\xf6\u011f\xfcn en y\xfcksek kat\u0131ndan/makam\u0131ndan]] d\xfc\u015fse orta yerde kalamaz. Belki yerde en yalanc\u0131 birinin mal\u0131 oldu\u011funu kabul etmek [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]]. Bu ise ey \u015feytan, y\xfcz derece sen [[katmerli|kat kat/az\u0131l\u0131]] bir \u015feytan olsan bozulmam\u0131\u015f hi\xe7bir akl\u0131 kand\u0131ramazs\u0131n ve \xe7\xfcr\xfcmemi\u015f hi\xe7bir kalbi ikna edemezsin.\\n\\n\u015eeytan d\xf6nd\xfc, dedi:\\n\\nNas\u0131l kand\u0131ramam? [[Ekser|\xe7o\u011fu/pek \xe7ok]] insanlara ve insan\u0131n me\u015fhur [[\xe2k\u0131llar\u0131na|ak\u0131ll\u0131lar\u0131na/d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcrlerine]] Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 ve Muhammed\u2019i [[ink\xe2r ettirdim|reddettirdim/kabul ettirmedim]] ve kand\u0131rd\u0131m.\\n\\n[[Elcevap|cevap/cevap olarak]]:\\n\\n[[Evvela|\xf6ncelikle/ilk olarak]]: Gayet uzak mesafeden bak\u0131lsa en b\xfcy\xfck bir \u015fey, en k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir \u015fey gibi g\xf6r\xfcnebilir. Bir y\u0131ld\u0131z, bir mum kadard\u0131r denilebilir.\\n\\n[[S\xe2niyen|ikinci olarak]]: Hem [[tebe\xee|dolayl\u0131/ikinci dereceden]] ve [[sath\xee|y\xfczeysel]] bir [[nazarla|bak\u0131\u015fla]] bak\u0131lsa gayet [[muhal|imkans\u0131z]] bir \u015fey, m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6r\xfcnebilir. Bir zaman bir ihtiyar adam ramazan hil\xe2lini g\xf6rmek i\xe7in semaya bakm\u0131\u015f. G\xf6z\xfcne bir beyaz k\u0131l inmi\u015f. O k\u0131l\u0131 ay zannetmi\u015f. \u201cAy\u2019\u0131 g\xf6rd\xfcm.\u201d demi\u015f. \u0130\u015fte [[muhaldir|imkans\u0131zd\u0131r]] ki hil\xe2l, o beyaz k\u0131l olsun. Fakat [[kasden|isteyerek/bilerek]] ve [[bizzat|kendi \u015fahs\u0131 ile/do\u011frudan]] aya bakt\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve o sa\xe7\u0131 [[tebe\xee|dolayl\u0131/ba\u011f\u0131ml\u0131 olarak]] ve dolay\u0131s\u0131yla ve ikinci derecede g\xf6r\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc i\xe7in o [[muhali|imkans\u0131z\u0131]] m\xfcmk\xfcn [[telakki etmi\u015f|kabul etmi\u015f/anlam\u0131\u015f]].\\n\\n[[S\xe2lisen|\xfc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc olarak]]: Hem kabul etmemek ba\u015fkad\u0131r, ink\xe2r etmek ba\u015fkad\u0131r. [[Adem-i kabul|kabul etmeme/yok sayma]] bir [[l\xe2kaytl\u0131kt\u0131r|ilgisizliktir/duyars\u0131zl\u0131kt\u0131r]], bir g\xf6z kapamakt\u0131r ve cahilane bir h\xfck\xfcms\xfczl\xfckt\xfcr. Bu surette \xe7ok [[muhal|imkans\u0131z]] \u015feyler onun i\xe7inde gizlenebilir. Onun akl\u0131 onlarla u\u011fra\u015fmaz. [[Amma|fakat/ama]] ink\xe2r ise o [[adem-i kabul|kabul etmeme]] de\u011fil belki o [[kabul-\xfc ademdir|yoklu\u011funu kabul etmektir]], bir h\xfck\xfcmd\xfcr. Onun akl\u0131 hareket etmeye mecburdur. O halde senin gibi bir \u015feytan onun akl\u0131n\u0131 elinden al\u0131r. Sonra ink\xe2r\u0131 ona yutturur.\\n\\nHem ey \u015feytan! [[B\xe2t\u0131l\u0131|hak olmayan\u0131/yanl\u0131\u015f\u0131]] hak ve [[muhali|imkans\u0131z\u0131]] m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6steren [[gaflet|dalg\u0131nl\u0131k/Allah\'\u0131 unutmu\u015fluk]] ve [[dalalet|sapk\u0131nl\u0131k/do\u011fru yoldan ayr\u0131lma]] ve [[safsata|yan\u0131lt\u0131c\u0131 s\xf6z/bo\u015f laf]] ve inat ve [[ma\u011flata|demagoji/\u015fa\u015f\u0131rtmaca]] ve [[m\xfck\xe2bere|b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck taslama/inatla inkar etme]] ve [[i\u011ffal|aldatma/kand\u0131rma]] ve g\xf6renek gibi \u015feytan\xee [[desiselerle|hilelerle/oyunlarla]], \xe7ok [[muhalat\u0131|imkans\u0131z \u015feyleri]] [[intac eden|sonu\xe7 veren/netice veren]] [[k\xfcf\xfcr|inan\xe7s\u0131zl\u0131k]] ve ink\xe2r\u0131 o [[bedbaht|talihsiz/mutsuz]] insan [[suretindeki|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015f\xfcndeki/\u015feklindeki]] hayvanlara yutturmu\u015fsun.\\n\\n[[R\xe2bian|d\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc olarak]]: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 [[kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer|insan s\xf6z\xfc]] [[farz etmek|varsaymak]], [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]] ki: [[\xc2lem-i insaniyetin|insanl\u0131k d\xfcnyas\u0131n\u0131n]] semas\u0131nda y\u0131ld\u0131zlar gibi parlayan [[asfiyalara|saf ve temiz olan \xe2limlere/ger\xe7e\u011fi bulanlara]], [[s\u0131dd\u0131k\xeenlere|son derece do\u011fru olanlara/peygamberlere en sad\u0131k olanlara]], [[aktablara|b\xfcy\xfck velilere/kutuplara]] [[bilm\xfc\u015fahede|g\xf6rerek/g\xf6zlemleyerek]] rehberlik eden ve [[bilbedahe|apa\xe7\u0131k bir \u015fekilde]] [[m\xfctemadiyen|s\xfcrekli/devaml\u0131]] hak ve [[hakkaniyeti|do\u011frulu\u011fu/adaleti]], [[s\u0131dk|do\u011fruluk]] ve sadakati, [[emn|g\xfcven]] ve emaneti [[umum|b\xfct\xfcn/genel]] [[tabakat-\u0131 ehl-i kemale|olgunluk ehlinin tabakalar\u0131na/seviyelerine]] [[talim eden|\xf6\u011freten]] ve [[erk\xe2n-\u0131 imaniyenin|iman\u0131n esaslar\u0131n\u0131n]] [[hakaikiyle|hakikatleriyle/ger\xe7ekleriyle]] ve [[erk\xe2n-\u0131 \u0130sl\xe2miyenin|\u0130slam\'\u0131n \u015fartlar\u0131n\u0131n/esaslar\u0131n\u0131n]] [[desatiriyle|d\xfcsturlar\u0131yla/prensipleriyle]] iki cihan\u0131n [[saadetini|mutlulu\u011funu]] [[temin eden|sa\u011flayan]] ve bu icraat\u0131n\u0131n [[\u015fehadetiyle|\u015fahitli\u011fiyle]] [[bizzarure|zorunlu olarak/ister istemez]] [[h\xe2lis|saf/temiz]] hak ve [[safi|kat\u0131ks\u0131z]] hakikat ve gayet do\u011fru ve pek ciddi olmak [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelen|gereken]] bir kitab\u0131; kendi [[evsaf\u0131n\u0131n|vas\u0131flar\u0131n\u0131n/niteliklerinin]] ve [[tesirat\u0131n\u0131n|etkilerinin]] ve [[envar\u0131n\u0131n|nurlar\u0131n\u0131n/\u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n]] z\u0131dd\u0131yla [[muttas\u0131f|vas\u0131flanm\u0131\u015f/s\u0131fatlanm\u0131\u015f]] [[tasavvur edip|d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp/hayal edip]] \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2 h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla ve asla]]\u2013 [[tasniat|uydurmalar/yapmac\u0131k \u015feyler]] ve iftiralar\u0131n [[mecmuas\u0131|toplam\u0131/birle\u015fimi]] [[nazar\u0131yla|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131yla]] bakmak; [[sofesta\xeeleri|\u015f\xfcphecileri/sofsitleri]] ve \u015feytanlar\u0131 dahi utand\u0131racak ve titretecek [[\u015fen\xee\u2019|\xe7irkin/i\u011fren\xe7]] bir [[hezeyan-\u0131 k\xfcfr\xee|k\xfcf\xfcr sa\xe7mal\u0131\u011f\u0131/inan\xe7s\u0131zl\u0131k say\u0131klamas\u0131]] olmakla beraber\u2026\\n\\n[[\u0130zhar etti\u011fi|ortaya koydu\u011fu/a\xe7\u0131klad\u0131\u011f\u0131]] din ve [[\u015feriat-\u0131 \u0130sl\xe2miyenin|\u0130slam \u015feriat\u0131n\u0131n/kanunlar\u0131n\u0131n]] [[\u015fehadetiyle|\u015fahitli\u011fiyle]] ve [[m\xfcddet-i hayat\u0131nda|hayat\u0131 boyunca]] g\xf6sterdi\u011fi [[bi\u2019l-ittifak|ittifakla/herkesin kabul\xfcyle]] [[fevkal\xe2de|ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc]] [[takvas\u0131n\u0131n|Allah\'tan sak\u0131nmas\u0131n\u0131n/g\xfcnahlardan ka\xe7\u0131nmas\u0131n\u0131n]] ve [[h\xe2lis|saf/i\xe7ten]] ve [[safi|kat\u0131ks\u0131z]] [[ubudiyetinin|kullu\u011funun]] [[del\xe2letiyle|delil olmas\u0131yla/g\xf6stermesiyle]] ve [[bi\u2019l-ittifak|ittifakla]] kendinde g\xf6r\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc [[ahl\xe2k-\u0131 hasenesinin|g\xfczel ahlak\u0131n\u0131n]] [[iktizas\u0131yla|gere\u011fiyle]] ve yeti\u015ftirdi\u011fi b\xfct\xfcn [[ehl-i hakikatin|hakikat ehlinin/ger\xe7e\u011fi bulanlar\u0131n]] ve [[sahib-i kemal\xe2t\u0131n|olgunluk sahiplerinin]] [[tasdikiyle|onaylamas\u0131yla/do\u011frulamas\u0131yla]] en [[mutekid|inan\xe7l\u0131/itikad\u0131 sa\u011flam]] en [[metin|sa\u011flam/dayan\u0131kl\u0131]] en [[emin|g\xfcvenilir]] en [[sad\u0131k|do\u011fru s\xf6zl\xfc]] bir zat\u0131 \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]] [[s\xfcmme|sonra (yine)]] [[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]] y\xfcz bin kere [[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]]\u2013 [[itikads\u0131z|inan\xe7s\u0131z]], en [[emniyetsiz|g\xfcvensiz]], Allah\u2019tan korkmaz, yalandan \xe7ekinmez bir [[vaziyette|durumda]] [[farz edip|varsay\u0131p]], [[muhalat\u0131n|imkans\u0131zl\u0131klar\u0131n]] en \xe7irkin ve [[menfur|nefret edilen/i\u011fren\xe7]] bir [[suretini|\u015feklini/bi\xe7imini]] ve [[dalaletin|sapk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131n]] en zul\xfcml\xfc ve [[zul\xfcmatl\u0131|karanl\u0131kl\u0131]] bir tarz\u0131n\u0131 [[irtik\xe2b etmek|i\u015flemek/yapmak]] [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]].","modernText":"[[hayat\u0131 boyunca/\xf6mr\xfc s\xfcresince|M\xfcddet-i hayat\u0131nda|]] ciddi [[hareketleriyle/davran\u0131\u015flar\u0131yla|harek\xe2t\u0131yla|]] [[Allah\'\u0131n/Hakk olan\u0131n|Hakk\u2019\u0131n|]] kanunlar\u0131n\u0131 [[insano\u011fluna/\xc2demo\u011fullar\u0131na|ben\xee-\xc2dem\u2019e|]] ders veren ve samimi [[fiilleriyle/yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u015flerle|ef\u2019aliyle|]] hakikatin [[prensiplerini/kurallar\u0131n\u0131|d\xfcsturlar\u0131n\u0131|]] [[insanl\u0131\u011fa|be\u015fere|]] [[\xf6\u011freten/ders veren|talim eden|]] ve [[saf/i\xe7ten|h\xe2lis|]] ve [[akla uygun/mant\u0131kl\u0131|makul|]] [[s\xf6zleriyle|akvaliyle|]] [[do\u011frulu\u011fun/do\u011fru yolun|istikametin|]] ve [[mutlulu\u011fun|saadetin|]] [[y\xf6ntemlerini/yollar\u0131n\u0131|us\xfbllerini|]] g\xf6steren ve [[kuran/yerle\u015ftiren|tesis eden|]] ve b\xfct\xfcn [[hayat hikayesinin/biyografisinin|tarih\xe7e-i hayat\u0131n\u0131n|]] [[\u015fahitli\u011fiyle/kan\u0131t\u0131yla|\u015fehadetiyle|]] Allah\u2019\u0131n azab\u0131ndan \xe7ok [[korkan|havf eden|]] ve herkesten [[fazla/\xe7ok|ziyade|]] Allah\u2019\u0131 bilen ve bildiren ve [[insan t\xfcr\xfcn\xfcn/insanl\u0131\u011f\u0131n|nev-i be\u015ferin|]] be\u015ften birisine ve [[yery\xfcz\xfcn\xfcn/yerk\xfcrenin|k\xfcre-i arz\u0131n|]] yar\u0131s\u0131na bin \xfc\xe7 y\xfcz elli sene [[tam bir ihti\u015famla/m\xfckemmel bir heybetle|kemal-i ha\u015fmetle|]] kumandanl\u0131k eden ve [[d\xfcnyay\u0131/\xe2lemi|cihan\u0131|]] [[aya\u011fa kald\u0131ran/yank\u0131land\u0131ran|velveleye veren|]] [[\xfcn\xfc yay\u0131lm\u0131\u015f/me\u015fhur olan|\u015f\xf6hret-\u015fiar|]] [[i\u015fleriyle/icraatlar\u0131yla|\u015fuunat\u0131yla|Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\'\u0131n emir ve iradesiyle ortaya \xe7\u0131kan haller]] [[insanl\u0131\u011f\u0131n|nev-i be\u015ferin|]] belki k\xe2inat\u0131n [[do\u011frusu/hakikaten|elhak|]] [[\xf6v\xfcn\xe7 kayna\u011f\u0131|medar-\u0131 fahri|]] olan bir zat\u0131 \u2013[[asla/kesinlikle \xf6yle de\u011fil|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]] y\xfcz bin defa [[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 Allah\u2019tan korkmaz ve bilmez ve yalandan \xe7ekinmez, haysiyetini tan\u0131maz [[varsaymakla/kabul etmekle|farz etmekle|]], y\xfcz derece [[imkans\u0131z\u0131|muhali|]] birden [[i\u015flemek/yapmak|irtik\xe2b etmek|]] [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]].\\n\\n\xc7\xfcnk\xfc \u015fu meselenin ortas\u0131 yoktur. [[\xe7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] [[imkans\u0131z oldu\u011fu halde varsayarak|farz-\u0131 muhal|]] olarak Kur\u2019an [[Allah kelam\u0131/Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2mullah|]] olmazsa [[g\xf6\u011f\xfcn en y\xfcksek kat\u0131ndan/makam\u0131ndan|ar\u015ftan|]] d\xfc\u015fse orta yerde kalamaz. Belki yerde en yalanc\u0131 birinin mal\u0131 oldu\u011funu kabul etmek [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]]. Bu ise ey \u015feytan, y\xfcz derece sen [[kat kat/az\u0131l\u0131|katmerli|]] bir \u015feytan olsan bozulmam\u0131\u015f hi\xe7bir akl\u0131 kand\u0131ramazs\u0131n ve \xe7\xfcr\xfcmemi\u015f hi\xe7bir kalbi ikna edemezsin.\\n\\n\u015eeytan d\xf6nd\xfc, dedi:\\n\\nNas\u0131l kand\u0131ramam? [[\xe7o\u011fu/pek \xe7ok|Ekser|]] insanlara ve insan\u0131n me\u015fhur [[ak\u0131ll\u0131lar\u0131na/d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcrlerine|\xe2k\u0131llar\u0131na|]] Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 ve Muhammed\u2019i [[reddettirdim/kabul ettirmedim|ink\xe2r ettirdim|]] ve kand\u0131rd\u0131m.\\n\\n[[cevap/cevap olarak|Elcevap|]]:\\n\\n[[\xf6ncelikle/ilk olarak|Evvela|]]: Gayet uzak mesafeden bak\u0131lsa en b\xfcy\xfck bir \u015fey, en k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir \u015fey gibi g\xf6r\xfcnebilir. Bir y\u0131ld\u0131z, bir mum kadard\u0131r denilebilir.\\n\\n[[ikinci olarak|S\xe2niyen|]]: Hem [[dolayl\u0131/ikinci dereceden|tebe\xee|]] ve [[y\xfczeysel|sath\xee|]] bir [[bak\u0131\u015fla|nazarla|]] bak\u0131lsa gayet [[imkans\u0131z|muhal|]] bir \u015fey, m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6r\xfcnebilir. Bir zaman bir ihtiyar adam ramazan hil\xe2lini g\xf6rmek i\xe7in semaya bakm\u0131\u015f. G\xf6z\xfcne bir beyaz k\u0131l inmi\u015f. O k\u0131l\u0131 ay zannetmi\u015f. \u201cAy\u2019\u0131 g\xf6rd\xfcm.\u201d demi\u015f. \u0130\u015fte [[imkans\u0131zd\u0131r|muhaldir|]] ki hil\xe2l, o beyaz k\u0131l olsun. Fakat [[isteyerek/bilerek|kasden|]] ve [[kendi \u015fahs\u0131 ile/do\u011frudan|bizzat|]] aya bakt\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve o sa\xe7\u0131 [[dolayl\u0131/ba\u011f\u0131ml\u0131 olarak|tebe\xee|]] ve dolay\u0131s\u0131yla ve ikinci derecede g\xf6r\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc i\xe7in o [[imkans\u0131z\u0131|muhali|]] m\xfcmk\xfcn [[kabul etmi\u015f/anlam\u0131\u015f|telakki etmi\u015f|]].\\n\\n[[\xfc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc olarak|S\xe2lisen|]]: Hem kabul etmemek ba\u015fkad\u0131r, ink\xe2r etmek ba\u015fkad\u0131r. [[kabul etmeme/yok sayma|Adem-i kabul|]] bir [[ilgisizliktir/duyars\u0131zl\u0131kt\u0131r|l\xe2kaytl\u0131kt\u0131r|]], bir g\xf6z kapamakt\u0131r ve cahilane bir h\xfck\xfcms\xfczl\xfckt\xfcr. Bu surette \xe7ok [[imkans\u0131z|muhal|]] \u015feyler onun i\xe7inde gizlenebilir. Onun akl\u0131 onlarla u\u011fra\u015fmaz. [[fakat/ama|Amma|]] ink\xe2r ise o [[kabul etmeme|adem-i kabul|]] de\u011fil belki o [[yoklu\u011funu kabul etmektir|kabul-\xfc ademdir|]], bir h\xfck\xfcmd\xfcr. Onun akl\u0131 hareket etmeye mecburdur. O halde senin gibi bir \u015feytan onun akl\u0131n\u0131 elinden al\u0131r. Sonra ink\xe2r\u0131 ona yutturur.\\n\\nHem ey \u015feytan! [[hak olmayan\u0131/yanl\u0131\u015f\u0131|B\xe2t\u0131l\u0131|]] hak ve [[imkans\u0131z\u0131|muhali|]] m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6steren [[dalg\u0131nl\u0131k/Allah\'\u0131 unutmu\u015fluk|gaflet|]] ve [[sapk\u0131nl\u0131k/do\u011fru yoldan ayr\u0131lma|dalalet|]] ve [[yan\u0131lt\u0131c\u0131 s\xf6z/bo\u015f laf|safsata|]] ve inat ve [[demagoji/\u015fa\u015f\u0131rtmaca|ma\u011flata|]] ve [[b\xfcy\xfckl\xfck taslama/inatla inkar etme|m\xfck\xe2bere|]] ve [[aldatma/kand\u0131rma|i\u011ffal|]] ve g\xf6renek gibi \u015feytan\xee [[hilelerle/oyunlarla|desiselerle|]], \xe7ok [[imkans\u0131z \u015feyleri|muhalat\u0131|]] [[sonu\xe7 veren/netice veren|intac eden|]] [[inan\xe7s\u0131zl\u0131k|k\xfcf\xfcr|]] ve ink\xe2r\u0131 o [[talihsiz/mutsuz|bedbaht|]] insan [[g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015f\xfcndeki/\u015feklindeki|suretindeki|]] hayvanlara yutturmu\u015fsun.\\n\\n[[d\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc olarak|R\xe2bian|]]: Hem Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131 [[insan s\xf6z\xfc|kel\xe2m-\u0131 be\u015fer|]] [[varsaymak|farz etmek|]], [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]] ki: [[insanl\u0131k d\xfcnyas\u0131n\u0131n|\xc2lem-i insaniyetin|]] semas\u0131nda y\u0131ld\u0131zlar gibi parlayan [[saf ve temiz olan \xe2limlere/ger\xe7e\u011fi bulanlara|asfiyalara|]], [[son derece do\u011fru olanlara/peygamberlere en sad\u0131k olanlara|s\u0131dd\u0131k\xeenlere|]], [[b\xfcy\xfck velilere/kutuplara|aktablara|]] [[g\xf6rerek/g\xf6zlemleyerek|bilm\xfc\u015fahede|]] rehberlik eden ve [[apa\xe7\u0131k bir \u015fekilde|bilbedahe|]] [[s\xfcrekli/devaml\u0131|m\xfctemadiyen|]] hak ve [[do\u011frulu\u011fu/adaleti|hakkaniyeti|]], [[do\u011fruluk|s\u0131dk|]] ve sadakati, [[g\xfcven|emn|]] ve emaneti [[b\xfct\xfcn/genel|umum|]] [[olgunluk ehlinin tabakalar\u0131na/seviyelerine|tabakat-\u0131 ehl-i kemale|]] [[\xf6\u011freten|talim eden|]] ve [[iman\u0131n esaslar\u0131n\u0131n|erk\xe2n-\u0131 imaniyenin|]] [[hakikatleriyle/ger\xe7ekleriyle|hakaikiyle|]] ve [[\u0130slam\'\u0131n \u015fartlar\u0131n\u0131n/esaslar\u0131n\u0131n|erk\xe2n-\u0131 \u0130sl\xe2miyenin|]] [[d\xfcsturlar\u0131yla/prensipleriyle|desatiriyle|]] iki cihan\u0131n [[mutlulu\u011funu|saadetini|]] [[sa\u011flayan|temin eden|]] ve bu icraat\u0131n\u0131n [[\u015fahitli\u011fiyle|\u015fehadetiyle|]] [[zorunlu olarak/ister istemez|bizzarure|]] [[saf/temiz|h\xe2lis|]] hak ve [[kat\u0131ks\u0131z|safi|]] hakikat ve gayet do\u011fru ve pek ciddi olmak [[gereken|l\xe2z\u0131m gelen|]] bir kitab\u0131; kendi [[vas\u0131flar\u0131n\u0131n/niteliklerinin|evsaf\u0131n\u0131n|]] ve [[etkilerinin|tesirat\u0131n\u0131n|]] ve [[nurlar\u0131n\u0131n/\u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n|envar\u0131n\u0131n|]] z\u0131dd\u0131yla [[vas\u0131flanm\u0131\u015f/s\u0131fatlanm\u0131\u015f|muttas\u0131f|]] [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp/hayal edip|tasavvur edip|]] \u2013[[asla ve asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2 h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 [[uydurmalar/yapmac\u0131k \u015feyler|tasniat|]] ve iftiralar\u0131n [[toplam\u0131/birle\u015fimi|mecmuas\u0131|]] [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131yla|nazar\u0131yla|]] bakmak; [[\u015f\xfcphecileri/sofsitleri|sofesta\xeeleri|]] ve \u015feytanlar\u0131 dahi utand\u0131racak ve titretecek [[\xe7irkin/i\u011fren\xe7|\u015fen\xee\u2019|]] bir [[k\xfcf\xfcr sa\xe7mal\u0131\u011f\u0131/inan\xe7s\u0131zl\u0131k say\u0131klamas\u0131|hezeyan-\u0131 k\xfcfr\xee|]] olmakla beraber\u2026\\n\\n[[ortaya koydu\u011fu/a\xe7\u0131klad\u0131\u011f\u0131|\u0130zhar etti\u011fi|]] din ve [[\u0130slam \u015feriat\u0131n\u0131n/kanunlar\u0131n\u0131n|\u015feriat-\u0131 \u0130sl\xe2miyenin|]] [[\u015fahitli\u011fiyle|\u015fehadetiyle|]] ve [[hayat\u0131 boyunca|m\xfcddet-i hayat\u0131nda|]] g\xf6sterdi\u011fi [[ittifakla/herkesin kabul\xfcyle|bi\u2019l-ittifak|]] [[ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc|fevkal\xe2de|]] [[Allah\'tan sak\u0131nmas\u0131n\u0131n/g\xfcnahlardan ka\xe7\u0131nmas\u0131n\u0131n|takvas\u0131n\u0131n|]] ve [[saf/i\xe7ten|h\xe2lis|]] ve [[kat\u0131ks\u0131z|safi|]] [[kullu\u011funun|ubudiyetinin|]] [[delil olmas\u0131yla/g\xf6stermesiyle|del\xe2letiyle|]] ve [[ittifakla|bi\u2019l-ittifak|]] kendinde g\xf6r\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc [[g\xfczel ahlak\u0131n\u0131n|ahl\xe2k-\u0131 hasenesinin|]] [[gere\u011fiyle|iktizas\u0131yla|]] ve yeti\u015ftirdi\u011fi b\xfct\xfcn [[hakikat ehlinin/ger\xe7e\u011fi bulanlar\u0131n|ehl-i hakikatin|]] ve [[olgunluk sahiplerinin|sahib-i kemal\xe2t\u0131n|]] [[onaylamas\u0131yla/do\u011frulamas\u0131yla|tasdikiyle|]] en [[inan\xe7l\u0131/itikad\u0131 sa\u011flam|mutekid|]] en [[sa\u011flam/dayan\u0131kl\u0131|metin|]] en [[g\xfcvenilir|emin|]] en [[do\u011fru s\xf6zl\xfc|sad\u0131k|]] bir zat\u0131 \u2013[[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]] [[sonra (yine)|s\xfcmme|]] [[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]] y\xfcz bin kere [[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 [[inan\xe7s\u0131z|itikads\u0131z|]], en [[g\xfcvensiz|emniyetsiz|]], Allah\u2019tan korkmaz, yalandan \xe7ekinmez bir [[durumda|vaziyette|]] [[varsay\u0131p|farz edip|]], [[imkans\u0131zl\u0131klar\u0131n|muhalat\u0131n|]] en \xe7irkin ve [[nefret edilen/i\u011fren\xe7|menfur|]] bir [[\u015feklini/bi\xe7imini|suretini|]] ve [[sapk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131n|dalaletin|]] en zul\xfcml\xfc ve [[karanl\u0131kl\u0131|zul\xfcmatl\u0131|]] bir tarz\u0131n\u0131 [[i\u015flemek/yapmak|irtik\xe2b etmek|]] [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]].","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.21-19:19","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"},{"pageId":9,"rawText":"Elhas\u0131l: On Dokuzuncu Mektup\u2019un On Sekizinci \u0130\u015faret\u2019inde denildi\u011fi gibi nas\u0131l kulakl\u0131 \xe2m\xee tabakas\u0131 i\u2019caz-\u0131 Kur\u2019an fehminde demi\u015f: Kur\u2019an, b\xfct\xfcn dinledi\u011fim ve d\xfcnyada mevcud kitaplara k\u0131yas edilse hi\xe7birisine benzemiyor ve onlar\u0131n derecesinde de\u011fildir. \xd6yle ise ya Kur\u2019an umumun alt\u0131ndad\u0131r veya umumun fevkinde bir derecesi vard\u0131r. Umumun alt\u0131ndaki \u015f\u0131k ise muhal olmakla beraber, hi\xe7bir d\xfc\u015fman hatt\xe2 \u015feytan dahi diyemez ve kabul etmez. \xd6yle ise Kur\u2019an, umum kitaplar\u0131n fevkindedir. \xd6yle ise mu\u2019cizedir.\\n\\nAynen \xf6yle de biz de ilm-i us\xfbl ve fenn-i mant\u0131k\xe7a sebr \xfc taksim denilen en kat\u2019\xee h\xfcccetle deriz:\\n\\nEy \u015feytan ve ey \u015feytan\u0131n \u015fakirdleri! Kur\u2019an, ya ar\u015f-\u0131 a\u2019zamdan ve ism-i a\u2019zamdan gelmi\u015f bir kel\xe2mullaht\u0131r veyahut \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2 y\xfcz bin kere h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 yerde Allah\u2019tan korkmaz ve Allah\u2019\u0131 bilmez, itikads\u0131z bir be\u015ferin d\xfczmesidir. Bu ise ey \u015feytan! S\xe2b\u0131k h\xfcccetlere kar\u015f\u0131 bunu sen diyemezsin ve diyemezdin ve diyemeyeceksin. \xd6yle ise bizzarure ve bil\xe2-\u015f\xfcphe Kur\u2019an, H\xe2l\u0131k-\u0131 k\xe2inat\u2019\u0131n kel\xe2m\u0131d\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ortas\u0131 yoktur ve muhaldir ve olamaz. Nas\u0131l ki kat\u2019\xee bir surette ispat ettik, sen de g\xf6rd\xfcn ve dinledin.\\n\\nHem Muhammed aleyhissal\xe2t\xfc vessel\xe2m, ya Resulullah\u2019t\u0131r ve b\xfct\xfcn resullerin ekmeli ve b\xfct\xfcn mahlukat\u0131n efdalidir veyahut \u2013h\xe2\u015f\xe2 y\xfcz bin defa h\xe2\u015f\xe2\u2013 Allah\u2019a iftira etti\u011fi ve Allah\u2019\u0131 bilmedi\u011fi ve azab\u0131na inanmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in itikads\u0131z, esfel-i safil\xeene sukut etmi\u015f bir be\u015fer farz etmek (H\xe2\u015fiye[2]) l\xe2z\u0131m gelir. Bu ise ey iblis! Ne sen ve ne de g\xfcvendi\u011fin Avrupa feylesoflar\u0131 ve Asya m\xfcnaf\u0131klar\u0131 bunu diyemezsiniz ve diyememi\u015fsiniz ve diyemeyeceksiniz ve dememi\u015fsiniz ve demeyeceksiniz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc bu \u015f\u0131kk\u0131 dinleyecek ve kabul edecek d\xfcnyada yoktur. Onun i\xe7indir ki g\xfcvendi\u011fin o feylesoflar\u0131n en m\xfcfsidleri ve o m\xfcnaf\u0131klar\u0131n en vicdans\u0131zlar\u0131 dahi diyorlar ki: \u201cMuhammed-i Arab\xee (asm) \xe7ok ak\u0131ll\u0131 idi ve \xe7ok g\xfczel ahl\xe2kl\u0131 idi.\u201d\\n\\nMadem \u015fu mesele iki \u015f\u0131kka m\xfcnhas\u0131rd\u0131r ve madem ikinci \u015f\u0131k muhaldir ve hi\xe7bir kimse buna sahip \xe7\u0131km\u0131yor ve madem kat\u2019\xee h\xfcccetlerle ispat ettik ki ortas\u0131 yoktur. Elbette ve bizzarure senin ve hizb\xfc\u2019\u015f-\u015feytan\u0131n ra\u011fm\u0131na olarak bilbedahe ve bihakkalyak\xeen, Muhammed-i Arab\xee aleyhissal\xe2t\xfc vessel\xe2m Resulullah\u2019t\u0131r ve b\xfct\xfcn resullerin ekmelidir ve b\xfct\xfcn mahlukat\u0131n efdalidir.\\n\\n\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0639\u064e\u062f\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0651\u0650\\n\\n\u015eeytan\u0131n \u0130kinci K\xfc\xe7\xfck Bir \u0130tiraz\u0131\\n\\nSure-i \u0642\u0653 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0627\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062c\u0656\u064a\u062f\u0650 i okurken\\n\\n\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0641\u0650\u0638\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u064d \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u062f\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0642\u0656\u064a\u0628\u064c \u0639\u064e\u062a\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c \u06de \u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062a\u0650 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0642\u0651\u0650 \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u062a\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064f \u06de \u0648\u064e \u0646\u064f\u0641\u0650\u062e\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0631\u0650 \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0639\u0656\u064a\u062f\u0650 \u06de \u0648\u064e \u062c\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064f\u0644\u0651\u064f \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064d \u0645\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0642\u064c \u0648\u064e \u0634\u064e\u0647\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c \u06de \u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0641\u0656\u0649 \u063a\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064d \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u0670\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0634\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0643\u064e \u063a\u0650\u0637\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0643\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064e \u062d\u064e\u062f\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c \u06de \u0648\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0631\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064f\u0647\u064f \u0647\u0670\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0649\u0651\u064e \u0639\u064e\u062a\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c \u06de \u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u0656\u0649 \u062c\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0644\u0651\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0641\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064d\\n\\n\u015eu \xe2yetleri okurken \u015feytan dedi ki: \u201cKur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n en m\xfchim fesahatini, siz onun selasetinde ve vuzuhunda buluyorsunuz. Halbuki \u015fu \xe2yette nereden nereye atl\u0131yor? Sekerattan t\xe2 k\u0131yamete atl\u0131yor. Nefh-i S\xfbr\u2019dan muhasebenin hitam\u0131na intikal ediyor ve ondan cehenneme idhali zikrediyor. Bu acib atlamaklar i\xe7inde hangi selaset kal\u0131r? Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n ekser yerlerinde, b\xf6yle birbirinden uzak meseleleri birle\u015ftiriyor. B\xf6yle m\xfcnasebetsiz vaziyetle selaset, fesahat nerede kal\u0131r?\u201d\\n\\nElcevap: Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Mu\u2019ciz\xfc\u2019l-Beyan\u2019\u0131n esas-\u0131 i\u2019caz\u0131, en m\xfchimlerinden bel\xe2gat\u0131ndan sonra \xeecazd\u0131r. \xcecaz, i\u2019caz-\u0131 Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n en metin ve en m\xfchim bir esas\u0131d\u0131r. Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019de \u015fu mu\u2019cizane \xeecaz, o kadar \xe7oktur ve o kadar g\xfczeldir ki ehl-i tetkik, kar\u015f\u0131s\u0131nda hayrettedirler.\\n\\nMesela\\n\\n\u0648\u064e \u0642\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u064f \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0639\u0656\u0649 \u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0627\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0644\u0650\u0639\u0656\u0649 \u0648\u064e\u063a\u0656\u064a\u0636\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0636\u0650\u0649\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0648\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064f\u0648\u062f\u0650\u0649\u0651\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0642\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064f\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e","oldText":"[[Elhas\u0131l|K\u0131saca|\xd6zetle]]: On Dokuzuncu Mektup\u2019un On Sekizinci \u0130\u015faret\u2019inde denildi\u011fi gibi nas\u0131l kulakl\u0131 [[\xe2m\xee|s\u0131radan halk|okumam\u0131\u015f, avam]] tabakas\u0131 [[i\u2019caz-\u0131 Kur\u2019an|Kur\'an\'\u0131n mucizeli\u011fi|Kur\'an\'\u0131n benzerini yapmaktan aciz b\u0131rakmas\u0131]] [[fehminde|anlamas\u0131nda|kavramas\u0131nda]] demi\u015f: Kur\u2019an, b\xfct\xfcn dinledi\u011fim ve d\xfcnyada [[mevcud|var olan]] kitaplara k\u0131yas edilse hi\xe7birisine benzemiyor ve onlar\u0131n derecesinde de\u011fildir. \xd6yle ise ya Kur\u2019an [[umumun|genelin|herkesin]] alt\u0131ndad\u0131r veya [[umumun|genelin|herkesin]] [[fevkinde|\xfcst\xfcnde|yukar\u0131s\u0131nda]] bir derecesi vard\u0131r. [[Umumun|Genelin|Herkesin]] alt\u0131ndaki \u015f\u0131k ise [[muhal|imkans\u0131z|m\xfcmk\xfcn olmayan]] olmakla beraber, hi\xe7bir d\xfc\u015fman hatt\xe2 \u015feytan dahi diyemez ve kabul etmez. \xd6yle ise Kur\u2019an, [[umum|b\xfct\xfcn|genel]] kitaplar\u0131n [[fevkindedir|\xfcst\xfcndedir]]. \xd6yle ise [[mu\u2019cizedir|mucizedir|insanlar\u0131n benzerini yapmaktan aciz kald\u0131\u011f\u0131 ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc i\u015ftir]].\\r\\n\\r\\nAynen \xf6yle de biz de [[ilm-i us\xfbl|y\xf6ntem ilmi|f\u0131k\u0131h veya kelam metodolojisi]] ve [[fenn-i mant\u0131k\xe7a|mant\u0131k ilmince]] [[sebr \xfc taksim|olas\u0131l\u0131klar\u0131 eleyerek ispatlama|sondaj ve k\u0131s\u0131mlara ay\u0131rma metodu]] denilen en [[kat\u2019\xee|kesin]] [[h\xfcccetle|delille|kan\u0131tla]] deriz:\\r\\n\\r\\nEy \u015feytan ve ey \u015feytan\u0131n [[\u015fakirdleri|\xf6\u011frencileri|talebeleri]]! Kur\u2019an, ya [[ar\u015f-\u0131 a\u2019zamdan|en b\xfcy\xfck makamdan|Allah\'\u0131n kudret ve saltanat\u0131n\u0131n tecelli etti\u011fi en y\xfcksek makamdan]] ve [[ism-i a\u2019zamdan|en b\xfcy\xfck isimden|Allah\'\u0131n en b\xfcy\xfck isminden]] gelmi\u015f bir [[kel\xe2mullaht\u0131r|Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfcd\xfcr]] veyahut \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla, y\xfcz bin defa hay\u0131r|Allah korusun, kesinlikle \xf6yle de\u011fil]] y\xfcz bin kere [[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]]\u2013 yerde Allah\u2019tan korkmaz ve Allah\u2019\u0131 bilmez, [[itikads\u0131z|inan\xe7s\u0131z]] bir be\u015ferin d\xfczmesidir. Bu ise ey \u015feytan! [[S\xe2b\u0131k|Ge\xe7en|\xd6nceki]] [[h\xfcccetlere|delillere|kan\u0131tlara]] kar\u015f\u0131 bunu sen diyemezsin ve diyemezdin ve diyemeyeceksin. \xd6yle ise [[bizzarure|zorunlu olarak|ister istemez]] ve [[bil\xe2-\u015f\xfcphe|\u015f\xfcphesiz]] Kur\u2019an, [[H\xe2l\u0131k-\u0131 k\xe2inat\u2019\u0131n|k\xe2inat Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n\u0131n]] [[kel\xe2m\u0131d\u0131r|s\xf6z\xfcd\xfcr]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ortas\u0131 yoktur ve [[muhaldir|imkans\u0131zd\u0131r]] ve olamaz. Nas\u0131l ki [[kat\u2019\xee|kesin]] bir [[surette|bi\xe7imde|\u015fekilde]] ispat ettik, sen de g\xf6rd\xfcn ve dinledin.\\r\\n\\r\\nHem Muhammed aleyhissal\xe2t\xfc vessel\xe2m, ya Resulullah\u2019t\u0131r ve b\xfct\xfcn resullerin [[ekmeli|en m\xfckemmeli|en kusursuzu]] ve b\xfct\xfcn [[mahlukat\u0131n|yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flar\u0131n]] [[efdalidir|en faziletlisidir|en \xfcst\xfcn\xfcd\xfcr]] veyahut \u2013[[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]] y\xfcz bin defa [[h\xe2\u015f\xe2|asla]]\u2013 Allah\u2019a iftira etti\u011fi ve Allah\u2019\u0131 bilmedi\u011fi ve azab\u0131na inanmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in [[itikads\u0131z|inan\xe7s\u0131z]], [[esfel-i safil\xeene|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131lar\u0131n en a\u015fa\u011f\u0131s\u0131na|cehennemin en derin tabakas\u0131na]] [[sukut etmi\u015f|d\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f|al\xe7alm\u0131\u015f]] bir be\u015fer [[farz etmek|varsaymak|kabul etmek]] ([[H\xe2\u015fiye|Dipnot]][2]) l\xe2z\u0131m gelir. Bu ise ey iblis! Ne sen ve ne de g\xfcvendi\u011fin Avrupa [[feylesoflar\u0131|filozoflar\u0131]] ve Asya m\xfcnaf\u0131klar\u0131 bunu diyemezsiniz ve diyememi\u015fsiniz ve diyemeyeceksiniz ve dememi\u015fsiniz ve demeyeceksiniz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc bu \u015f\u0131kk\u0131 dinleyecek ve kabul edecek d\xfcnyada yoktur. Onun i\xe7indir ki g\xfcvendi\u011fin o [[feylesoflar\u0131n|filozoflar\u0131n]] en [[m\xfcfsidleri|bozguncular\u0131|fesat \xe7\u0131karanlar\u0131]] ve o m\xfcnaf\u0131klar\u0131n en vicdans\u0131zlar\u0131 dahi diyorlar ki: \u201cMuhammed-i Arab\xee (asm) \xe7ok ak\u0131ll\u0131 idi ve \xe7ok g\xfczel ahl\xe2kl\u0131 idi.\u201d\\r\\n\\r\\nMadem \u015fu mesele iki \u015f\u0131kka [[m\xfcnhas\u0131rd\u0131r|s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131d\u0131r|aittir]] ve madem ikinci \u015f\u0131k [[muhaldir|imkans\u0131zd\u0131r]] ve hi\xe7bir kimse buna sahip \xe7\u0131km\u0131yor ve madem [[kat\u2019\xee|kesin]] [[h\xfcccetlerle|delillerle|kan\u0131tlarla]] ispat ettik ki ortas\u0131 yoktur. Elbette ve [[bizzarure|zorunlu olarak|ister istemez]] senin ve [[hizb\xfc\u2019\u015f-\u015feytan\u0131n|\u015feytan\u0131n taraf\u0131n\u0131n|\u015feytan\u0131n partisinin/grubunun]] [[ra\u011fm\u0131na|z\u0131dd\u0131na|inad\u0131na]] olarak [[bilbedahe|apa\xe7\u0131k|besbelli]] ve [[bihakkalyak\xeen|ya\u015fayarak kesin bilmekle|ger\xe7e\u011fin ta kendisi olarak]], Muhammed-i Arab\xee aleyhissal\xe2t\xfc vessel\xe2m Resulullah\u2019t\u0131r ve b\xfct\xfcn resullerin [[ekmelidir|en m\xfckemmelidir]] ve b\xfct\xfcn [[mahlukat\u0131n|yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flar\u0131n]] [[efdalidir|en faziletlisidir]].\\r\\n\\r\\n[[\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0639\u064e\u062f\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u0651|Meleklerin, insanlar\u0131n ve cinlerin say\u0131s\u0131nca ona salat ve selam olsun]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u015eeytan\u0131n \u0130kinci K\xfc\xe7\xfck Bir \u0130tiraz\u0131\\r\\n\\r\\nSure-i [[\u0642\u0653 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0627\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062c\u0656\u064a\u062f\u0650|K\xe2f. \u015eerefli Kur\u2019an\u2019a andolsun]] i okurken\\r\\n\\r\\n[[\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0641\u0650\u0638\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u064d \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u062f\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0642\u0656\u064a\u0628\u064c \u0639\u064e\u062a\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c|\u0130nsan hi\xe7bir s\xf6z s\xf6ylemez ki, yan\u0131nda g\xf6zetleyen yazmaya haz\u0131r bir melek bulunmas\u0131n]] \u06de [[\u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062a\u0650 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0642\u0650\u0651 \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u062a\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064f|\xd6l\xfcm sarho\u015flu\u011fu ger\xe7ekten gelir de: \u0130\u015fte (ey insan) bu, senin \xf6teden beri ka\xe7t\u0131\u011f\u0131n \u015feydir, denir]] \u06de [[\u0648\u064e \u0646\u064f\u0641\u0650\u062e\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0631\u0650 \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0639\u0656\u064a\u062f\u0650|S\xfbr\u2019a \xfcf\xfcr\xfcl\xfcr; i\u015fte bu, gelece\u011fi vaad edilen g\xfcnd\xfcr]] \u06de [[\u0648\u064e \u062c\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0651 \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064d \u0645\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0642\u064c \u0648\u064e \u0634\u064e\u0647\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c|Herkes, yan\u0131nda bir s\xfcr\xfcc\xfc ve bir de \u015fahit oldu\u011fu halde gelir]] \u06de [[\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0641\u0656\u0649 \u063a\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064d \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u0670\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0634\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0643\u064e \u063a\u0650\u0637\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0643\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064e \u062d\u064e\u062f\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c|Andolsun ki sen bundan gaflette idin; i\u015fte \u015fimdi senden perdeni kald\u0131rd\u0131k, bug\xfcn art\u0131k g\xf6z\xfcn keskindir]] \u06de [[\u0648\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0631\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064f\u0647\u064f \u0647\u0670\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0649\u064e\u0651 \u0639\u064e\u062a\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c|Beraberindeki (melek) \u015f\xf6yle der: \u0130\u015fte bu yan\u0131mdaki haz\u0131rd\u0131r]] \u06de [[\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u0656\u0649 \u062c\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0644\u064e\u0651 \u0643\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064d|(Allah \u015f\xf6yle buyurur): At\u0131n cehenneme her inat\xe7\u0131 k\xe2firi]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u015eu \xe2yetleri okurken \u015feytan dedi ki: \u201cKur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n en m\xfchim [[fesahatini|ifade d\xfczg\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc|s\xf6z\xfcn a\xe7\u0131k ve kusursuz olmas\u0131n\u0131]], siz onun [[selasetinde|ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda|s\xf6z\xfcn kolayca anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131r ve ak\u0131c\u0131 olmas\u0131nda]] ve [[vuzuhunda|a\xe7\u0131kl\u0131\u011f\u0131nda|belirginli\u011finde]] buluyorsunuz. Halbuki \u015fu \xe2yette nereden nereye atl\u0131yor? [[Sekerattan|\xf6l\xfcm sarho\u015flu\u011fundan|\xf6l\xfcm an\u0131ndaki bayg\u0131nl\u0131ktan]] t\xe2 k\u0131yamete atl\u0131yor. [[Nefh-i S\xfbr\u2019dan|Sur\'a \xfcf\xfcr\xfclmesinden]] [[muhasebenin|hesap g\xf6rmenin]] [[hitam\u0131na|sonuna|bitimine]] [[intikal ediyor|ge\xe7iyor]] ve ondan cehenneme [[idhali|dahil edilmeyi|koymay\u0131]] [[zikrediyor|an\u0131yor|s\xf6yl\xfcyor]]. Bu [[acib|\u015fa\u015f\u0131lacak|garip]] atlamaklar i\xe7inde hangi [[selaset|ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131k]] kal\u0131r? Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n [[ekser|\xe7o\u011fu]] yerlerinde, b\xf6yle birbirinden uzak meseleleri birle\u015ftiriyor. B\xf6yle [[m\xfcnasebetsiz|uygunsuz|ili\u015fkisiz]] [[vaziyetle|durumla]] [[selaset|ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131k]], [[fesahat|ifade d\xfczg\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc]] nerede kal\u0131r?\u201d\\r\\n\\r\\n[[Elcevap|Cevap|Yan\u0131t]]: [[Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Mu\u2019ciz\xfc\u2019l-Beyan\u2019\u0131n|beyan\u0131 mucize olan Kur\'an\'\u0131n|a\xe7\u0131klamalar\u0131yla aciz b\u0131rakan Kur\'an\'\u0131n]] [[esas-\u0131 i\u2019caz\u0131|mucizelik esas\u0131|mucize olu\u015funun temeli]], en m\xfchimlerinden [[bel\xe2gat\u0131ndan|s\xf6z\xfcn d\xfczg\xfcn ve yerinde s\xf6ylenmesinden|edebi sanat\u0131ndan]] sonra [[\xeecazd\u0131r|az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatmakt\u0131r]]. [[\xcecaz|Az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatma]], [[i\u2019caz-\u0131 Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n|Kur\'an\'\u0131n mucizeli\u011finin]] en [[metin|sa\u011flam]] ve en m\xfchim bir esas\u0131d\u0131r. [[Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019de|hikmetli Kur\'an\'da]] \u015fu [[mu\u2019cizane|mucizevi bir \u015fekilde]] [[\xeecaz|az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatma]], o kadar \xe7oktur ve o kadar g\xfczeldir ki [[ehl-i tetkik|inceleme ehli|ara\u015ft\u0131rmac\u0131lar]], kar\u015f\u0131s\u0131nda hayrettedirler.\\r\\n\\r\\nMesela\\r\\n\\r\\n[[\u0648\u064e \u0642\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u064f \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0639\u0656\u0649 \u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0627\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0644\u0650\u0639\u0656\u0649 \u0648\u064e\u063a\u0656\u064a\u0636\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0636\u0650\u0649\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0648\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064f\u0648\u062f\u0650\u0649\u0650\u0651 \u0648\u064e\u0642\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064f\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e|Denildi ki: \u201cEy yer, suyunu yut! Ey g\xf6k, sen de suyunu tut!\u201d Su \xe7ekildi, i\u015f bitirildi; gemi C\xfbd\xee\u2019ye oturdu. Ve \u201cZalimler toplulu\u011fu Allah\u2019\u0131n rahmetinden uzak olsun!\u201d denildi.]]","modernText":"[[K\u0131saca|Elhas\u0131l|\xd6zetle]]: On Dokuzuncu Mektup\u2019un On Sekizinci \u0130\u015faret\u2019inde denildi\u011fi gibi nas\u0131l kulakl\u0131 [[s\u0131radan halk|\xe2m\xee|okumam\u0131\u015f, avam]] tabakas\u0131 [[Kur\'an\'\u0131n mucizeli\u011fi|i\u2019caz-\u0131 Kur\u2019an|Kur\'an\'\u0131n benzerini yapmaktan aciz b\u0131rakmas\u0131]] [[anlamas\u0131nda|fehminde|kavramas\u0131nda]] demi\u015f: Kur\u2019an, b\xfct\xfcn dinledi\u011fim ve d\xfcnyada [[var olan|mevcud|]] kitaplara k\u0131yas edilse hi\xe7birisine benzemiyor ve onlar\u0131n derecesinde de\u011fildir. \xd6yle ise ya Kur\u2019an [[genelin|umumun|herkesin]] alt\u0131ndad\u0131r veya [[genelin|umumun|herkesin]] [[\xfcst\xfcnde|fevkinde|yukar\u0131s\u0131nda]] bir derecesi vard\u0131r. [[Genelin|Umumun|Herkesin]] alt\u0131ndaki \u015f\u0131k ise [[imkans\u0131z|muhal|m\xfcmk\xfcn olmayan]] olmakla beraber, hi\xe7bir d\xfc\u015fman hatt\xe2 \u015feytan dahi diyemez ve kabul etmez. \xd6yle ise Kur\u2019an, [[b\xfct\xfcn|umum|genel]] kitaplar\u0131n [[\xfcst\xfcndedir|fevkindedir|]]. \xd6yle ise [[mucizedir|mu\u2019cizedir|insanlar\u0131n benzerini yapmaktan aciz kald\u0131\u011f\u0131 ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfc i\u015ftir]].\\r\\n\\r\\nAynen \xf6yle de biz de [[y\xf6ntem ilmi|ilm-i us\xfbl|f\u0131k\u0131h veya kelam metodolojisi]] ve [[mant\u0131k ilmince|fenn-i mant\u0131k\xe7a|]] [[olas\u0131l\u0131klar\u0131 eleyerek ispatlama|sebr \xfc taksim|sondaj ve k\u0131s\u0131mlara ay\u0131rma metodu]] denilen en [[kesin|kat\u2019\xee|]] [[delille|h\xfcccetle|kan\u0131tla]] deriz:\\r\\n\\r\\nEy \u015feytan ve ey \u015feytan\u0131n [[\xf6\u011frencileri|\u015fakirdleri|talebeleri]]! Kur\u2019an, ya [[en b\xfcy\xfck makamdan|ar\u015f-\u0131 a\u2019zamdan|Allah\'\u0131n kudret ve saltanat\u0131n\u0131n tecelli etti\u011fi en y\xfcksek makamdan]] ve [[en b\xfcy\xfck isimden|ism-i a\u2019zamdan|Allah\'\u0131n en b\xfcy\xfck isminden]] gelmi\u015f bir [[Allah\'\u0131n s\xf6z\xfcd\xfcr|kel\xe2mullaht\u0131r|]] veyahut \u2013[[asla, y\xfcz bin defa hay\u0131r|h\xe2\u015f\xe2 s\xfcmme h\xe2\u015f\xe2|Allah korusun, kesinlikle \xf6yle de\u011fil]] y\xfcz bin kere [[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 yerde Allah\u2019tan korkmaz ve Allah\u2019\u0131 bilmez, [[inan\xe7s\u0131z|itikads\u0131z|]] bir be\u015ferin d\xfczmesidir. Bu ise ey \u015feytan! [[Ge\xe7en|S\xe2b\u0131k|\xd6nceki]] [[delillere|h\xfcccetlere|kan\u0131tlara]] kar\u015f\u0131 bunu sen diyemezsin ve diyemezdin ve diyemeyeceksin. \xd6yle ise [[zorunlu olarak|bizzarure|ister istemez]] ve [[\u015f\xfcphesiz|bil\xe2-\u015f\xfcphe|]] Kur\u2019an, [[k\xe2inat Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n\u0131n|H\xe2l\u0131k-\u0131 k\xe2inat\u2019\u0131n|]] [[s\xf6z\xfcd\xfcr|kel\xe2m\u0131d\u0131r|]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ortas\u0131 yoktur ve [[imkans\u0131zd\u0131r|muhaldir|]] ve olamaz. Nas\u0131l ki [[kesin|kat\u2019\xee|]] bir [[bi\xe7imde|surette|\u015fekilde]] ispat ettik, sen de g\xf6rd\xfcn ve dinledin.\\r\\n\\r\\nHem Muhammed aleyhissal\xe2t\xfc vessel\xe2m, ya Resulullah\u2019t\u0131r ve b\xfct\xfcn resullerin [[en m\xfckemmeli|ekmeli|en kusursuzu]] ve b\xfct\xfcn [[yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flar\u0131n|mahlukat\u0131n|]] [[en faziletlisidir|efdalidir|en \xfcst\xfcn\xfcd\xfcr]] veyahut \u2013[[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]] y\xfcz bin defa [[asla|h\xe2\u015f\xe2|]]\u2013 Allah\u2019a iftira etti\u011fi ve Allah\u2019\u0131 bilmedi\u011fi ve azab\u0131na inanmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in [[inan\xe7s\u0131z|itikads\u0131z|]], [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131lar\u0131n en a\u015fa\u011f\u0131s\u0131na|esfel-i safil\xeene|cehennemin en derin tabakas\u0131na]] [[d\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f|sukut etmi\u015f|al\xe7alm\u0131\u015f]] bir be\u015fer [[varsaymak|farz etmek|kabul etmek]] ([[Dipnot|H\xe2\u015fiye|]][2]) l\xe2z\u0131m gelir. Bu ise ey iblis! Ne sen ve ne de g\xfcvendi\u011fin Avrupa [[filozoflar\u0131|feylesoflar\u0131|]] ve Asya m\xfcnaf\u0131klar\u0131 bunu diyemezsiniz ve diyememi\u015fsiniz ve diyemeyeceksiniz ve dememi\u015fsiniz ve demeyeceksiniz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc bu \u015f\u0131kk\u0131 dinleyecek ve kabul edecek d\xfcnyada yoktur. Onun i\xe7indir ki g\xfcvendi\u011fin o [[filozoflar\u0131n|feylesoflar\u0131n|]] en [[bozguncular\u0131|m\xfcfsidleri|fesat \xe7\u0131karanlar\u0131]] ve o m\xfcnaf\u0131klar\u0131n en vicdans\u0131zlar\u0131 dahi diyorlar ki: \u201cMuhammed-i Arab\xee (asm) \xe7ok ak\u0131ll\u0131 idi ve \xe7ok g\xfczel ahl\xe2kl\u0131 idi.\u201d\\r\\n\\r\\nMadem \u015fu mesele iki \u015f\u0131kka [[s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131d\u0131r|m\xfcnhas\u0131rd\u0131r|aittir]] ve madem ikinci \u015f\u0131k [[imkans\u0131zd\u0131r|muhaldir|]] ve hi\xe7bir kimse buna sahip \xe7\u0131km\u0131yor ve madem [[kesin|kat\u2019\xee|]] [[delillerle|h\xfcccetlerle|kan\u0131tlarla]] ispat ettik ki ortas\u0131 yoktur. Elbette ve [[zorunlu olarak|bizzarure|ister istemez]] senin ve [[\u015feytan\u0131n taraf\u0131n\u0131n|hizb\xfc\u2019\u015f-\u015feytan\u0131n|\u015feytan\u0131n partisinin/grubunun]] [[z\u0131dd\u0131na|ra\u011fm\u0131na|inad\u0131na]] olarak [[apa\xe7\u0131k|bilbedahe|besbelli]] ve [[ya\u015fayarak kesin bilmekle|bihakkalyak\xeen|ger\xe7e\u011fin ta kendisi olarak]], Muhammed-i Arab\xee aleyhissal\xe2t\xfc vessel\xe2m Resulullah\u2019t\u0131r ve b\xfct\xfcn resullerin [[en m\xfckemmelidir|ekmelidir|]] ve b\xfct\xfcn [[yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flar\u0131n|mahlukat\u0131n|]] [[en faziletlisidir|efdalidir|]].\\r\\n\\r\\n[[Meleklerin, insanlar\u0131n ve cinlerin say\u0131s\u0131nca ona salat ve selam olsun|\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0639\u064e\u062f\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u0651|]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u015eeytan\u0131n \u0130kinci K\xfc\xe7\xfck Bir \u0130tiraz\u0131\\r\\n\\r\\nSure-i [[K\xe2f. \u015eerefli Kur\u2019an\u2019a andolsun|\u0642\u0653 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0627\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062c\u0656\u064a\u062f\u0650|]] i okurken\\r\\n\\r\\n[[\u0130nsan hi\xe7bir s\xf6z s\xf6ylemez ki, yan\u0131nda g\xf6zetleyen yazmaya haz\u0131r bir melek bulunmas\u0131n|\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0641\u0650\u0638\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u064d \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u062f\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0642\u0656\u064a\u0628\u064c \u0639\u064e\u062a\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c|]] \u06de [[\xd6l\xfcm sarho\u015flu\u011fu ger\xe7ekten gelir de: \u0130\u015fte (ey insan) bu, senin \xf6teden beri ka\xe7t\u0131\u011f\u0131n \u015feydir, denir|\u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062a\u0650 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0642\u0650\u0651 \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u062a\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064f|]] \u06de [[S\xfbr\u2019a \xfcf\xfcr\xfcl\xfcr; i\u015fte bu, gelece\u011fi vaad edilen g\xfcnd\xfcr|\u0648\u064e \u0646\u064f\u0641\u0650\u062e\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0631\u0650 \u0630\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0639\u0656\u064a\u062f\u0650|]] \u06de [[Herkes, yan\u0131nda bir s\xfcr\xfcc\xfc ve bir de \u015fahit oldu\u011fu halde gelir|\u0648\u064e \u062c\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0651 \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064d \u0645\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0642\u064c \u0648\u064e \u0634\u064e\u0647\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c|]] \u06de [[Andolsun ki sen bundan gaflette idin; i\u015fte \u015fimdi senden perdeni kald\u0131rd\u0131k, bug\xfcn art\u0131k g\xf6z\xfcn keskindir|\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0641\u0656\u0649 \u063a\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064d \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u0670\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0634\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0643\u064e \u063a\u0650\u0637\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0643\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064e \u062d\u064e\u062f\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c|]] \u06de [[Beraberindeki (melek) \u015f\xf6yle der: \u0130\u015fte bu yan\u0131mdaki haz\u0131rd\u0131r|\u0648\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0631\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064f\u0647\u064f \u0647\u0670\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0649\u064e\u0651 \u0639\u064e\u062a\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064c|]] \u06de [[(Allah \u015f\xf6yle buyurur): At\u0131n cehenneme her inat\xe7\u0131 k\xe2firi|\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u0656\u0649 \u062c\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0644\u064e\u0651 \u0643\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0656\u064a\u062f\u064d|]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u015eu \xe2yetleri okurken \u015feytan dedi ki: \u201cKur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n en m\xfchim [[ifade d\xfczg\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc|fesahatini|s\xf6z\xfcn a\xe7\u0131k ve kusursuz olmas\u0131n\u0131]], siz onun [[ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda|selasetinde|s\xf6z\xfcn kolayca anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131r ve ak\u0131c\u0131 olmas\u0131nda]] ve [[a\xe7\u0131kl\u0131\u011f\u0131nda|vuzuhunda|belirginli\u011finde]] buluyorsunuz. Halbuki \u015fu \xe2yette nereden nereye atl\u0131yor? [[\xf6l\xfcm sarho\u015flu\u011fundan|Sekerattan|\xf6l\xfcm an\u0131ndaki bayg\u0131nl\u0131ktan]] t\xe2 k\u0131yamete atl\u0131yor. [[Sur\'a \xfcf\xfcr\xfclmesinden|Nefh-i S\xfbr\u2019dan|]] [[hesap g\xf6rmenin|muhasebenin|]] [[sonuna|hitam\u0131na|bitimine]] [[ge\xe7iyor|intikal ediyor|]] ve ondan cehenneme [[dahil edilmeyi|idhali|koymay\u0131]] [[an\u0131yor|zikrediyor|s\xf6yl\xfcyor]]. Bu [[\u015fa\u015f\u0131lacak|acib|garip]] atlamaklar i\xe7inde hangi [[ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131k|selaset|]] kal\u0131r? Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n [[\xe7o\u011fu|ekser|]] yerlerinde, b\xf6yle birbirinden uzak meseleleri birle\u015ftiriyor. B\xf6yle [[uygunsuz|m\xfcnasebetsiz|ili\u015fkisiz]] [[durumla|vaziyetle|]] [[ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131k|selaset|]], [[ifade d\xfczg\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc|fesahat|]] nerede kal\u0131r?\u201d\\r\\n\\r\\n[[Cevap|Elcevap|Yan\u0131t]]: [[beyan\u0131 mucize olan Kur\'an\'\u0131n|Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Mu\u2019ciz\xfc\u2019l-Beyan\u2019\u0131n|a\xe7\u0131klamalar\u0131yla aciz b\u0131rakan Kur\'an\'\u0131n]] [[mucizelik esas\u0131|esas-\u0131 i\u2019caz\u0131|mucize olu\u015funun temeli]], en m\xfchimlerinden [[s\xf6z\xfcn d\xfczg\xfcn ve yerinde s\xf6ylenmesinden|bel\xe2gat\u0131ndan|edebi sanat\u0131ndan]] sonra [[az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatmakt\u0131r|\xeecazd\u0131r|]]. [[Az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatma|\xcecaz|]], [[Kur\'an\'\u0131n mucizeli\u011finin|i\u2019caz-\u0131 Kur\u2019an\u2019\u0131n|]] en [[sa\u011flam|metin|]] ve en m\xfchim bir esas\u0131d\u0131r. [[hikmetli Kur\'an\'da|Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019de|]] \u015fu [[mucizevi bir \u015fekilde|mu\u2019cizane|]] [[az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatma|\xeecaz|]], o kadar \xe7oktur ve o kadar g\xfczeldir ki [[inceleme ehli|ehl-i tetkik|ara\u015ft\u0131rmac\u0131lar]], kar\u015f\u0131s\u0131nda hayrettedirler.\\r\\n\\r\\nMesela\\r\\n\\r\\n[[Denildi ki: \u201cEy yer, suyunu yut! Ey g\xf6k, sen de suyunu tut!\u201d Su \xe7ekildi, i\u015f bitirildi; gemi C\xfbd\xee\u2019ye oturdu. Ve \u201cZalimler toplulu\u011fu Allah\u2019\u0131n rahmetinden uzak olsun!\u201d denildi.|\u0648\u064e \u0642\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u064f \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0639\u0656\u0649 \u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0627\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0644\u0650\u0639\u0656\u0649 \u0648\u064e\u063a\u0656\u064a\u0636\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0653\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0636\u0650\u0649\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0648\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064f\u0648\u062f\u0650\u0649\u0650\u0651 \u0648\u064e\u0642\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064f\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e|]]","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.25-21:08","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:08"},{"pageId":10,"rawText":"K\u0131sa birka\xe7 c\xfcmle ile Tufan h\xe2dise-i az\xeemesini netaiciyle \xf6yle \xeecazk\xe2rane ve mu\u2019cizane beyan ediyor ki \xe7ok ehl-i bel\xe2gat\u0131, bel\xe2gat\u0131na secde ettirmi\u015f.\\n\\nHem mesela\\n\\n\u0643\u064e\u0630\u0651\u064e\u0628\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0637\u064e\u063a\u0652\u0648\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0627\u0650\u0630\u0650 \u0627\u0646\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0634\u0652\u0642\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0642\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0642\u0652\u064a\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0630\u0651\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064f\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0648\u0651\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064f \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte kavm-i Semud\u2019un acib ve m\xfchim h\xe2disat\u0131n\u0131 ve netaicini ve s\xfb-i \xe2k\u0131betlerini, b\xf6yle k\u0131sa birka\xe7 c\xfcmle ile \xeecaz i\xe7inde bir i\u2019caz ile selasetli ve vuzuhlu ve fehmi ihl\xe2l etmez bir tarzda beyan ediyor.\\n\\nHem mesela\\n\\n\u0648\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0630\u0652 \u0630\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0645\u064f\u063a\u064e\u0627\u0636\u0650\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0638\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0642\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0670\u0649 \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u0651\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u0656\u0649 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0638\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0642\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 c\xfcmlesinden \u0641\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0670\u0649 \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u0651\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 c\xfcmlesine kadar \xe7ok c\xfcmleler matv\xeedir. O mezk\xfbr olmayan c\xfcmleler; fehmi ihl\xe2l etmiyor, selasete zarar vermiyor. Hazret-i Yunus aleyhissel\xe2m\u0131n k\u0131ssas\u0131ndan m\xfchim esaslar\u0131 zikreder. M\xfcteb\xe2kisini akla havale eder.\\n\\nHem mesela, Sure-i Yusuf\u2019ta \u0641\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0633\u0650\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650 kelimesinden \u064a\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064f\u0641\u064f \u0627\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u0650\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0642\u064f ortas\u0131nda yedi sekiz c\xfcmle \xeecaz ile tayyedilmi\u015f. Hi\xe7 fehmi ihl\xe2l etmiyor, selasetine zarar vermiyor.\\n\\nBu \xe7e\u015fit mu\u2019cizane \xeecazlar Kur\u2019an\u2019da pek \xe7oktur. Hem pek g\xfczeldir.\\n\\nAmma Sure-i Kaf\u2019\u0131n \xe2yeti ise ondaki \xeecaz pek acib ve mu\u2019cizanedir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc k\xe2firin pek m\xfcthi\u015f ve \xe7ok uzun ve bir g\xfcn\xfc elli bin sene olan istikbaline ve o istikbalin deh\u015fetli ink\u0131labat\u0131nda k\xe2firin ba\u015f\u0131na gelecek el\xeem ve m\xfchim h\xe2disata birer birer parmak bas\u0131yor. \u015eim\u015fek gibi fikri, onlar \xfcst\xfcnde gezdiriyor. O pek \xe7ok uzun zaman\u0131, haz\u0131r bir sahife gibi nazara g\xf6sterir. Zikredilmeyen h\xe2disat\u0131 hayale havale edip ulvi bir selasetle beyan eder.\\n\\n\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064f\u0631\u0650\u0626\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0627\u0670\u0646\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u0650\u062a\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u062a\u064f\u0631\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey \u015feytan! \u015eimdi bir s\xf6z\xfcn daha varsa s\xf6yle\u2026\\n\\n\u015eeytan der: Bunlara kar\u015f\u0131 gelemem, m\xfcdafaa edemem. Fakat \xe7ok ahmaklar var, beni dinliyorlar ve insan suretinde \xe7ok \u015feytanlar var, bana yard\u0131m ediyorlar ve feylesoflardan \xe7ok firavunlar var, enaniyetlerini ok\u015fayan meseleleri benden ders al\u0131yorlar. Senin bu gibi s\xf6zlerin ne\u015frine set \xe7ekerler. Bunun i\xe7in sana teslim-i silah etmem!\\n\\n\u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0643\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f\\n\\n***\\n\\n[1] H\xe2\u015fiye: Evet, k\xfcre-i arz k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle beraber semavata kar\u015f\u0131 gelebilir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc nas\u0131l ki daim\xee bir \xe7e\u015fme, v\xe2ridats\u0131z b\xfcy\xfck bir g\xf6lden daha b\xfcy\xfck denilebilir. Hem bir \xf6l\xe7ek ile bir \u015fey \xf6l\xe7erek ba\u015fka yere nakledilen ve onun elinden ge\xe7mi\u015f ve ona girmi\u015f \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015f bir mahsulatla, zahiren binler defa \xf6l\xe7ekten b\xfcy\xfck ve da\u011f gibi bir cisimle o \xf6l\xe7ek muvazeneye \xe7\u0131kabilir.\\n\\nAynen \xf6yle de k\xfcre-i arz, Cenab-\u0131 Hak onu sanat\u0131na bir me\u015fher ve icad\u0131na bir mah\u015fer ve hikmetine medar ve kudretine mazhar ve rahmetine mezher ve cennetine mezraa ve hadsiz k\xe2inata ve mahlukat \xe2lemlerine \xf6l\xe7ek ve mazi denizlerine ve gayb \xe2lemine akacak bir \xe7e\u015fme h\xfckm\xfcnde icad etmi\u015f. Her sene kat kat ve katmerli y\xfcz bin tarzda, masnuattan dokunmu\u015f g\xf6mleklerini de\u011fi\u015ftirdi\u011fi ve \xe7ok defa dolup maziye bo\u015faltarak gayb \xe2lemine d\xf6kt\xfc\u011f\xfc b\xfct\xfcn o m\xfcteceddid \xe2lemleri ve arz\u0131n m\xfcteaddid g\xf6mleklerini nazara al, yani b\xfct\xfcn mazisini haz\u0131r farz et. Sonra yeknesak ve bir derece basit semavata kar\u015f\u0131 muvazene et. G\xf6receksin ki arz, ziyade gelmezse noksan da kalmaz. \u0130\u015fte \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650 s\u0131rr\u0131n\u0131 anla.\\n\\n[2] H\xe2\u015fiye: Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem, k\xe2firlerin k\xfcfriyatlar\u0131n\u0131 ve galiz tabiratlar\u0131n\u0131 iptal etmek i\xe7in zikretti\u011fine istinaden, ehl-i dalaletin fikr-i k\xfcfr\xeelerinin b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn muhaliyetini ve b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn \xe7\xfcr\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc g\xf6stermek i\xe7in \u015fu tabirat\u0131 farz-\u0131 muhal suretinde, titreyerek kullanmaya mecbur oldum.","oldText":"K\u0131sa birka\xe7 c\xfcmle ile [[Tufan h\xe2dise-i az\xeemesini|Tufan b\xfcy\xfck olay\u0131n\u0131|Nuh Tufan\u0131 denilen o b\xfcy\xfck olay\u0131]] [[netaiciyle|sonu\xe7lar\u0131yla|neticeleriyle]] \xf6yle [[\xeecazk\xe2rane|k\u0131saca ve \xf6zl\xfcce|az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatarak]] ve [[mu\u2019cizane|mucizevi bir \u015fekilde|mucize gibi]] [[beyan ediyor|a\xe7\u0131kl\u0131yor|anlat\u0131yor]] ki \xe7ok [[ehl-i bel\xe2gat\u0131|belagat ehlini|s\xf6z\xfc g\xfczel ve etkili s\xf6yleyenleri]], [[bel\xe2gat\u0131na|s\xf6z sanat\u0131na|edebi \xfcst\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfcne]] secde ettirmi\u015f.\\r\\n\\r\\nHem mesela\\r\\n\\r\\n[[\u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0651\u0628\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0637\u064e\u063a\u0652\u0648\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0627\u0650\u0630\u0650 \u0627\u0646\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0634\u0652\u0642\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0642\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0642\u0652\u064a\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0651\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0651\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0648\u0651\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064f \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627|Sem\xfbd (kavmi), azg\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131 y\xfcz\xfcnden (peygamberini) yalanlad\u0131. Onlar\u0131n en bedbaht\u0131 (deveyi kesmek i\xe7in) at\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda, Allah\u2019\u0131n Res\xfbl\xfc onlara: \u201cAllah\u2019\u0131n devesine ve onun su i\xe7me hakk\u0131na dokunmay\u0131n!\u201d dedi. Ama onlar onu yalanlad\u0131lar ve deveyi kestiler. Bunun \xfczerine Rableri g\xfcnahlar\u0131 sebebiyle onlar\u0131 hel\xe2k edip yerle bir etti. (Allah, bu i\u015fin) sonucundan korkmaz (ki).]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130\u015fte [[kavm-i Semud\u2019un|Semud kavminin]] [[acib|\u015fa\u015f\u0131rt\u0131c\u0131|garip ve hayret verici]] ve m\xfchim [[h\xe2disat\u0131n\u0131|olaylar\u0131n\u0131|ba\u015flar\u0131ndan ge\xe7enleri]] ve [[netaicini|sonu\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131]] ve [[s\xfb-i \xe2k\u0131betlerini|k\xf6t\xfc sonlar\u0131n\u0131|feci ak\u0131betlerini]], b\xf6yle k\u0131sa birka\xe7 c\xfcmle ile [[\xeecaz|\xf6zl\xfcl\xfck|az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatma]] i\xe7inde bir [[i\u2019caz|mucizelik|benzeri yap\u0131lamayan ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfcl\xfck]] ile [[selasetli|ak\u0131c\u0131|s\xf6z\xfcn p\xfcr\xfczs\xfcz ve ak\u0131c\u0131 olmas\u0131]] ve [[vuzuhlu|a\xe7\u0131k|net ve anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131r]] ve [[fehmi|anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131|kavray\u0131\u015f\u0131]] [[ihl\xe2l etmez|bozmaz|zarar vermez]] bir tarzda [[beyan ediyor|a\xe7\u0131kl\u0131yor|ifade ediyor]].\\r\\n\\r\\nHem mesela\\r\\n\\r\\n[[\u0648\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0630\u0652 \u0630\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0645\u064f\u063a\u064e\u0627\u0636\u0650\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0638\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0642\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0670\u0649 \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064f\u0651\u0644\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u0656\u0649 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e|Z\xfcnn\xfbn\u2019u (bal\u0131k sahibi Yunus\u2019u) da an. Hani o, \xf6fkelenerek gitmi\u015fti de kendisini asla s\u0131k\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmayaca\u011f\u0131m\u0131z\u0131 zannetmi\u015fti. Derken karanl\u0131klar i\xe7inde, \u201cSenden ba\u015fka il\xe2h yoktur. Seni eksikliklerden uzak tutar\u0131m. Ben ger\xe7ekten zalimlerden oldum\u201d diye dua etti.]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130\u015fte [[\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0642\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650|kendisini asla s\u0131k\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmayaca\u011f\u0131m\u0131z\u0131 (g\xfcc\xfcm\xfcz\xfcn yetmeyece\u011fini)]] c\xfcmlesinden [[\u0641\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0670\u0649 \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064f\u0651\u0644\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650|karanl\u0131klar i\xe7inde nida etti (seslendi)]] c\xfcmlesine kadar \xe7ok c\xfcmleler [[matv\xeedir|d\xfcr\xfclm\xfc\u015ft\xfcr|gizli b\u0131rak\u0131lm\u0131\u015f, atlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r]]. O [[mezk\xfbr|zikredilen|bahsedilen]] olmayan c\xfcmleler; [[fehmi|anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131]] [[ihl\xe2l etmiyor|bozmuyor]], [[selasete|ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131\u011fa]] zarar vermiyor. Hazret-i Yunus aleyhissel\xe2m\u0131n [[k\u0131ssas\u0131ndan|hikayesinden|ibretlik olay\u0131ndan]] m\xfchim esaslar\u0131 [[zikreder|anar|bahseder]]. [[M\xfcteb\xe2kisini|geriye kalan\u0131n\u0131]] akla [[havale eder|b\u0131rak\u0131r|y\xfckler]].\\r\\n\\r\\nHem mesela, Sure-i Yusuf\u2019ta [[\u0641\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0633\u0650\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650|beni g\xf6nderin]] kelimesinden [[\u064a\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064f\u0641\u064f \u0627\u064e\u064a\u064f\u0651\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0650\u0651\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0642\u064f|Yusuf, ey s\u0131dd\u0131k (do\u011fru s\xf6zl\xfc)]] ortas\u0131nda yedi sekiz c\xfcmle [[\xeecaz|\xf6zl\xfcl\xfck]] ile [[tayyedilmi\u015f|at\u0131lm\u0131\u015f|ge\xe7ilmi\u015f, d\xfcr\xfclm\xfc\u015f]]. Hi\xe7 [[fehmi|anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131]] [[ihl\xe2l etmiyor|bozmuyor]], [[selasetine|ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131na]] zarar vermiyor.\\r\\n\\r\\nBu \xe7e\u015fit [[mu\u2019cizane|mucizevi|mucize gibi]] [[\xeecazlar|\xf6zl\xfc anlat\u0131mlar]] Kur\u2019an\u2019da pek \xe7oktur. Hem pek g\xfczeldir.\\r\\n\\r\\nAmma Sure-i Kaf\u2019\u0131n \xe2yeti ise ondaki [[\xeecaz|\xf6zl\xfcl\xfck]] pek [[acib|\u015fa\u015f\u0131rt\u0131c\u0131|garip]] ve [[mu\u2019cizanedir|mucizevidir]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc k\xe2firin pek m\xfcthi\u015f ve \xe7ok uzun ve bir g\xfcn\xfc elli bin sene olan [[istikbaline|gelece\u011fine]] ve o [[istikbalin|gelece\u011fin]] deh\u015fetli [[ink\u0131labat\u0131nda|d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcmlerinde|b\xfcy\xfck de\u011fi\u015fim ve devrimlerinde]] k\xe2firin ba\u015f\u0131na gelecek [[el\xeem|ac\u0131 verici|elemli]] ve m\xfchim [[h\xe2disata|olaylara]] birer birer parmak bas\u0131yor. \u015eim\u015fek gibi fikri, onlar \xfcst\xfcnde gezdiriyor. O pek \xe7ok uzun zaman\u0131, [[haz\u0131r|haz\u0131rda olan|\u015fimdiki]] bir sahife gibi [[nazara|bak\u0131\u015fa|g\xf6ze]] g\xf6sterir. Zikredilmeyen [[h\xe2disat\u0131|olaylar\u0131]] [[hayale havale edip|hayal g\xfcc\xfcne b\u0131rak\u0131p]] [[ulvi|y\xfcce|y\xfcksek]] bir [[selasetle|ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131kla]] [[beyan eder|a\xe7\u0131klar|anlat\u0131r]].\\r\\n\\r\\n[[\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064f\u0631\u0650\u0626\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0627\u0670\u0646\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u0650\u062a\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u062a\u064f\u0631\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e|Kur\u2019an okundu\u011fu zaman onu dinleyin ve susun ki size merhamet edilsin.]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130\u015fte ey \u015feytan! \u015eimdi bir s\xf6z\xfcn daha varsa s\xf6yle\u2026\\r\\n\\r\\n\u015eeytan der: Bunlara kar\u015f\u0131 gelemem, [[m\xfcdafaa edemem|savunamam]]. Fakat \xe7ok ahmaklar var, beni dinliyorlar ve insan [[suretinde|\u015feklinde|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfcnde]] \xe7ok \u015feytanlar var, bana yard\u0131m ediyorlar ve [[feylesoflardan|filozoflardan]] \xe7ok firavunlar var, [[enaniyetlerini|benliklerini|egolar\u0131n\u0131]] ok\u015fayan meseleleri benden ders al\u0131yorlar. Senin bu gibi s\xf6zlerin [[ne\u015frine|yay\u0131lmas\u0131na|yay\u0131nlanmas\u0131na]] [[set \xe7ekerler|engel olurlar]]. Bunun i\xe7in sana [[teslim-i silah etmem|silah\u0131 teslim etmem|teslim olmam]]!\\r\\n\\r\\n[[\u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0643\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0643\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f|Seni her t\xfcrl\xfc noksandan tenzih ederiz. Senin bize \xf6\u011fretti\u011finden ba\u015fka bizim hi\xe7bir bilgimiz yoktur. \u015e\xfcphesiz her \u015feyi hakk\u0131yla bilen, her \u015feyi hikmetle yapan sensin.]]\\r\\n\\r\\n***\\r\\n\\r\\n[1] [[H\xe2\u015fiye|Dipnot]]: Evet, [[k\xfcre-i arz|d\xfcnya k\xfcresi|yery\xfcz\xfc]] k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle beraber [[semavata|g\xf6klere]] kar\u015f\u0131 gelebilir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc nas\u0131l ki daim\xee bir \xe7e\u015fme, [[v\xe2ridats\u0131z|gelirsiz|su kayna\u011f\u0131 olmayan]] b\xfcy\xfck bir g\xf6lden daha b\xfcy\xfck denilebilir. Hem bir \xf6l\xe7ek ile bir \u015fey \xf6l\xe7erek ba\u015fka yere nakledilen ve onun elinden ge\xe7mi\u015f ve ona girmi\u015f \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015f bir [[mahsulatla|\xfcr\xfcnlerle|\xe7\u0131kan sonu\xe7larla]], [[zahiren|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015fte]] binler defa \xf6l\xe7ekten b\xfcy\xfck ve da\u011f gibi bir cisimle o \xf6l\xe7ek [[muvazeneye \xe7\u0131kabilir|dengelenip kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131r\u0131labilir]].\\r\\n\\r\\nAynen \xf6yle de [[k\xfcre-i arz|d\xfcnya k\xfcresi|yery\xfcz\xfc]], [[Cenab-\u0131 Hak|Hakk olan Y\xfcce Allah]] onu sanat\u0131na bir [[me\u015fher|sergi yeri|te\u015fhir yeri]] ve [[icad\u0131na|yaratmas\u0131na|var etmesine]] bir [[mah\u015fer|toplanma yeri]] ve hikmetine [[medar|kaynak|dayanak]] ve kudretine [[mazhar|g\xf6r\xfcnme yeri|tecelli yeri]] ve rahmetine [[mezher|\xe7i\xe7ek a\xe7ma yeri|zuhur yeri]] ve cennetine [[mezraa|tarla|ekim yeri]] ve [[hadsiz|s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z|say\u0131s\u0131z]] k\xe2inata ve [[mahlukat|yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flar]] \xe2lemlerine \xf6l\xe7ek ve [[mazi|ge\xe7mi\u015f]] denizlerine ve [[gayb \xe2lemine|g\xf6r\xfcnmeyen aleme]] akacak bir \xe7e\u015fme h\xfckm\xfcnde [[icad etmi\u015f|yaratm\u0131\u015f|var etmi\u015f]]. Her sene kat kat ve katmerli y\xfcz bin tarzda, [[masnuattan|sanatl\u0131 varl\u0131klardan]] dokunmu\u015f g\xf6mleklerini de\u011fi\u015ftirdi\u011fi ve \xe7ok defa dolup maziye bo\u015faltarak [[gayb \xe2lemine|g\xf6r\xfcnmeyen aleme]] d\xf6kt\xfc\u011f\xfc b\xfct\xfcn o [[m\xfcteceddid|yenilenen|tazelenen]] \xe2lemleri ve arz\u0131n [[m\xfcteaddid|\xe7e\u015fitli|\xe7ok say\u0131da]] g\xf6mleklerini [[nazara al|dikkate al|g\xf6z \xf6n\xfcne al]], yani b\xfct\xfcn mazisini [[haz\u0131r|\u015fimdiki zaman]] [[farz et|varsay]]. Sonra [[yeknesak|tek d\xfcze|monoton]] ve bir derece basit [[semavata|g\xf6klere]] kar\u015f\u0131 [[muvazene et|kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131r|\xf6l\xe7]]. G\xf6receksin ki arz, [[ziyade|fazla]] gelmezse [[noksan|eksik]] da kalmaz. \u0130\u015fte [[\u0631\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650|G\xf6klerin ve yerin Rabbi]] s\u0131rr\u0131n\u0131 anla.\\r\\n\\r\\n[2] [[H\xe2\u015fiye|Dipnot]]: [[Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem|Hikmetli Kur\'an]], k\xe2firlerin [[k\xfcfriyatlar\u0131n\u0131|k\xfcf\xfcr s\xf6zlerini|inkar ifadelerini]] ve [[galiz|kaba|\xe7irkin ve a\u011f\u0131r]] [[tabiratlar\u0131n\u0131|tabirlerini|ifadelerini]] iptal etmek i\xe7in [[zikretti\u011fine|zikretmesine|anmas\u0131na]] [[istinaden|dayanarak]], [[ehl-i dalaletin|sapk\u0131nl\u0131k ehlinin|yoldan \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015flar\u0131n]] [[fikr-i k\xfcfr\xeelerinin|inkarc\u0131 fikirlerinin]] b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn [[muhaliyetini|imkans\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131]] ve b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn \xe7\xfcr\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc g\xf6stermek i\xe7in \u015fu [[tabirat\u0131|tabirleri|ifadeleri]] [[farz-\u0131 muhal|imkans\u0131z varsay\u0131m|olmayacak bir \u015feyi olmu\u015f sayma]] [[suretinde|\u015feklinde]], titreyerek kullanmaya mecbur oldum.","modernText":"K\u0131sa birka\xe7 c\xfcmle ile [[Tufan b\xfcy\xfck olay\u0131n\u0131|Tufan h\xe2dise-i az\xeemesini|Nuh Tufan\u0131 denilen o b\xfcy\xfck olay\u0131]] [[sonu\xe7lar\u0131yla|netaiciyle|neticeleriyle]] \xf6yle [[k\u0131saca ve \xf6zl\xfcce|\xeecazk\xe2rane|az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatarak]] ve [[mucizevi bir \u015fekilde|mu\u2019cizane|mucize gibi]] [[a\xe7\u0131kl\u0131yor|beyan ediyor|anlat\u0131yor]] ki \xe7ok [[belagat ehlini|ehl-i bel\xe2gat\u0131|s\xf6z\xfc g\xfczel ve etkili s\xf6yleyenleri]], [[s\xf6z sanat\u0131na|bel\xe2gat\u0131na|edebi \xfcst\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfcne]] secde ettirmi\u015f.\\r\\n\\r\\nHem mesela\\r\\n\\r\\n[[Sem\xfbd (kavmi), azg\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131 y\xfcz\xfcnden (peygamberini) yalanlad\u0131. Onlar\u0131n en bedbaht\u0131 (deveyi kesmek i\xe7in) at\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda, Allah\u2019\u0131n Res\xfbl\xfc onlara: \u201cAllah\u2019\u0131n devesine ve onun su i\xe7me hakk\u0131na dokunmay\u0131n!\u201d dedi. Ama onlar onu yalanlad\u0131lar ve deveyi kestiler. Bunun \xfczerine Rableri g\xfcnahlar\u0131 sebebiyle onlar\u0131 hel\xe2k edip yerle bir etti. (Allah, bu i\u015fin) sonucundan korkmaz (ki).|\u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0651\u0628\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0637\u064e\u063a\u0652\u0648\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0627\u0650\u0630\u0650 \u0627\u0646\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0634\u0652\u0642\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0642\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0642\u0652\u064a\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0641\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0651\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0651\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0648\u0651\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u06de \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064f \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u0670\u064a\u0647\u064e\u0627|]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130\u015fte [[Semud kavminin|kavm-i Semud\u2019un|]] [[\u015fa\u015f\u0131rt\u0131c\u0131|acib|garip ve hayret verici]] ve m\xfchim [[olaylar\u0131n\u0131|h\xe2disat\u0131n\u0131|ba\u015flar\u0131ndan ge\xe7enleri]] ve [[sonu\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131|netaicini|]] ve [[k\xf6t\xfc sonlar\u0131n\u0131|s\xfb-i \xe2k\u0131betlerini|feci ak\u0131betlerini]], b\xf6yle k\u0131sa birka\xe7 c\xfcmle ile [[\xf6zl\xfcl\xfck|\xeecaz|az s\xf6zle \xe7ok mana anlatma]] i\xe7inde bir [[mucizelik|i\u2019caz|benzeri yap\u0131lamayan ola\u011fan\xfcst\xfcl\xfck]] ile [[ak\u0131c\u0131|selasetli|s\xf6z\xfcn p\xfcr\xfczs\xfcz ve ak\u0131c\u0131 olmas\u0131]] ve [[a\xe7\u0131k|vuzuhlu|net ve anla\u015f\u0131l\u0131r]] ve [[anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131|fehmi|kavray\u0131\u015f\u0131]] [[bozmaz|ihl\xe2l etmez|zarar vermez]] bir tarzda [[a\xe7\u0131kl\u0131yor|beyan ediyor|ifade ediyor]].\\r\\n\\r\\nHem mesela\\r\\n\\r\\n[[Z\xfcnn\xfbn\u2019u (bal\u0131k sahibi Yunus\u2019u) da an. Hani o, \xf6fkelenerek gitmi\u015fti de kendisini asla s\u0131k\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmayaca\u011f\u0131m\u0131z\u0131 zannetmi\u015fti. Derken karanl\u0131klar i\xe7inde, \u201cSenden ba\u015fka il\xe2h yoktur. Seni eksikliklerden uzak tutar\u0131m. Ben ger\xe7ekten zalimlerden oldum\u201d diye dua etti.|\u0648\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0630\u0652 \u0630\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0645\u064f\u063a\u064e\u0627\u0636\u0650\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0638\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0642\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0670\u0649 \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064f\u0651\u0644\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u0656\u0649 \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0645\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e|]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130\u015fte [[kendisini asla s\u0131k\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmayaca\u011f\u0131m\u0131z\u0131 (g\xfcc\xfcm\xfcz\xfcn yetmeyece\u011fini)|\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0642\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650|]] c\xfcmlesinden [[karanl\u0131klar i\xe7inde nida etti (seslendi)|\u0641\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0670\u0649 \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064f\u0651\u0644\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650|]] c\xfcmlesine kadar \xe7ok c\xfcmleler [[d\xfcr\xfclm\xfc\u015ft\xfcr|matv\xeedir|gizli b\u0131rak\u0131lm\u0131\u015f, atlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r]]. O [[zikredilen|mezk\xfbr|bahsedilen]] olmayan c\xfcmleler; [[anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131|fehmi|]] [[bozmuyor|ihl\xe2l etmiyor|]], [[ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131\u011fa|selasete|]] zarar vermiyor. Hazret-i Yunus aleyhissel\xe2m\u0131n [[hikayesinden|k\u0131ssas\u0131ndan|ibretlik olay\u0131ndan]] m\xfchim esaslar\u0131 [[anar|zikreder|bahseder]]. [[geriye kalan\u0131n\u0131|M\xfcteb\xe2kisini|]] akla [[b\u0131rak\u0131r|havale eder|y\xfckler]].\\r\\n\\r\\nHem mesela, Sure-i Yusuf\u2019ta [[beni g\xf6nderin|\u0641\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0633\u0650\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650|]] kelimesinden [[Yusuf, ey s\u0131dd\u0131k (do\u011fru s\xf6zl\xfc)|\u064a\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064f\u0641\u064f \u0627\u064e\u064a\u064f\u0651\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0650\u0651\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0642\u064f|]] ortas\u0131nda yedi sekiz c\xfcmle [[\xf6zl\xfcl\xfck|\xeecaz|]] ile [[at\u0131lm\u0131\u015f|tayyedilmi\u015f|ge\xe7ilmi\u015f, d\xfcr\xfclm\xfc\u015f]]. Hi\xe7 [[anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131|fehmi|]] [[bozmuyor|ihl\xe2l etmiyor|]], [[ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131na|selasetine|]] zarar vermiyor.\\r\\n\\r\\nBu \xe7e\u015fit [[mucizevi|mu\u2019cizane|mucize gibi]] [[\xf6zl\xfc anlat\u0131mlar|\xeecazlar|]] Kur\u2019an\u2019da pek \xe7oktur. Hem pek g\xfczeldir.\\r\\n\\r\\nAmma Sure-i Kaf\u2019\u0131n \xe2yeti ise ondaki [[\xf6zl\xfcl\xfck|\xeecaz|]] pek [[\u015fa\u015f\u0131rt\u0131c\u0131|acib|garip]] ve [[mucizevidir|mu\u2019cizanedir|]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc k\xe2firin pek m\xfcthi\u015f ve \xe7ok uzun ve bir g\xfcn\xfc elli bin sene olan [[gelece\u011fine|istikbaline|]] ve o [[gelece\u011fin|istikbalin|]] deh\u015fetli [[d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcmlerinde|ink\u0131labat\u0131nda|b\xfcy\xfck de\u011fi\u015fim ve devrimlerinde]] k\xe2firin ba\u015f\u0131na gelecek [[ac\u0131 verici|el\xeem|elemli]] ve m\xfchim [[olaylara|h\xe2disata|]] birer birer parmak bas\u0131yor. \u015eim\u015fek gibi fikri, onlar \xfcst\xfcnde gezdiriyor. O pek \xe7ok uzun zaman\u0131, [[haz\u0131rda olan|haz\u0131r|\u015fimdiki]] bir sahife gibi [[bak\u0131\u015fa|nazara|g\xf6ze]] g\xf6sterir. Zikredilmeyen [[olaylar\u0131|h\xe2disat\u0131|]] [[hayal g\xfcc\xfcne b\u0131rak\u0131p|hayale havale edip|]] [[y\xfcce|ulvi|y\xfcksek]] bir [[ak\u0131c\u0131l\u0131kla|selasetle|]] [[a\xe7\u0131klar|beyan eder|anlat\u0131r]].\\r\\n\\r\\n[[Kur\u2019an okundu\u011fu zaman onu dinleyin ve susun ki size merhamet edilsin.|\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064f\u0631\u0650\u0626\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0627\u0670\u0646\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u0650\u062a\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u062a\u064f\u0631\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e|]]\\r\\n\\r\\n\u0130\u015fte ey \u015feytan! \u015eimdi bir s\xf6z\xfcn daha varsa s\xf6yle\u2026\\r\\n\\r\\n\u015eeytan der: Bunlara kar\u015f\u0131 gelemem, [[savunamam|m\xfcdafaa edemem|]]. Fakat \xe7ok ahmaklar var, beni dinliyorlar ve insan [[\u015feklinde|suretinde|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfcnde]] \xe7ok \u015feytanlar var, bana yard\u0131m ediyorlar ve [[filozoflardan|feylesoflardan|]] \xe7ok firavunlar var, [[benliklerini|enaniyetlerini|egolar\u0131n\u0131]] ok\u015fayan meseleleri benden ders al\u0131yorlar. Senin bu gibi s\xf6zlerin [[yay\u0131lmas\u0131na|ne\u015frine|yay\u0131nlanmas\u0131na]] [[engel olurlar|set \xe7ekerler|]]. Bunun i\xe7in sana [[silah\u0131 teslim etmem|teslim-i silah etmem|teslim olmam]]!\\r\\n\\r\\n[[Seni her t\xfcrl\xfc noksandan tenzih ederiz. Senin bize \xf6\u011fretti\u011finden ba\u015fka bizim hi\xe7bir bilgimiz yoktur. \u015e\xfcphesiz her \u015feyi hakk\u0131yla bilen, her \u015feyi hikmetle yapan sensin.|\u0633\u064f\u0628\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0653\u0627 \u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0643\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0643\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064f|]]\\r\\n\\r\\n***\\r\\n\\r\\n[1] [[Dipnot|H\xe2\u015fiye|]]: Evet, [[d\xfcnya k\xfcresi|k\xfcre-i arz|yery\xfcz\xfc]] k\xfc\xe7\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcyle beraber [[g\xf6klere|semavata|]] kar\u015f\u0131 gelebilir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc nas\u0131l ki daim\xee bir \xe7e\u015fme, [[gelirsiz|v\xe2ridats\u0131z|su kayna\u011f\u0131 olmayan]] b\xfcy\xfck bir g\xf6lden daha b\xfcy\xfck denilebilir. Hem bir \xf6l\xe7ek ile bir \u015fey \xf6l\xe7erek ba\u015fka yere nakledilen ve onun elinden ge\xe7mi\u015f ve ona girmi\u015f \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015f bir [[\xfcr\xfcnlerle|mahsulatla|\xe7\u0131kan sonu\xe7larla]], [[g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015fte|zahiren|]] binler defa \xf6l\xe7ekten b\xfcy\xfck ve da\u011f gibi bir cisimle o \xf6l\xe7ek [[dengelenip kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131r\u0131labilir|muvazeneye \xe7\u0131kabilir|]].\\r\\n\\r\\nAynen \xf6yle de [[d\xfcnya k\xfcresi|k\xfcre-i arz|yery\xfcz\xfc]], [[Hakk olan Y\xfcce Allah|Cenab-\u0131 Hak|]] onu sanat\u0131na bir [[sergi yeri|me\u015fher|te\u015fhir yeri]] ve [[yaratmas\u0131na|icad\u0131na|var etmesine]] bir [[toplanma yeri|mah\u015fer|]] ve hikmetine [[kaynak|medar|dayanak]] ve kudretine [[g\xf6r\xfcnme yeri|mazhar|tecelli yeri]] ve rahmetine [[\xe7i\xe7ek a\xe7ma yeri|mezher|zuhur yeri]] ve cennetine [[tarla|mezraa|ekim yeri]] ve [[s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131z|hadsiz|say\u0131s\u0131z]] k\xe2inata ve [[yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flar|mahlukat|]] \xe2lemlerine \xf6l\xe7ek ve [[ge\xe7mi\u015f|mazi|]] denizlerine ve [[g\xf6r\xfcnmeyen aleme|gayb \xe2lemine|]] akacak bir \xe7e\u015fme h\xfckm\xfcnde [[yaratm\u0131\u015f|icad etmi\u015f|var etmi\u015f]]. Her sene kat kat ve katmerli y\xfcz bin tarzda, [[sanatl\u0131 varl\u0131klardan|masnuattan|]] dokunmu\u015f g\xf6mleklerini de\u011fi\u015ftirdi\u011fi ve \xe7ok defa dolup maziye bo\u015faltarak [[g\xf6r\xfcnmeyen aleme|gayb \xe2lemine|]] d\xf6kt\xfc\u011f\xfc b\xfct\xfcn o [[yenilenen|m\xfcteceddid|tazelenen]] \xe2lemleri ve arz\u0131n [[\xe7e\u015fitli|m\xfcteaddid|\xe7ok say\u0131da]] g\xf6mleklerini [[dikkate al|nazara al|g\xf6z \xf6n\xfcne al]], yani b\xfct\xfcn mazisini [[\u015fimdiki zaman|haz\u0131r|]] [[varsay|farz et|]]. Sonra [[tek d\xfcze|yeknesak|monoton]] ve bir derece basit [[g\xf6klere|semavata|]] kar\u015f\u0131 [[kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131r|muvazene et|\xf6l\xe7]]. G\xf6receksin ki arz, [[fazla|ziyade|]] gelmezse [[eksik|noksan|]] da kalmaz. \u0130\u015fte [[G\xf6klerin ve yerin Rabbi|\u0631\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650|]] s\u0131rr\u0131n\u0131 anla.\\r\\n\\r\\n[2] [[Dipnot|H\xe2\u015fiye|]]: [[Hikmetli Kur\'an|Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem|]], k\xe2firlerin [[k\xfcf\xfcr s\xf6zlerini|k\xfcfriyatlar\u0131n\u0131|inkar ifadelerini]] ve [[kaba|galiz|\xe7irkin ve a\u011f\u0131r]] [[tabirlerini|tabiratlar\u0131n\u0131|ifadelerini]] iptal etmek i\xe7in [[zikretmesine|zikretti\u011fine|anmas\u0131na]] [[dayanarak|istinaden|]], [[sapk\u0131nl\u0131k ehlinin|ehl-i dalaletin|yoldan \xe7\u0131km\u0131\u015flar\u0131n]] [[inkarc\u0131 fikirlerinin|fikr-i k\xfcfr\xeelerinin|]] b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn [[imkans\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131|muhaliyetini|]] ve b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn \xe7\xfcr\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc g\xf6stermek i\xe7in \u015fu [[tabirleri|tabirat\u0131|ifadeleri]] [[imkans\u0131z varsay\u0131m|farz-\u0131 muhal|olmayacak bir \u015feyi olmu\u015f sayma]] [[\u015feklinde|suretinde|]], titreyerek kullanmaya mecbur oldum.","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.25-21:10","lastUpdated":"2025.12.25-21:10"}]')}}]);